            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>今年南方雪灾，北方干且暖。因为暖，这几天迎春与连翘金晃晃一片，玉兰也开了。往年我把玉兰当雪看，今年不许。在北方，如此早春算是灿烂，我已没有东风一吹，顿起游南方花海的念提。日前收到朱千华的信以及《南方草木札记》文稿，约我作序，我又有蠢蠢欲动回南方之心了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000146": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000146",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000147": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000147",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>《南方草木札记》，我读罢有欣欣向荣的感觉，空气湿润，和光同水，不是和光同尘，东边日出西边雨，是和光同水。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000148": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000148",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000149": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000149",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>植物志不论，植物栽种培育工具书不论，以前我读过以草木为主题的文学性图书，大致可分为&quot;博闻录异&quot;与&quot;言志抒情&quot;两大类。《南方草木札记》很让人马上联想到《南方草木状》，这会心生喜欢的。《南方草木状》，我是当文学看的（我把《本草纲目》也当文学看，大概与我日常里所持的泛文学观有关）。《南方草木状》本质还是&quot;博闻录异&quot;，如&quot;诸蔗&quot;条可说&quot;博闻&quot;；&quot;枫人&quot;条可说&quot;录异&quot;，这样的条目颇多。还有一类是&quot;言志抒情&quot;的，杨朔、秦牧他们的以草木为文学性主题的散文随笔常常如此。在这两者之间，另有一种既&quot;博闻录异&quot;又&quot;言志抒情&quot;的--姑且论之为&quot;新草木写作&quot;。这个写作较为边缘，以前有我乡前贤周瘦鹃先生，现在则有一时才俊朱千华等人。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000150": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000150",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000151": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000151",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>不管怎么写，只要欣欣向荣，其华竞发，春华者冬秀，夏华者春秀，秋华者夏秀，冬华者秋秀，四时未尝无华也，读者就不寂寥。起码我是心生喜欢的。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000152": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000152",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000153": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000153",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>是为序。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000154": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000154",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000155": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000155",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>二零零八年三月二十六日   目木楼头</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000156": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000156",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000157": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000157",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>缘起</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000158": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000158",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000159": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000159",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>四月，在南方腹地。邕水以南，或者以北的大片地带，有着无数的希望。漫天的春花一路扑卷。一亩亩，一垅垅。早年读屈子，始对那些奇花异草产生迷恋。江蓠、秋兰、木兰、椒、蕙、芳、薜荔，白芷，杜衡，春兰……注定与我今生有缘。她们的芬芳早就漫过我的衣衫，至今仍能让我幸福地沐浴。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000160": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000160",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000161": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000161",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>一年来，行走在南方。随处可见南方草木摇扬葳蕤，散发出盎然生意。山水纡曲。邕江两岸山峦重叠，丘陵延绵。大明山、大瑶山、十万大山皆不知里数，袅袅濯濯，封天蔽日。山渐深，草木泉石渐幽。空山无人，水流花开。有草木杂乱丛生，枝叶却茂盛。风吹草动。远远望去，仿佛丹青高手，逸笔草草。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000162": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000162",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000163": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000163",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>我把采撷到的这些草木，带回去，夹入我的书中。让她们美好的品质，时时芳香我的灵魂。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000164": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000164",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000165": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000165",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>有些事情恍如梦中。有些日子历历在目。很多时候，我一个人踯躅在草木繁茂的心圩江畔，或安静地坐在宽阔无边的榕树下，听百鸟鸣唱；或是在月色迷离的晚上，撑条竹排，滑行在清澈的山水间，不远处飘来壮女、瑶女、侗女撩人的山歌。那山歌仅几里地外，仿佛扑鼻而来的一缕缕清香，早已让我莫名心动。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000166": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000166",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000167": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000167",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>正文</p></div>"
        },
