        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000319": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000319",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><h2><span style=\"\">第9节：潮湿而柔软的思念--番石榴</span></h2></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000320": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000320",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>\t</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000321": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000321",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>潮湿而柔软的思念--番石榴</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000322": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000322",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000323": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000323",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>来南方之后，如同进入植物王国，满目繁花，却又不知其名。还有那些目不暇接的时蔬瓜果，更是闻所未闻，根本叫不出它们的名字。我第一次看见番石榴，是和爱人在超市的水果摊。当时就很惊讶，怎么是这个名字？与石榴的样子毫不相干啊。初次相识，感觉其貌不扬。它的皮是青黄色，不像苹果那样光滑，也不像梨那样粗糙，但它的形状像青梨。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000324": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000324",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000325": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000325",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>北方的石榴我是见识过的。譬如临潼石榴，我吃过，果中佳品，名不虚传。还带回几只。临潼石榴形色美艳，十分惹人喜爱。其他地方也有。什么青壳石榴，软籽石榴等。不管是哪种，其形状大体相似。籽粒或白似水晶，或红如玛瑙。晋人潘岳在《安石榴赋》中写道&quot;榴者，天下之奇树，九州之名果&quot;、&quot;缤纷磊落，垂光耀质，滋味浸液，馨香流溢&quot;。把石</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000326": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000326",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000327": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000327",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>榴的色、香、味、形写得华美又鲜活。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000328": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000328",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000329": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000329",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>但是当我见到番石榴，仔细端详，怎么也看不出石榴的样子。番石榴像青梨。番石榴和北方的石榴不一样，它是南方的特产。首先它的外表像梨但不是梨，它有着雪白的果肉和淡粉的籽。番石榴熟了，就散出一种浓浓的果香--这香味是另类的，并不好闻。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000330": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000330",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000331": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000331",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>买来番石榴，洗净，用洁白的盘子盛。先看，状如生梨，外表嫩绿色，青翠翠的感觉。可连皮生食，不用削皮去籽。咬一口，慢慢回味，不是脆。也不是甜。而是有点绵，有青枣的感觉。一开始，似乎并没有预料的那样清脆好吃。另外，还有籽。那些籽像芝麻，也是白白的，据说吃下去没事的。就连籽一起吃。籽很硬。却也嚼着咽下去了--那些籽是很讨厌的--你在嚼着软绵绵的果肉时，那些硬的籽搅在里面，磕磕碰碰的，很不爽。说实话，我初次吃番石榴的感觉，并不是太好。也就没把这果子放在心上。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000332": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000332",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000333": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000333",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>后来，和爱人在科园大道一家西餐厅再次吃到番石榴。果盘。番石榴切好，一瓣一瓣放盘子里。我都忘了曾经吃过番石榴。时令鲜果，令人垂涎。就一瓣一瓣吃。果肉淡青色，微脆，籽儿淡黄色，有甜味。感觉很奇妙--满满一盘番石榴，很快吃完。但番石榴入口之后还是有点独特的气味--却一下子说不出，在你回味之际，又消失。这是一种很有个性的味道，它不能用单纯的酸或甜来形容--当你吃过一次--有的人就此不再对此果发生兴趣，就不吃；如果再吃一回，那种绵软香甜的味就出来了，经常吃，还能上瘾。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000334": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000334",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000335": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000335",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>后来，在小区的水果摊上，看过一种叫&quot;胭脂红&quot;的番石榴，个不大，但总算让我找到了一点石榴的感觉--很像。就买了两斤尝尝鲜。色泽鲜红，果肉厚，爽绵嫩滑。但后来，我又听说，胭脂红，山里人称之为鸡屎果，说熟了的果子有那一种味。我就不信，仔细检查，味虽有异，却不是传说的那样。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000336": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000336",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000337": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000337",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>我只见识了番石榴，却没看见番石榴树是什么样子。有时候，我握着青青的番石榴悬想半天，想像着番石榴树的样子。这样的青果子，不是太精致的，挂在庭院里是很不错的观赏植物。我想像在一个秋日的午后，我在庭院里喝着茶，看着树上挂满青青的番石榴。树是落叶乔木或灌木，我不知道，但肯定不高大，像石榴那样丛生，枝条直挺而细密，附有硬刺。树皮有些粗糙，但木质坚硬，整株树上上下下盘根错节。在春天的时候，番石榴的花，一定也是很火红的吧。先是枝头长出一个个花骨朵，似小小的火苗，有杜鹃那般红艳。一树开花笑满枝，多灿烂，在梦中可以笑出声。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000338": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000338",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000339": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000339",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>庭院景致毕竟太玲珑了些。哪有一片番石榴园来得宽敞疏放呢。我曾想在心圩江畔拥有一片番石榴园。心圩江有很大的一片空地，正荒着。如果种番石榴树，一定是件美事。那样我就可以天天看到番石榴树了。当番石榴成熟，满园飘香，遍野芬芳。树枝上挂满了青翠的果子。那些果子的形状很奇特。圆形，椭圆形，葫芦形，纺锤形。园子里长满灌木丛，大部分是番石榴树，放眼远望，成片成片的，满园都是。有些树老了，树干硕大，树冠宽阔。还有，那些番石榴都是新的品种，当你切开番石榴，你会看到果心有不同的颜色。一如五谷的光芒。白心、红心、黄心、紫心。番石榴切开，放入盘子里，五颜六色，水嫩得让人不忍触摸。那是一种潮湿柔软的思念。她水嫩的肌肤之香像一曲山歌从我身边绕过。一年只有这一次，隔着遥远，故乡的风声在异乡幽幽响起。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000340": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000340",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000341": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000341",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>找一个好天气，和心爱的人一起远足，去看番石榴树吧。南方的骄阳洒在那些番石榴树上，树叶里渗出稠密的绿，洒下来，点点滴滴，就长成青绿的番石榴。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000342": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000342",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000343": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000343",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000344": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000344",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><h2><span style=\"\">第10节：黄叶拥篱青灯煨竽--荔浦芋头(1)</span></h2></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000345": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000345",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>\t</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000346": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000346",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>黄叶拥篱青灯煨竽--荔浦芋头</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000347": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000347",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000348": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000348",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>芋头其貌不扬，外表毛糙，许多芋头子堆在一起像乡间的那些毛头小子。芋头南北都有。不是稀罕物。当年在苏北古溪河畔，母亲常在自留地里种芋头。培土，浇灌，茎有一人多高。叶子很大，远远望去，像莲叶田田，一片碧绿。那些没完没了的炎热中午，我躺在芋头叶下睡觉，梦见沙沙沙的声音。阳光穿透芋叶像急雨般射来。那时我早起的第一件事就是去看芋头叶，亮晶晶的水珠布满叶上，摇摇欲坠。我踮起脚才能看到。我一手抓住芋头的茎，芋叶上的水珠，就滚落我一脸。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000349": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000349",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000350": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000350",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>芋头长成一棵一棵。母亲用镰刀割下一些支茎，切碎，煮熟，做猪食。那些翠绿的叶子就成了猪们的梦--它们吃饱了，会安静好长时间。我在农村那些年，家里每年都养一两头猪。最大一只，有五百斤重。有一次，不知何故那头猪撞断圈栏，疯了似的跑到地里，把芋头拱倒--它的嘴像尖利的犁--把土里的芋头翻了个遍。不知它要找什么，谁也不敢碰它。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000351": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000351",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000352": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000352",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>我的一个表兄是兽医。站在旁边观察良久，终于明白原委。猪吃了没煮熟的芋叶。叶子看似翠绿，若没煮熟就会有一种很刺激的成分。猪吃了满嘴麻痒，忍不住嗷嗷叫，龇牙咧嘴，像长满刺。后来，我看到那头壮实的猪嘴肿得像个冬瓜。表兄对此束手无策。而猪并没有停下来的意思。最后，表兄找来渔网，撒下，把猪网住。任由它在地上翻滚。折腾完了。芋头地一片狼藉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000353": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000353",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000354": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000354",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>那是我十岁前见到过的芋头地。我至今还能想起，那猪精疲力竭地躺在地上，后来就把它抬上大板车拖走了--临走还是龇牙咧嘴状，很恐怖。这件事母亲说过多次。十岁之前，我记住了很多奇怪的事。芋头地里那头疯狂的猪是其中之一。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000355": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000355",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000356": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000356",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000357": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000357",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><h2><span style=\"\">第11节：黄叶拥篱青灯煨竽--荔浦芋头(2)</span></h2></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000358": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000358",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>\t</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000359": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000359",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>被猪拱出来的芋头都是很小的子儿。母亲把芋头子从芋头上掰下来，用瓷片刮净毛皮，做芋头青菜汤。我和母亲吃了好长时间的芋头青菜汤。母亲说过，故乡的芋头是一种叫香芋的品种，吃起来很香，很粉，是其他地方没有的。故乡的芋头吃法，很朴素，没有多少花样。除了做汤，还可以炒着吃。还可以刨成丝，和些肉末，炸芋头丸，对贫穷的故乡而言，这是最奢侈的一种吃法--并不常有，一年中只有春节才吃上一回。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000360": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000360",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000361": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000361",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>此外，就是冬天，大雪封门时，于火盆旁边，烤芋。后来读《小窗幽记》，所说的&quot;拥炉煨芋，欣然一饱&quot;，也就是这个境界吧。火盆红红的，周边一圈围了芋头，连着皮，冒着热气。饿了，就撕开皮吃。香喷喷的。一家人围着火盆，外面风雪再大，日子再穷，也都是暖洋洋的。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000362": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000362",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000363": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000363",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>你听完我的叙述并不出声。我不知道我所说的故乡的芋是不是很土--做法简单，吃法单一。虽然其味香糯无比。这里是邕江宾馆的休闲大厅。环境很优雅。萨克斯在吹KennyG的《GoingHome》。餐桌边有两丈高的鱼尾葵。我们在鱼尾葵下喝菊花茶聊天。我们谈起芋头的起因是，这家宾馆有个特色菜，叫拔丝芋头。我第一次听说，不知啥味儿。于是就谈起芋头。我说，芋头在《史记》上，称为&quot;蹲鸱&quot;。鸱，是猫头鹰。细细回味一下，真的很有意思。芋头的样子，很是可爱，大而圆，褐色，周身有毛，圆圆的芋头子让人想到猫头鹰圆圆的眼睛。这个想像，真是绝妙而奇特。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000364": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000364",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000365": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000365",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>你似乎对我说的故乡香芋没有特别的兴趣。你很平静。你问我去过荔浦没有。我说去了。只是匆匆而过。你说，荔浦产芋头。我说这不奇怪啊，全国都产芋头。你说，荔浦芋头是皇帝吃的，是贡品。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000366": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000366",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000367": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000367",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>我感到十分的新奇。芋头本是村野粗蔬，成为贡品，自有不寻常之处。正待细说，服务生端上一只盘子，说是拔丝芋头。奇怪的是，盘子上有罩。像一个要揭开的魔术，里面充满诱惑。罩掀开，一股热气冲天--浓郁的蜜香--芋香扑鼻而来。你迅速拿筷子将那些芋块一个个分开--那些金黄色的芋块上，浇了一层滚热的糖稀。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000368": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000368",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000369": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000369",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>荔浦芋头产于桂林地区的荔浦县。一般饭店，荔浦芋头是难以吃到的。因为荔浦芋头很特别，只有那一方水土盛产。这里的拔丝芋头，就是用荔浦芋头做的。我轻轻咬一口。视之，芋肉布满细小的红丝线。慢慢品尝。很香糯，口感松粉，细滑，有特别的甘香。果然与众不同。据说还有一道名菜，叫荔浦芋头扣肉，也是名不虚传。你说，下次请吃荔浦芋头扣肉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000370": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000370",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000371": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000371",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>我说，芋头的叶子，在我们家乡，叫芋头胡子，真是很形象的--那叶子就像一把垂下来的大胡子。南方叫什么？</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000372": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000372",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000373": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000373",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>你说，在南方，芋头叶，叫芋荷，也很形象。如果到了一片芋地，放眼远望，虽无红花，却也是满目&quot;接天莲叶无穷碧&quot;的景致，足以让人流连忘返了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000374": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000374",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000375": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000375",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>我说，在我家乡，结子的大芋头，家乡话，叫芋头头子。南方叫什么？你说，那就更形象了，叫&quot;芋娘&quot;。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000376": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000376",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000377": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000377",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>芋娘！我一下子震住了。在南方，大芋头，称为芋娘。多么形象的称呼--她的周围簇拥着许多芋子，像暖暖的一家。可是，当我听到芋娘二字，心中忽然堵得慌。来南方快有一年时间，却不曾回去看望母亲一眼。母亲已到古稀之年，还在家里忙碌着一日三餐。我知道，芋头青菜汤定然是少不了的。还有，母亲做的油炸芋头丸，我很久没有吃到了。当年在古溪河，母亲每年都要种好几亩芋头。只是每到冬天，她那种芋的手，常常有裂口。望着眼前的贡品荔浦芋头，我再也没有吃下去的心思。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000378": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000378",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000379": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000379",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000380": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000380",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><h2><span style=\"\">第12节：突然被打开的时光 -- 桫椤</span></h2></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000381": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000381",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>\t</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000382": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000382",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>突然被打开的时光 -- 桫椤     第一次看见桫椤，是在靖西。通灵大峡谷。这里是地球上一道美丽的裂痕。天光漏下。瀑布如注。那些阳光下的亚热带植物所散发的潮湿气息使天空不住地晃动。我们三人，在谷底茂密的丛林中向前穿行。到处是奇异的植物，翩然的蝴蝶，还有天空下低低飞翔的不知名的昆虫。就在那个阳光充足的溪边，我看见了桫椤。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000383": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000383",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000384": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000384",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>那时我们刚吃完饭，通过狭小的通道口进入峡谷，一下子走进原始丛林。感觉很奇异。也许是外界温度与峡谷里相差太多--有一种冷--像时光从身边倏忽飞逝。那些翠绿的植物皆闻所未闻。经过溪边，水湛蓝。水下有苔藓，有倒影，有阳光反射，一片清亮。很多植物来不及细看。我们感到身体轻飘飘地向前滑翔--真是这样的感觉--向谷底深处进发，全是下坡。天光变成了狭长的一条。我们在通灵谷底的暗无天日与柳暗花明间穿行。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000385": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000385",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000386": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000386",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>桫椤性喜温暖湿润，常生长在林下或河边、溪谷两旁的阴湿之地。在一道小溪的拐弯处，我看见了桫椤。桫椤这两个字，我一辈子都会记得很清楚。很多年前，我拿着一本画册给儿子讲恐龙。我说恐龙的食物是沙罗。儿子当即纠正说，呵呵老爸也读错字呢。不是沙罗，是桫椤。那个字读梭。我很惶恐。心里不踏实，忙去翻字典。桫椤果然读梭罗。于是桫椤这两个字就顽强地印在脑海里。真是坚韧，怎么也忘不掉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000387": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000387",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000388": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000388",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>说桫椤是很坚韧的植物真是太委屈它了。桫椤岂止是坚韧，活在世上已有两亿年。两亿年是什么概念？没人知道。人类的大脑容量有限，想像有限，很多问题无法解决。譬如我们无法知道宇宙多大又如何起源，无法知道恐龙如何灭绝而它的主要食物桫椤却繁衍至今。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000389": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000389",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000390": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000390",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>我知道有一种叫蕨菜的草本植物。清炒蕨菜是一道美味。我极喜欢。主要是吃的感觉不一样。因为吃蕨菜能让我想到桫椤。蕨类植物在植物王国里是较为低级的一个类群，有的能长成树，叫树蕨。桫椤又名树蕨。这种巨大的蕨类在远古时代曾遍布全球，是当时恐龙的食物之一。两亿年过去了，桫椤仍在南方各地生长，成了国宝。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000391": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000391",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000392": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000392",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>这是一个十分隐蔽的幽深山涧，一株桫椤出现在我的眼前。树干上，有枯枝垂下，显示出一种坚毅与沧桑，表面布满六角形的斑纹。株形亭亭玉立，根细长，无主根，树上不分枝杈，没有枝条。树冠如巨伞，叶形如凤尾，短的有一米，长的有三米，巨大叶子从树干上向四周伸展，远看像一把大伞，撑在地面之上；从上往下看，桫椤叶都集中在树干顶端，叶子 四散飘逸，体态优美，宛如孔雀开屏。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000393": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000393",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000394": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000394",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>沿山涧上行，不远处还有三株很小的桫椤，看样子生长得很慢。桫椤没有花，也不结果实和种子。它的叶片背面有许多孢子囊，看起来像一个个黄色小点，里面长着许多孢子，它们就是靠这些藏在叶片背面的孢子繁衍后代的。这三株小桫椤就是那棵老桫椤的孢子成熟后随风飘散，落到这里生长。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000395": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000395",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000396": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000396",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>在两亿年前恐龙生活的年代，桫椤曾遍及世界，高大而繁茂，是远古恐龙的主要食物。侏罗纪时代是桫椤最为繁茂的时期。地球十分潮湿，到处布满沼泽与河流，桫椤遮天蔽日，与大型爬行动物恐龙共同统治地球。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000397": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000397",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000398": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000398",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>尽管岁月变迁，恐龙灭绝，气候剧烈变化，桫椤仍旧在地球上一个个角落里秘密生存下来。我们进入通灵峡谷，进入了侏罗纪时代。一个时光交错的世界。我们，在瞬间来到了二亿年前。峡谷幽深。无比辽阔的天空。起伏的群山。高大的桫椤铺天盖地。还有其他的古木，生长在溪水中间。远远望去，竟是树在水中生，水在树间流的景致。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000399": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000399",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000400": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000400",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>那些古老的桫椤在这沟谷里生长。老了，就躺下，在水中长眠。桫椤木质坚硬无比，它们不会烂朽。只会长出片片的绿苔。一些桫椤的孢子落在上面，生根成长。那些根系重叠缠绕，在清凉的水里很安静，像迷人的珊瑚。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000401": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000401",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000402": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000402",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000403": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000403",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><h2><span style=\"\">第13节：青青竹叶下的山家野笋--八渡笋(1)</span></h2></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000404": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000404",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>\t</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000405": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000405",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>青青竹叶下的山家野笋--八渡笋</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000406": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000406",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000407": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000407",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>笋，竹之前身。凡产竹之地皆有食笋之风。古今皆然。笋乃春天寻常野蔬，味极鲜美。当年在如皋乡下，初春时节吃笋的情景至今不能忘怀。老宅东山墙有竹园一片。每年春雨飘过，大片竹笋破土而出。此为春笋，却少有人采挖。一棵笋就是一根竹子。竹子长成了，编成竹器，可以换钱。竹编，乡里人的主要经济来源。笋再鲜美，不忍吃。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000408": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000408",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000409": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000409",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>也有例外。那些春笋很尖。时从墙角、路边冒出。这才可以尝鲜。用手掰，啪。很脆。满满一捧回家。剥去层层笋壳，春笋细而长的玉身就暴露在眼前。最常见的吃法，笋炒鸡蛋。笋切成薄片，和鸡蛋炒。淡淡的清香。苏东坡称笋片为玉版，真是绝妙。还有别号，玉兰片。玉兰片为毛竹嫩笋加工而成，形状似玉兰花瓣。玉版，玉兰片，这些名字就能让人回味半天。一边嚼着薄薄的玉版，一边感觉春暖花开，春天的气息就这样融入身体。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000410": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000410",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000411": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000411",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>挖笋时间有讲究。最好是笋刚冒尖一两天采挖。太嫩没嚼头，口感不佳。太老也不行，难嚼，有渣。这是青竹笋，长大后的竹竿，细而长，极有韧性，是竹编的上好材料，我故乡有大量种植。现在街头有毛竹笋卖，很大很粗，也常吃，终感觉粗糙，少了春味。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000412": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000412",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000413": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000413",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>乡野时蔬中，惟笋与文人最结缘。竹笋的味道清雅隽永。千百年来关于笋的诗文墨宝有无数。细想起来，这无数诗文画稿，该是还给竹笋的一笔笔人情债吧。无论你是一介书生，还是文人画师，吃笋无数，除了写诗作文泼墨绘画，你何以报答那样的美味。我在南方，幸得口福尝过美味的八渡笋，吃得越多，越觉得要为八渡笋做点什么。秀才人情纸半张。文字虽俗，却又不敢怠慢。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000414": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000414",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000415": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000415",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>未在南方生活的人，无法想像南方草木品种之繁茂--常常令你目不暇接。许多司空见惯之草木，皆有不寻常之荣誉。荔浦的芋头是贡品。百色地区的八渡笋也是贡品。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000416": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000416",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000417": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000417",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>去南宁西北250公里，到百色市。再西北60公里，到竹笋之乡田林县。田林县西部，驮娘江畔的八渡瑶族乡，此地特产八渡笋。百色地区，有田林县，有西林县。两县之间有驮娘江相连。驮娘江势险如游龙。八渡一带，原始山岩壁立，直指苍穹。植物生长茂盛，林木苍翠，藤萝掩蔽。康熙五年，广西西林县知事王维淮过驮娘江，留下诗篇《舟过钳牙》：天数蛮荒作险阻，奇绝鬼斧兼神工。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000418": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000418",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000419": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000419",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>这是一个古老神秘的地方，四面原始森林环抱，阳光猛烈，又有云雾缭绕，树木葱茏，涧泉淙淙，堪称人间仙境。大凡深山老林总有不寻常之处。有奇花异草，更有山珍野味。这里长年气候湿润，盛产楠竹。八渡笋即生长于此。据说这种笋不论个头大小，身上都只有八个笋节，当地人便称之为八渡笋。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000420": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000420",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000421": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000421",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>第一次看见八渡笋，是在联华超市。袋装的笋丝。上面写着一行字：&quot;真的很土&quot;。广告做得很诱人。很土的东西不多了。土，是一种本真，一种真味。否则，当年进贡皇上的八渡笋如果真的很土，岂不有欺君之罪。当时见了八渡笋丝，就喜欢。笋丝蛋黄色，摸一摸，很有柔性。当即买两包八渡笋丝。回家。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000422": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000422",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000423": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000423",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000424": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000424",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><h2><span style=\"\">第14节：青青竹叶下的山家野笋--八渡笋(2)</span></h2></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000425": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000425",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>\t</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000426": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000426",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>在一个休息日，我决定亲自下厨，好好领略一下八渡笋的美味。取出笋丝，浸入水中，泡。约两个时辰，换水数次。然后置入沸水，煮。取出，仍置清水中泡，又换水数次。水清了，笋丝就算发好了。捞出笋丝。沥干的笋丝满目金黄色。如果你是第一次看到，你会误以为是百页丝（俗称千张、豆腐皮）。可以乱真。当然，同样的一盘笋丝与百页丝，笋丝的价格要贵得多。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000427": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000427",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000428": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000428",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>我精心制作了一盘笋丝炒肉。笋丝很耐炒，越炒越多，蓬蓬松松的，满满一盘，正是佐酒佳品。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000429": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000429",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000430": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000430",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>夏日。嚼着八渡贡笋，佐以冰镇漓泉啤酒，大快朵颐。八渡笋是什么滋味？除了通常感觉到的柔，易嚼，无渣，爽口的特点外，给我印象最深的是：香，糯。它不是那种清香--但可以让你触摸到山川之灵气。感觉也不是滑或脆。它让你在咀嚼时感到四野之丰盈，笋丝的柔软又恰到好处--然后让你齿颊留香，久久回味。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000431": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000431",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000432": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000432",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>果然名不虚传。吃完八渡笋，泡茶。随手翻书，真是巧，就看见一幅画--</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000433": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000433",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000434": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000434",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>雪夜，一老一少的邻居对酌到半夜，没有了下酒菜。老的说：&quot;你后园竹林子的笋怕是长出来了，拔几支，开水撩一撩，撕开。倒点酱油、麻油，多加点辣子就是菜&quot;。这幅画的作者，不是别人，乃自称&quot;湘西老刁民&quot;的黄永玉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000435": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000435",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000436": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000436",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>美食之美，首先得有意境。坐着喝酒。爱人相伴。虽无觥筹交错，但浅斟闲话之间，其乐也融融。和爱人商量好，来年春天，去百色一游。当然，田林八渡是必去的。那时，阳光爬满山野，择一家山边的小客栈，临窗小酌。窗外，高山幽篁，修竹繁茂。桌上是新剥春笋，小酒数两。同样是吃八渡笋，此等风雅闲情，就是当年皇上，亦未必能有如此的受用吧。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000437": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000437",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000438": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000438",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>现在，八渡笋已加工成很多品种。最常见的是笋丝。此外还有笋干，熏笋等。朋友送来一袋熏笋。熏笋用木炭烤干，有浓浓的烟火味。许多熏制品都有烟火味。所谓人间烟火，那是一种实在真切的日子。熏笋的好处是，可以长久地保存，不易变质。另外，那独特的烟火气息，是一味清醒剂，能让人从梦中回归到现实。本来，真实的生活，就是烟熏火燎的日子。许多浪漫的梦想，都会在寻常生活的烟熏火燎之下一天天风干，一天天远去。恍若隔世。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000439": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000439",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000440": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000440",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>我把熏笋用水浸泡，做熏笋炒腊肉。整个房间里弥漫着熏笋的烟火气息。日子变得悠远而漫长。不管怎样，这样的日子充满温馨，淡淡的。所谓生活，不正是这样的么。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000441": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000441",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000442": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000442",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>但我总是想到故乡。那片竹园还在吗。在的。春雨敲击竹园，笋尖的梦想，开始伸向四面八方。我能听见东山墙边的竹笋正在拔节，拱得泥土嘎吱嘎吱响呢。尖尖笋芽，执著地向上挺立。她们多快乐--正裹着枯黄色的笋壳，跳草裙舞。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000443": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000443",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000444": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000444",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>32</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000445": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000445",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000446": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000446",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000447": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000447",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><h2><span style=\"\">第15节：隐藏窑火，月照静眠的冬日山乡--苦丁茶</span></h2></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000448": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000448",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>\t</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000449": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000449",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>隐藏窑火，月照静眠的冬日山乡--苦丁茶</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000450": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000450",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000451": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000451",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>就文字而言，我一直推崇鲁迅，他的小说散文，百读不厌。也读苦雨斋。很久以前读过厚厚的《苦茶》，后来才知道，这书名原是出版社用来糊弄人的。正确的书名是《知堂回想录》。知堂的文字很多，追随者也众，知堂热一波一波。我记住的，有《乌篷船》、《故乡的野菜》几篇。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000452": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000452",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000453": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000453",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>&quot;在这样的时候，常引起一种空想，觉得如在江村小屋里，靠玻璃窗，烘着白炭火钵，喝清茶，同友人谈闲话，那是颇愉快地事。&quot;这是喝清茶。心境是闲的，与治国平天下无关。后来，苦茶庵取代了苦雨斋。苦茶，一种凄凉而又无奈的人生况味。很多人说到知堂，总想到苦茶二字，以为知堂喜欢苦茶，其实不是。知堂在《关于苦茶》中说：&quot;一位友人因为记起吃苦茶的那句话，顺便买了一包特种的茶叶拿来送我，这是我很熟的一个朋友，我感谢他的好意，可是这茶实在太苦，我终于没有能够多吃。&quot;</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000454": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000454",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000455": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000455",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>知堂说的是苦丁茶。北方少有人喝苦丁茶的。味太苦，不习惯。苦丁茶有清热去火的作用，南方人多有饮用。南方水土性温，四季湿热，水果吸足了炙热的阳光，品种又多，常吃容易上火。照中医的理论，清火的最好办法，就是苦味。在南方，苦味很多。苦瓜，苦丁茶，苦麻菜，苦菊等。还有王老吉，也苦得要命。我来南方之后，陆续尝到这些苦味。第一个就是苦丁茶。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000456": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000456",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000457": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000457",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>来南方时，正是夏天。大量水果上市。其中鲜荔枝，两三元一斤，都是名品。什么妃子笑，挂绿，糯米糍等，挂满果市。荔枝上有很长的枝和鲜绿的叶，证明荔枝刚摘下不久。想想千年前的美人吃荔枝那么费劲，不由生出一种优越感--买她十来斤。回家猛吃。日啖荔枝三百颗。我才吃了三十颗，第二天就上火了。口内溃疡。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000458": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000458",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000459": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000459",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>爱人找来苦丁茶。说去内火。这是我第一次喝苦丁茶。一根根，墨绿色，卷得比牙签略大些。倒也整齐。茶泡好，叶子展开，水色清碧，深深的样子，因听人说过味极苦，一时竟不敢品饮，只静静望着，如临深潭。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000460": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000460",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000461": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000461",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>终于我还是想尝她一尝。轻碰杯沿，啜一小口，舌尖与整个口腔中突然有一种似曾相识的浓烈弥散着，仿佛在这浓烈的夏季感到一股冰凉袭来。这不是传说中的苦涩，而是冰凉，直抵心间。连头发也竖起来。苦也。但我默默地承受着。任丝丝苦味涌向周身每个毛孔。我甚至想，会不会有泪涌出。但没有。只有这时才知道，这苦味在很久之前已经领略。曾经很多。我只有不断地咽下去。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000462": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000462",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000463": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000463",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>后来我在大新县的一个茶庄里喝了名扬天下的万承苦丁茶。2007年的5月长假，我们三人去了靖西。回来时路过大新县。大新地处桂西南边陲，与越南毗连。我很喜欢这个地方。我们沿中越界河归春河行走了很长时间。很难想像这里就是国界--我宁愿想像成在村庄里行走，归春河不过是村边的一条小溪。山清水秀。我们又去看了德天跨国瀑布，看了清代设立的中越53号国界碑--我还是无法把两个国家分开--只有在这里才明白国与国之间原来是这样的纠缠不清。这里是一片植物王国，景致疏朗，一片明媚的异域风光。好山好水出好茶。著名的大新苦丁茶就产于此地。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000464": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000464",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000465": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000465",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>大新原名万承县。万承苦丁茶是广西传统名茶之一，很多资料记载，万承苦丁茶历来是贡品。产于万承县苦丁乡，现在的地理位置在大新龙门乡苦丁村。旧本《辞海》曾有记载：&quot;苦丁茶者，广西特产名茶也，产于万承县苦丁乡，故称万承苦丁茶。&quot;苦丁村位于大新县的小明山深处，已有千年历史。原名皋屯，因苦丁茶出名，久之，易名苦丁村。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000466": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000466",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000467": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000467",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>苦丁村原有苦丁茶母树六棵，现遗存五棵，最大的一棵被誉为茶王，２００年以上的树龄，是广西最大、最老的苦丁茶树，枝叶苍翠，树干通直，四季常青。枝稍顶芽采摘后，易萌发新芽，茶叶产量较高。一棵茶树每年都有万元收入。当春茶上市，各方客商不远千里慕名而来，门庭若市。秋季，茶果成熟，一片鲜红色，绿叶丛中点点红，令人赏心悦目。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000468": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000468",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000469": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000469",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>很多人都喜欢喝苦丁茶。那样的苦味也有人喝？有的。不是因为喜欢，而是为健康。苦丁茶的神奇功效，古书上早有记载。唐代名医陈藏器在《本草拾遗》里说：&quot;久食令人瘦，去人脂&quot;。真是踏破铁鞋无觅处。瘦身，减肥，古人早就有了秘方。这条记载，对于现代人而言，是多么令人兴奋的发现。李时珍在《本草纲目》中说得更详细：叶气味苦、平、无毒。煮饮，止渴、明目、除烦、消痰利水，通小肠，治淋，止头痛、烦热，噙咽，清上膈，利咽喉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000470": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000470",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000471": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000471",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>但是，喝苦丁茶仅仅是为了健康吗。也不是。取一白瓷碗，泡一两枚苦丁茶。片刻，即有如烟如丝的黄色汁液在水中浮游。卷叶次第舒展，叶色由墨绿转还为清绿。慢慢品饮，个中甘苦滋味，会让你久久地悬想半天。只有这时才可感觉，苦茶的味道，原来与人生的种种况味有着多么的相似。人生如茶，沥尽苦涩，始得清淡。清淡是一种境界。非历经苦涩不能达到。譬如苦茶庵。我曾看见一张照片。上面是知堂和一个小女孩，在苦茶庵前蹲着，是很慈祥很温暖的一幕。可是，他内心复杂的感情，自嘲，悲哀，叹息，挣扎种种，又有谁能说得清。那种苦茶心境，现在又有几人理解。苦茶庵终于作古。苦茶庵因城市改造已不复存在。这使后人读苦茶庵时，又多了一味苦涩。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000472": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000472",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000473": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000473",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>来南方已有一年时间。我每日喝着从大新带回来的苦丁茶。想着以前的人生与以后的日子。现在，我安静地坐在这里，静静地写作。我努力回味这一年来在南方的种种感受。心中充满感激。口中的涩苦，早已荡然无存。只觉口舌生津，那一脉苦味化着丝丝甘甜周身弥漫。这样想着，眼里竟有些许湿润。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000474": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000474",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000475": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000475",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000476": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000476",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><h2><span style=\"\">第16节：山花摇落一溪香--百香果(1)</span></h2></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000477": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000477",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>\t</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000478": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000478",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>山花摇落一溪香--百香果</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000479": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000479",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000480": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000480",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>我对百香果一无所知。其实很多时候面对南方茂盛的奇花异草，我像刘姥姥进大观园。我看到那个女子。在桃源。路边一棵榕树下。我放慢脚步对她凝望，没惊动她。我像个偷窥者，站在不远处，另一棵榕树下。我仿佛看见梦中出现了无数次的湄公河和水边女人。湄公河流域不总是热带的丛林。譬如流经的越南。沿河两岸还有金色的稻田，头戴尖顶斗笠的越南妇女，到处都是她们忙碌的身影。听说，在越南农村，男人在家烧饭做菜，妇女在田间做活。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000481": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000481",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000482": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000482",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>她的出现，让我想到湄公河的女子。南方气温高，紫外线强，爱美的女性总怕晒黑。她的手上还拿着斗笠。我看见了她明媚的眼睛。还有&quot;越南髻&quot;--她的长发很随意，用夹子一夹，这就是传说中的越南髻。说是自然随意，却又不潦草，很有女人味。桃源路是个繁华街道，路边长着扁桃树。她静静地坐在树阴下。南方山川秀丽，气候热烈，生活在这里的女子总让人对南方这片阳光的土地产生一种敞开的诗意和视野。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000483": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000483",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000484": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000484",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>你是越南人吗？我问她。她笑笑说是钦州人。她有着南方女子特有的清秀之美。南方女子之美，有时并非来自她们饱满的胸脯、纤细的腰肢、或修长的大腿。她们的真正魅力，在于她们娴静安详的性格、欲语还休的眼神，还有回眸时掠过的微微颤动的伤感。她问我，你买果子么。我这才看见她的编织篮里的水果。我不认识，问她这是什么果子。她说，百香果。我说果有百香吗。她说，你闻闻就知道了。她说话的时候，那些树叶的阴影像忧郁的时光在她的脸上飘忽不定。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000485": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000485",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000486": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000486",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>对于闻所未闻的南方水果我见识得不算少。很多果实不知道名字，不知道如何吃法。她们的每次出现总让我充满惊艳之感，却又束手无策。或奇特，或芳香，或鲜亮，充满诱惑。这个钦州女子所说的百香果，我是第一次见。岂止是我。很多人都没有见过。行人来到她的面前，总会驻足观望片刻，看这稀罕之果。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000487": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000487",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000488": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000488",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>百香果的形状并不特别，鹅蛋那么大，外表平滑整齐，颜色紫红，深紫浅紫都有，并不很均匀，上面布满细碎白点。摸之，稍硬。轻闻，真是奇了，一下子涌出许多种水果的香味。我将百香果放在鼻下，细细辨别。香蕉。菠萝。柠檬。草莓。番石榴。各种味都有。刚闻着像草莓，番石榴的香味又飘来。几种味让你产生梦幻。好像是某种果味，再闻，又不是，飘忽，捉摸不定。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000489": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000489",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000490": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000490",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000491": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000491",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><h2><span style=\"\">第17节：山花摇落一溪香--百香果(2)</span></h2></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000492": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000492",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>\t</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000493": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000493",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>我问，这百香果好吃吗。她说，很好吃的。说着，她握着一个百香果，看了一下，用双手捏，裂开一道口，撕开，露出果肉。她把撕开的两半百香果递给我，说你尝尝。两半百香果毫无保留地把全部内心袒露在我的眼前。厚厚的果壳，盛着黄黄的果汁，像蛋黄那样的颜色。还有籽，黑色，裹着一层透明的果肉，像石榴籽那样。我拿着两半百香果，犹豫半天，不知怎么吃。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000494": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000494",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000495": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000495",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>这是我家里种的百香果。钦州女子说，早上刚摘下的。当地的价太便宜，就来这里了。我问多少钱一斤。说五元。我问，从钦州到这里，果不会变质吗。说不会的，鲜果极耐贮运，可放１－３个月不变质，长途运输都不必保鲜。问是树上长的吗。说不是，是藤，像葡萄一样的果藤，搭棚，春种夏收，年收两批。这种果产量高，棚上密密麻麻都挂满了。春暖花开，夏秋收获。百香果从七月起开始收果，即使在寒冬的日子里，也能挂果累累。我想像着在一个初夏，一个大风骤起的黄昏，成熟的百香果密密挂满果棚，噼噼啪啪落下来。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000496": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000496",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000497": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000497",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>我问味道怎么样。她说，你尝一下就知道了。我将手上的百香果黄黄的果汁连同黑籽吃进嘴里。一阵的酸甜飘过齿间，接着各种果味在嘴里弥漫。她说，籽是可以吃的。我嚼着百香果的籽，很脆，连同果汁咽下。霎时间，百香果，百般滋味涌在心头。春花开了，千百种野花在体内盛放。一种艳丽的果实，像怀春的浅褐色女人一样饱满。湄公河。水边浣衣女子。河边打草的老者。挂满藤架的百香果。一派山野田园风光。这一切都在炽热的南方。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000498": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000498",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000499": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000499",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>这样的美果当然不能不买。买两斤吧。钦州女人就用秤称两斤。递给我。我掏出十元钱给她。我伸出的手悬在那里--只眨眼工夫，钦州女人不见了。我看见城管的车停在街边。戴大檐帽的城管赶鸭子似的追着几个小贩。其中有那个钦州女子的身影--她吃力地挑着编织篮，像受惊的小兔，步伐零乱，消失在小巷深处。这突如其来的一幕让我不知所措。我手上拎着两斤百香果站在那里发呆。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000500": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000500",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000501": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000501",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>一种无言的恼怒在心中滋长--有人破坏了我的心情。是的，一种美好的情愫在霎时间被冲击得荡然无存，而我又不知去找谁。那个湄公河的女子，奇异的百香果，美丽的桃源路，像梦幻一样从我眼前消失。我站在原地等了很长时间。那个钦州女子一定会来的。但没有。我不知道她去了哪儿。是不是百香果被没收了。很久，她都没有来。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000502": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000502",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000503": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000503",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>桃源路依旧整洁漂亮，几乎看不到街边有小贩--这个城市管理得很好。我经常往来于桃源路。桃源路拐个弯就是双拥路了。这里高楼林立，是个繁华所在。树荫下有许多行人，大家步履匆匆，都在为生活奔波。我也是。只是，树荫下，那个钦州女子，再也没有出现过，直到当我不得不离开的时候。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000504": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000504",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000505": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000505",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>我没有吃那百香果。我略数数，竟有二十来个。我不时放到鼻下闻一闻。两斤百香果长时间放着，室内有奇异的果香。我不忍吃的原因是因为一种落寞--有什么东西不见了。那个画面仍然很清晰：湄公河，一袭白裙的女子，黑发，倒影，她的身边，摆放着一篮篮紫色的百香果。在淡淡的回忆中总是抹不去一缕心情--也许这就是我遗失的东西。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000506": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000506",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000507": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000507",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000508": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000508",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><h2><span style=\"\">第18节：一个深山峡谷的秘密--咬人树</span></h2></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000509": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000509",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>\t</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000510": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000510",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>一个深山峡谷的秘密--咬人树</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000511": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000511",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000512": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000512",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>很久以前，听说过一种植物，叫食人树。有关食人树的说法有几起。如，有人目睹一棵巨型开花植物将一名年轻女子消化掉。地点在马达加斯加。又有一个食人树的故事，发生在菲律宾棉兰老岛。有人声称，他在漫步时走入岛上禁区，一棵食人树伸展开，叶子发出嘶嘶声。后来向导及时赶到，把他推开，远离了那些可能致命的叶子。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000513": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000513",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000514": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000514",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>这些奇闻，总让我想起《西游记》。木仙庵三藏谈诗。唐三藏在荆棘岭上遇到几个树精藤怪。这几位树精都有上千年的修行功夫，能吟诗作对。偶听唐僧月下吟诗，定要与他切磋。谈着谈着，竟要好事成双，将杏仙妹妹与唐僧成亲。清风朗月之下，也算是美事一桩。直到悟空断喝一声，才把那些树精藤怪们吓退。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000515": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000515",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000516": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000516",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>看到这里，我对孙猴子是有意见的。干吗呢。那些树精藤怪与其他妖怪不一样，虽非人类，但并非恶类，也没看出他们要吃唐僧肉的企图。孙猴子此时的一声断喝，真是最不懂性情，最煞风景，最无趣了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000517": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000517",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000518": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000518",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>据说，还有一种叫奠柏的食人树。生长在印尼爪哇岛，是世上最凶猛的食人树。这种树长着许多柔软的枝条，如果人不小心触到树，那些枝条马上就像乌贼的卷须一样把人卷住，且越卷越紧，脱不了身。这时树会分泌一种液汁，人粘着就慢慢被消化掉。当地人已掌握了它的脾气，用小动物去喂它。等它吃饱，懒得动了，就赶快去采集它的树汁。树液是制药的原料。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000519": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000519",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000520": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000520",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>无论是传说还是神话，我都认为不是偶然的，总有某种现象客观存在。对于自然界那些诸如UFO之类，我信以为然。人类大脑想像力毕竟有限。和浩瀚无边的宇宙相比，这些所谓的食人树之类植物，实不足为奇。树精藤怪诸多异事发生的背景，总是在深山老林。那些杳无人迹的原始深林里，无数植物生存至今，不是一件寻常事。有的植物已知道如何保护自己，如何生存下去。譬如，我曾在深山见过一种野枣树。那是一种低矮灌木。野枣树上密密麻麻布满了刺，任何人用手摘枣，都会被刺伤--这些刺在保护野枣成熟。野枣没有成熟时，要靠刺来保护。野枣成熟了，才落在地上。这样，它们才一代代延续至今。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000521": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000521",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000522": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000522",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>我没见过食人树。但我见过咬人树。在靖西通灵大峡谷的原始地带，生长着一种让人畏惧的植物。进入峡谷之前，导游再三提醒我们不可随便触摸沿路植物。这里的植物，有的是上亿年的品种，很多都是侏罗纪时代的植物。进化至今，其中有些甚至会咬人。植物咬人，总是一件新鲜事。一路上，看到许多警示牌，上面画的是禁止手摸。大家变得规矩多了。通灵大峡谷绝大多数植物，我们没有见过，谁也不知哪种植物会随时伸过来咬上一口。大家左顾右盼，又希望能看到那种神奇的植物在眼前出现。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000523": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000523",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000524": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000524",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>峡谷幽深。沿途泉水涓涓倾出，尝之，味甘。山侧多凤尾葵，风兰，轴轮葵，桄榔树，板蓝根，鸟巢兰之类，远近随风，处处芬馥，如入百草园。越往前行，景致越深。两侧绝壁千丈，林木高茂。类于《西游记》中的荆棘岭。导游说，很多年前，通灵峡谷曾有蛇树的传说。蛇树，高大挺拔，像木菠萝，树干筒状，它的枝条垂下来，能像蛇一样捕捉动物，如果动物被它碰到，树枝就会把猎物紧紧缠绕，枝上有许多细小的刺，刺入猎物的身体，然后从树枝上分泌出一种液体，把猎物牢牢粘住，直到猎物腐烂为止，此树就是靠这种方法来获取肥料生存。但这种蛇树又是一种不可多得的珍贵药材，据说有起死回生之功效，且十分灵验。于是很多人冒着生命的危险，前来砍伐。最终导致绝种。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000525": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000525",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000526": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000526",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>听了导游的解说，虽为咬人树的灭绝遗憾，但仍感后背发凉。大家目光四处逡巡，总感到那些茂林深处会随时伸出一根恐怖的藤，像蛇一样游来。越前行，林木萧森。泉声夹道，怪石奇花，不可胜数。更有独木成林的奇观。浓密的绿色之中，各类珍禽异兽繁衍生息。峡谷间绝壁千仞，巨型钟乳高悬，溪涧、洞穴、深潭、飞瀑比比皆是。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000527": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000527",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000528": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000528",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>蓦然间，一块写有咬人树的木牌出现在眼前，大家屏住呼吸，心情异常紧张。终于见到了传说已久的植物。大家睁大眼睛，陌生地，谨慎地看着这棵神奇的植物。咬人树的叶子非常像广玉兰，树叶宽厚，叶面对称。树叶上有密密麻麻的细绒毛，这种细绒毛就是树的嘴巴，牙齿，很尖利，一旦碰到人的皮肤，会使皮肤变红，疼痛难忍，两天后成为一条伤痕，伤痕红肿，半月方愈。若用药物治疗，也需一周。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000529": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000529",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000530": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000530",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>尽管如此，导游还是鼓动大家试一试。她说不必担心被咬。就是被咬，也没有生命危险。如哪位勇敢，可以用手背让它咬一咬，试一试被咬的感觉，留下伤痕作个纪念，让你们一辈子记得美丽的靖西。鼓吹半天，没人响应。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000531": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000531",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000532": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000532",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>通灵大峡谷中的咬人树，已确认是我国目前稀有的优质野生漆树。所谓咬人，实是皮肤过敏。它的叶子能分泌一种刺激性的物质，当人或其他动物触碰到它，它尖利的刺毛，就会刺入人或动物的皮肤，使之过敏，疼痛难忍。但是，据当地百姓说，如果在春天，咬人树枝端萌发出一蔟蔟绿里透红的嫩芽，是可以采食的，其味极似香椿，可戴手套采摘炒食，有以毒攻毒的奇效--整个夏天都能百毒不侵。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000533": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000533",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000534": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000534",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>传说归传说。类似吃河豚鱼的心情。味再鲜美，谁也不会轻易去尝那样的嫩芽。这样也好，咬人树可以尽情生长了。离开咬人树，踏着青幽的石径继续前行。满眼的深绿浅翠。通灵大峡谷就是一个梦，寂寥无声。只有隐隐远去的轰鸣瀑布，才让我们从梦中回到现实。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000535": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000535",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000536": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000536",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>卷二</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000537": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000537",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000538": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000538",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000539": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000539",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><h2><span style=\"\">第19节：隔河相望，你依然残忍而美丽--烟草(1)</span></h2></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000540": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000540",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>\t</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000541": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000541",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>隔河相望，你依然残忍而美丽--烟草</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000542": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000542",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000543": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000543",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>去靖西。路上可见成片成片的烟草正茂盛地生长。我和向导坐在车子最前面。一眼望去，大片的嫩绿一直绵延到远处山坡。我不知道是烟草，以为是玉米，像极了。我说，这里的玉米长得这么壮。向导说，是烟草。我仔细看，才明白自己看错。叶子肥大，粉红花开在顶上。烟草是第一次见到。不由多了几分认真与新奇。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000544": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000544",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000545": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000545",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>但我很小时候看过烟叶丝。祖父抽水烟就用烟叶丝。那时还在苏北乡下。祖父手里常捧着水烟台。水烟台是个很奇妙的东西，即使是现在想起来也是。结构也巧妙。铜质，有烟嘴，烟管，烟筒。烟台里装水，用来过滤烟油。每吸一口，就能听到水烟台咕噜咕噜的响声。吸完一口，拔出烟嘴，吹掉烟灰，再从烟筒里把烟丝装到烟嘴上，再吸。这过程，在我童年记忆中，再熟悉不过。祖父身上的烟草气息，我一辈子都能记得。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000546": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000546",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000547": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000547",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>烟丝是很香的。曾有好几次，我轻轻揉开香烟的卷纸，看里面金黄色的烟丝，再放到鼻下闻。那烟丝味很香，很好闻。现在回想我那时的表情，一定是很陶醉的样子。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000548": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000548",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000549": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000549",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>始终没有机会看到烟草生长，不知道烟草是一种怎样的植物，总想一见。现在，如愿以偿。向导告诉我，靖西气候与土壤，最适宜烟草生长。烟香飘逸，香气量、质均较好，刺激较小。靖西是壮乡最大的烟叶基地。向导说，这里是&quot;真龙&quot;的故乡。原来，我满街看到的&quot;真龙&quot;卷烟，原料来自这里。真龙是名牌，我没尝试过。满街都是它的形象广告，一看就知道这家烟厂的实力雄厚。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000550": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000550",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000551": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000551",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>我们的车子在靖西5万亩的优质烟草基地里穿行。烟草是相当漂亮的一种植物。种植很整齐，一亩亩，一陇陇。尤其是她的叶子，很可爱，丰满优美，远远望去，像女子的绿裙，裙摆在风中翻飞。顶端开着花，长型，一朵朵，白里透红，像喇叭花，每一株有几十朵吧。很奇妙的是，我们在成片的烟草里行驶，空气里就有了某种青涩味，不用说，那是烟草的青春气息了。长时间在烟叶里行走，不知会不会被烟叶熏醉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000552": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000552",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000553": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000553",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000554": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000554",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><h2><span style=\"\">第20节：隔河相望，你依然残忍而美丽--烟草(2)</span></h2></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000555": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000555",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>\t</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000556": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000556",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>许多烟农在田间忙碌。锄草，培土，施肥。烟草长到一定程度，要把顶部掐掉，把靠近地面发黄的叶子剪掉。这样，营养就会全部输送到剩下的几片叶子上。目之所及，那遍野的烟草，在阳光沐浴下，蓬蓬勃勃。宽大而深绿的叶子，映着阳光，泛起油油的光泽。看着让人喜欢。叶子渐渐生长，变得丰盈。叶子颜色由绿色转为黄绿色，叶脉变白，发亮，叶片下垂，自然弯曲，成弓形，叶边下卷，看起来黄灿灿，亮堂堂。此时便可采收。记得有一种香烟的牌子，叫黄金叶，多好听的名字。想想这名字就能闻见烟草的香味。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000557": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000557",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000558": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000558",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>向导是土生土长的靖西人。说自家种植了6亩烤烟。据他介绍，采收烟叶的时间很有讲究。宜在早上和上午进行，以利对烟草的成熟度识别。旱天采露水烟叶。以利保湿变黄。烟叶成熟，若遇降雨，可在雨后采收，以防返青。若降雨时间较长并出现了返青烟，可等其重新落黄后再行采收。质量好的烟叶，可以卖到每斤6元的价格。这样计算，向导一家六亩地烟叶收入约有15000元。加上产前投入、烤房、煤炭等补助约3700元，减去物资、烤烟用煤等费用约6000元，种植6亩烤烟纯收入约为13000元。靖西百姓的日子，好过多了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000559": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000559",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000560": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000560",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>田间获得的优质叶片，需要精心烤制，才可生产出色香味俱佳的优质烤烟。我看到烟草的田埂上，有许多很奇怪的建筑，两层楼，还有烟囱。有的是单独一幢，有的几座连在一起。向导说，那是烟叶的烤房。烟叶收割后，要烘烤才能卖。烟的质量好坏，手感如何，浓烈与否，除了取决烟叶生长的质量，更重要的是看烤烟的功夫。这些相配套的烤烟房，也成为引人注目的建筑群。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000561": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000561",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000562": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000562",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>旅行车途中停下。我走到田间，摘了一片烟叶。碧绿的，很宽大的叶子。放到鼻下闻，有一丝苦涩味。端详良久，我决定收藏这片烟叶。我把这片烟叶夹入书中。后来去德天，就忘了。回后来才发现，书本中藏着靖西烟叶。软软的，黄了。我把这片烟叶卷起来，用线扎好，放在窗台上晒。南方阳光很烈。几个日头晒过，烟叶干透了，成黄褐色，这是我的&quot;秘制雪茄&quot;。再闻，带着浓浓的烟草味。决定尝一尝。点火。吸。美丽的靖西像浓烈的情人一下子融入我的体内。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000563": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000563",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000564": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000564",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>我抽着&quot;秘制雪茄&quot;，读《烟草和魔鬼》。芥川龙之介与茨威格、陀思妥耶夫斯基都是天才人物，是我最心仪的三位艺术大师。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000565": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000565",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000566": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000566",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>&quot;后来这植物茎部的顶端开了一簇簇的花儿，是漏斗形的淡紫色的花。魔鬼大概因为辛勤劳动过一场，花儿开了，感到颇为高兴。早祷和晚祷后，它就到田里来不遗余力地侍弄。&quot;</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000567": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000567",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000568": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000568",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>芥川的《烟草和魔鬼》是一篇类似于民间传说的作品。一养牛者，与种植某种植物的魔鬼打赌，赌注是肉体和灵魂，猜那植物叫什么。养牛者猜不出，又不甘把肉体和灵魂交给魔鬼。遂牵牛在园中遛跶。心出一计。把黄牛的缰绳解下，照着牛屁股猛打，把它赶进园子里。牛撞毁了篱笆，把个园子践踏得稀烂。魔鬼一看，说：&quot;这畜生，干吗踩我的烟草园子！&quot;</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000569": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000569",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000570": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000570",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>答案就这样出来了。牛者赢得整个庄园的烟草。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000571": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000571",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000572": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000572",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>人类赢了烟草又怎样。当人类自以为赢了的时候，说不定已经落入了圈套呢。谁知道烟草是不是魔鬼对人类的圈套。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000573": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000573",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000574": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000574",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000575": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000575",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><h2><span style=\"\">第21节：月白风清，在南方山野里的低吟浅唱--甘蔗(1)</span></h2></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000576": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000576",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>\t</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000577": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000577",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>月白风清，在南方山野里的低吟浅唱--甘蔗</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000578": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000578",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000579": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000579",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>我写过《青纱帐》。青纱帐是我的童年。来南方，看到甘蔗林。第一次看到漫山遍野的甘蔗林，让我想起北方的青纱帐。青纱帐在平原，玉米地，高粱地都是，远远望去，满眼深绿。青纱帐深不可测，隐隐约约的，埋伏一样。甘蔗林是一片一片的浅绿色，多在丘陵地带，背景有香蕉林，有青山。阳光照下来，一片明朗，总让人感觉天那么遥远，不能抵达。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000580": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000580",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000581": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000581",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>早年，北方人不大容易吃到甘蔗。与流通不畅有关。至少，在我苏北故乡就吃不到。可以吃玉米秆。玉米快要成熟时，秸秆也甜，可以当甘蔗吃。那要付出代价。不是每根玉米秆都保证甜，常常是，尝了很多，竟没有一根是甜的。玉米秆掰下来，挂在秆上的玉米，就没有用了，浆没灌足，只好自己啃。现在想起来，那应该是很好很好的一种营养品。好是好，就是不甜。还有青涩味，没人喜欢吃。那时更渴望能吃到甜甜的玉米秆。于是我体内常常灌足了那样乏味的营养品。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000582": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000582",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000583": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000583",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>除了玉米秆，故乡还有一种叫芦稷的植物，现在想起来，那植物与高粱相似。其秆很甜，只是比玉米秆细小。此种植物的皮很锋利，容易划伤嘴唇。产量低，种植不多，偶尔看见河边斜坡上有种植，也都不敢随便吃，在远处有人看着。不常吃到。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000584": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000584",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000585": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000585",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>到南方来一年有余。面对遥远的山冈，满是甘蔗林和野花的香气。由</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000586": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000586",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000587": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000587",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>青纱帐到甘蔗林，渐入佳境。渐入佳境不是我说的，是顾恺之。这个成语太熟了。甘蔗。东晋。顾恺之。这三个词放在一起就有故事。中国史上，魏晋时代是个另类。放荡不羁，天马行空，我行我素。顾恺之也没例外。倒啖甘蔗，传为千古佳话。《晋书·顾恺之传》记载：&quot;恺之每食甘蔗，恒自尾至本，人或怪之。云：渐入佳境。&quot;</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000588": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000588",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000589": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000589",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>吃甘蔗倒着吃。从梢部往根部吃，越吃越甜。吃甘蔗吃出灵感，吃出佳境来，无疑是高人。倒啖甘蔗的本质，是与众不同。一个成功的画家，必须要有鲜明的个性，不模仿别人，要时刻想到与众不同。顾恺之深得倒啖甘蔗之意味。他的人物画无不精妙，皆有点睛之笔。透过《女史箴图》，可领略顾恺之的画风。人物线条柔软而缠绵，像蚕丝一样细密流畅。后人沿袭了这种娴静的线条风格，线条上不再赋加色彩，使之独立成为画种，谓之白描。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000590": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000590",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000591": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000591",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>写《南方草木札记》，读得最多的，自然是《南方草木状》。内容虽简略，却都是些活化石的材料。《南方草木状》，东晋初年，广州刺史稽含所著。其中所列的食用植物就有甘蔗。《齐民要术》说：&quot;甘蔗，远近皆有。交趾所产甘蔗特醇好，本末无厚薄，其味至均。围数寸，长丈余，颇似竹。斩而食之，既甘；迮取汁为饴饧，名之曰糖，益复珍也。又煎而嚗之，既凝，如冰，破如博棋，食之，入口消释，时人谓之石蜜。&quot;可见在当时，岭南广大地区，甘蔗已经是一种很有名的经济作物了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000592": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000592",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000593": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000593",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>在此之前，三国时代，甘蔗已有生长。曹丕能文能武，写得一手好诗，撰有《典论·论文》。他的武功也不错，从小骑马、射箭，功夫了得。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000594": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000594",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000595": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000595",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>一天，和一个叫邓展的将军讨论剑术。邓展说，你说得头头是道，到底有没有真功夫呢。曹丕说那我们来比试。曹丕顺手抓一根甘蔗扔过去，然后自己也抓一根。这是一种棍术的交流。啪啪几下，把邓展打倒。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000596": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000596",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000597": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000597",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>北方街头所卖甘蔗，粗，节短，皮色多深紫，或青皮。斩头去尾，论根卖。也有论斤卖。很少有人见过甘蔗如何生长。吃甘蔗多在冬天。记得每每春节，大过年的，街头一下子冒出许多卖甘蔗的小贩。居然生意兴隆。蔗摊周围皮屑满地，一片狼藉。削甘蔗似乎有专用刨刀。刷刷几下，皮削尽，露出晶莹的杆，剁成几节。边走边嚼，也是风景。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000598": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000598",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000599": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000599",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000600": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000600",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><h2><span style=\"\">第22节：月白风清，在南方山野里的低吟浅唱--甘蔗(2)</span></h2></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000601": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000601",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>\t</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000602": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000602",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>邕城街头，有很多榨汁机，专榨甘蔗汁，再经过冰冻，一定是很可口的饮品。但我一次也没尝过。吃甘蔗，如果没有咬，没有啖，没有嚼的过程，那与囫囵吞枣无异。我是坚决不买那种榨汁喝的。很多时候，我宁愿去买一根蔗，把皮削去，一口一口啖，啖出甜味来，那是真的甜，是甘蔗给予人类最原始的意味。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000603": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000603",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000604": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000604",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>但是，蔗皮是要刨去的。否则容易划伤嘴，也不卫生，蔗皮上细菌很多。有时我会驻足观望，看一些小女生围着蔗摊，叽叽喳喳吃甘蔗。吃甘蔗是个很奇怪的动作。女孩子们平时优雅矜持，很淑女，但吃甘蔗，却旁若无人，面部表情极丰富，龇牙裂嘴，嚼完之后又吐出，全然没有淑女的样子。但她们啖得痛快，是那种随心所欲的自由与享受，不是淑女们所能体味到的。每每路过蔗摊，我会停下，买上一根，或者看那些女生在摊边大嚼甘蔗的模样。风前横笛斜吹雨。小红低唱我吹箫。几个女生堆在一起吃甘蔗，浑然一幕竹箫的专场。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000605": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000605",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000606": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000606",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>南方几乎没有冬天。甘蔗林，香蕉林，无数的青竹，繁茂密集。那些杂树，交错纠缠。大片阳光，浮在枝叶上面。漫山遍野的甘蔗，最后都去了糖厂。后来才知道，更多的甘蔗，融入了千家万户。丁亥春节，我在南方邕城。南方人过春节，有一习俗，喜欢买一捆甘蔗放在家里。寓意不言而明。一家人吃完年夜饭，团团围坐，一边嚼着甜蜜的甘蔗，一边祈祷来  年全家甜甜蜜蜜，日子像甘蔗一样，节节向上。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000607": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000607",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000608": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000608",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>甘蔗削好了，可以放在冰箱里冷藏，这是我读余光中后的一个发现。想来，那样的冰镇甘蔗，一定是晶莹透亮的，嚼起来一定是清脆的感觉，别有风味。但我一直没有尝试过。余光中写了一组水果诗。台湾盛产各种水果。诗人饕餮之余，常有吟咏。甘蔗不是水果，但余光中写了《埔里甘蔗》。本来就喜欢余光中。读这一首，真有啖得痛快之感：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000609": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000609",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000610": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000610",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>无论是倒啖或者顺吃</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000611": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000611",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000612": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000612",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>每一口都是口福</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000613": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000613",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000614": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000614",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>第一口就咬入了佳境</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000615": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000615",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000616": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000616",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>却笑东晋的名士</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000617": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000617",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000618": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000618",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>嚼来还是太拘谨</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000619": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000619",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000620": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000620",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>而真要啖得痛快</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000621": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000621",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000622": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000622",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>就务必冰得彻底……</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000623": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000623",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000624": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000624",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>--余光中《埔里甘蔗》</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000625": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000625",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000626": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000626",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>按照余光中的意思，吃甘蔗，不必像顾恺之那样倒啖，因为每一口，都能咬出佳境，如一股股甘洌的清泉，浇遍肺腑。诗人啖得痛快。冰箱里的冰镇甘蔗会吃完吗。不会的。吃完最后一支，还有一千支，一万支在等着他。毕竟是大诗人，情之豪迈，令人想起李白。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000627": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000627",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000628": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000628",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000629": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000629",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><h2><span style=\"\">第23节：在阳光下赤脚而行--罗汉果</span></h2></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000630": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000630",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>\t</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000631": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000631",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>在阳光下赤脚而行--罗汉果 </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000632": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000632",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000633": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000633",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>我在桂东北山区转了很长时间。到过最边远的一些山寨。譬如恭城县。我到过恭城县的观音乡，很僻，在与湖南省交界处。在这些地方，我搜集了不少瑶族的民俗资料。后来，我又来到永福。来永福之前，我就知道永福的罗汉果。实际上，罗汉果与佛教无关。如果硬要扯上一点关系，那就是神果。罗汉果在瑶族人心目中，被誉为长寿果，仙果。这是一味神奇的止咳良药。我在永福，看到了罗汉果的藤萝，棚棚架架，果子挂满了，像无数垂下的青气球。除了药用功效，我还知道，挂满藤萝的罗汉果，很好看。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000634": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000634",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000635": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000635",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>由于种种原因，瑶族医药没有专门的典著。瑶族的灵香草，曾载入李时珍的《本草纲目》。但不知为何，罗汉果作为一味神奇的良药，遍查历代本草均无记载。李时针的《本草纲目》里也没有。有些遗憾。但这并不影响罗汉果的神奇功效。对罗汉果有详细记载的，是清代的《临桂县志》、《永宁州志》。不仅有罗汉果之名，还有其形态、性味、效用记载，这为罗汉果的药用提供了可靠的历史依据：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000636": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000636",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000637": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000637",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>光绪十一年的《永宁州志》有罗汉果作药的记载。永宁即今永福县。光绪三十一年《临桂县志》记载：罗汉果，磊如柿，椭圆，中空，味甜，性凉，治劳嗽。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000638": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000638",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000639": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000639",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>关于罗汉果的名字，已经没有人知道它的来历。但是当地的瑶族人，给这个奇特的名字赋予了许多神奇的传说。我在永福的几天，搜集到了不少关于罗汉果的传说。我把它们记在这里。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000640": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000640",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000641": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000641",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>传说一：相传古时有一瑶族女子，进山采药。晌午，烈日当空，口渴难忍，遂至一山涧，寻找山泉野果充饥。此山名大瑶山。生长着许多茂密的植物。瑶女四处寻找。蓦然看见密林深处有许多罗汉。瑶女躲在远处观望。此处的树上缠满藤萝。一种青绿的果子挂满树梢。众罗汉旁若无人，摘果大嚼，良久，离去。瑶女亦去采摘野果充饥。清甜爽口，饥渴顿消。异之。遂将果实带回山寨，檐前屋后遍植。次年，果实累累。瑶女将果子分送族人。有久咳不愈、咽喉疼痛者，竟然康复。问果名。瑶女说，因于深山遇罗汉，叫罗汉果吧。从此，罗汉果声名远扬。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000642": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000642",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000643": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000643",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>传说二：很久以前，有位瑶族樵夫，其母患咳喘病，久治不愈。有天樵夫上山，被虫蛰，手臂红肿不已，他见身边几个野果，便摘下，捣碎，果汁涂之。竟然缓解肿痛。于是，将果带回家，给母亲吃，不久，咳喘病痊愈。有个叫罗汉的郎中来此，见此果神奇，潜心研究，制成罗汉果茶，为百姓广为服用。从此，称此果为罗汉果。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000644": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000644",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000645": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000645",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>不管怎样，罗汉果的神奇药效，使之成为一味名贵药材。市面上不容易买到。但有罗汉果冲剂卖。我曾经买了很多罗汉果冲剂给母亲服用。母亲患支气管炎久矣。一直咳嗽，各种偏方吃了不少，总也不见好。当年住寄啸山庄，内有许多枇杷树，我曾剪下许多枇杷叶煎汁给母亲服用。枇杷叶是有镇咳效果的。但，只是镇。每每喝完枇杷叶汁，母亲剧烈的咳嗽，总才平息下来。但不久，又咳。于是，我想到了罗汉果冲剂。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000646": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000646",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000647": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000647",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>并不是我想到的，是南方的S告诉我的。我在电话中说母亲的咳嗽久不见好。她说，何不用罗汉果冲剂试试。这是我平生第一次听说罗汉果。名字怪怪的，总让人想到，是不是因罗汉的形象命名的。于是，每当母亲咳嗽的时候，我就想起S说的罗汉果冲剂。抱着试一试的态度，跑遍全城。终于在一家私人药房里买到了。查看上面的药用说明：生津止渴，清肝润肺，化痰止咳，明目益思。真是如获至宝。买了五大包。满载而归。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000648": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000648",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000649": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000649",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>回来后，我用枇杷叶煎汁，再用枇杷汁冲泡罗汉果颗粒。我不知道世上有没有这个药方。我把两种镇咳草药和在一起给母亲服用。居然很有效果。几次服用之后，有很长时间听不到母亲剧烈的咳嗽了。我把这个近乎奇迹的疗效告诉了S。S说，那是长生果，名不虚传的。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000650": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000650",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000651": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000651",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>S给我寄了很多罗汉果--不是冲剂，而是一个个黄褐色的鹅蛋大的果子。我在心里感激S的一片好意。同时我又有些失望。果子不是鲜绿鲜亮的那种。黄褐色，轻轻一碰，壳就破了。壳很薄，鸡蛋壳那样薄。再看里面，毛茸茸的，也是黄褐色，整个样子，像是枯萎很久，或是风干了。这就是罗汉果吗？罗汉果不是鲜绿的吗？我在心里想着，S给我的罗汉果，是不是存放的时间太长了，给我时没有注意到已经风干？想到S千里迢迢寄罗汉果给我，毕竟是一片心意，我就没有扔掉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000652": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000652",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000653": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000653",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>我把S寄来的那些黄褐色的、早已风干了的罗汉果放起来。我理解的水果，都应该是鲜绿可口的。即使是在买不到罗汉果冲剂的时候，我也没有想到那些风干了的罗汉果。但我一直没有扔。直到后来，我来到南方，才发现，我错了。我对罗汉果的一无所知让我误会了S。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000654": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000654",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000655": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000655",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>那一日，我和S在邕江宾馆吃饭。饭前点一壶茶，罗汉果茶。服务员端来茶壶。外加一只罗汉果。那是和S寄给我的一模一样的罗汉果，黄褐色。我有些奇怪了。这不正是那种风干了的罗汉果吗。在我疑惑的目光下，服务员拿起罗汉果，轻轻一捏，壳破了，露出毛茸茸的黄褐色的果肉。正是S寄给我的那种罗汉果。在我惊诧的目光中，服务员掰开果肉，一瓣一瓣放进茶壶，放水冲泡。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000656": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000656",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000657": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000657",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>我问S：罗汉果怎么是这样子的？S笑着说，这果子好。烤得不错。我亲自挑选的。个大形圆，色泽黄褐，摇不响，壳不破、不焦，味甜而不苦。这是上好的罗汉果。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000658": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000658",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000659": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000659",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>烤？我一下子晕了。罗汉果要烤？这烤字烤得我浑身热燥，心里不是滋味。喝着罗汉果茶，和S聊天。我想知道罗汉果怎么会是烤出来的。原来，罗汉果熟了，要放置一周，使果实糖化。再用慢火烘烤，外壳干，果皮呈黄褐色，即可。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000660": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000660",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000661": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000661",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>我忽然想到S寄给我的一大盒罗汉果，至今还放在我的书柜上。我急忙走出门外，拿出手机给母亲打电话。我告诉她，我的书柜上有一盒圆圆的果子，快快找出来。母亲找了半天，在书丛中翻出了S寄给我的那盒罗汉果。我知道，母亲的咳嗽声，又要停歇好长一段时间了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000662": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000662",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000663": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000663",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000664": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000664",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><h2><span style=\"\">第24节：看着我，不要忽然转过脸去--龙眼(1)</span></h2></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000665": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000665",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>\t</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000666": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000666",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>看着我，不要忽然转过脸去--龙眼</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000667": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000667",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000668": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000668",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>今夏，灵山没去成。一直有个愿望，读完《灵山》，再去品赏灵山荔枝。两座灵山并无联系，但感觉很奇妙。灵山荔枝，待来年再去吃。今夏去了灵水。灵水有泉，有深潭，可游泳，更有漫山遍野的龙眼，怎么也吃不完。灵水在武鸣。武鸣是龙眼之乡，距邕城30公里。这么近，那漫山龙眼就天天在你眼前晃，晃啊晃的，直晃得你儿女情长--在龙眼成熟的季节，你变得心荡神漾，每日寻思着去赴一场曼妙的约会。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000669": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000669",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000670": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000670",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>灵水龙眼，是武鸣的特产。长于大明山。北回归线横穿山中。独特的地理位置使大明山形成了奇异的山水脉象。每年春天后，阳光直射点往大明山移动，到大明山，又回转南移。古代居住此地的壮乡百姓对这个现象不可思议，认为大明山是神灵所在，遂叫大明山为岜是。岜是，壮语，意即神山。广西山系，有一片弧--都阳山，大明山，大瑶山，架桥岭。这片弧，是李四光说的。照传统的理解，就是龙脉。大明山则是龙眼。于是大明山越说越神奇，成了壮乡的圣山。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000671": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000671",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000672": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000672",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>武鸣的水也好。有湖名灵水。在武鸣县城南1公里处，是个天然泉水湖。国家体委游泳队的训练基地。灵水是深潭，湖岸怪石嶙峋，绿树成荫，水色澄澈幽美。灵水并不深，最深处才有3米。有清泉9注，汩汩涌出，称九龙泉。春夏秋冬，水温无变化，是个天然游泳池。每年农历三月初三及中秋节，数万壮乡男女，聚集湖边，搭台对歌，观灯赏月。远树迷漫，山野风情，比起西湖七月半，总是让人多了些记挂与向往。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000673": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000673",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000674": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000674",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>圣山，灵水。武鸣有这两样，足够了。出龙眼不再稀奇。出上好的龙眼也不再稀奇。去武鸣除了游圣山，游灵水，还可以品尝灵水龙眼。圣山灵水孕育滋养出来的神果，总是不同凡响。每到龙眼成熟季节，从邕城去武鸣的路上，宝马奔驰，香车美人络绎不绝。为什么去吃龙眼的多数是女人？因为养颜，想青春永驻。留住青春的方法多种，植物养颜是一种时尚。与其涂脂抹粉，不若享用植物精华来代替，吃水果。水果之中，首选新鲜的龙眼。这不是空穴来风。李时珍说：食品以荔枝为贵，而资益则龙眼为良。王士雄，清代医学家，他对龙眼情有独钟，说龙眼为果中神品。神品自然非同寻常了。想想也是，再美的化妆品，毕竟是化学制品，对肌肤有伤害。龙眼乃自然造化，天然果品，无限的甜美与滋养会让更多的女人迷上龙眼。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000675": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000675",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000676": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000676",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000677": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000677",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><h2><span style=\"\">第25节：看着我，不要忽然转过脸去--龙眼(2)</span></h2></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000678": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000678",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>\t</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000679": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000679",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>龙眼有许多异称，都很美。如桂圆，蜜脾，龙目，荔枝奴，绣木团，骊珠、海珠丛。其中，荔枝奴的别称很形象。因为龙眼的成熟期一般都跟在荔枝之后，吃完荔枝，龙眼紧接着就上市了。龙眼春天开花夏日结果。大多是春节后不久开花，满树繁花。风一吹，落英满地。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000680": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000680",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000681": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000681",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>成百上千的人浩浩荡荡涌到武鸣吃龙眼，场面很壮观。足见武鸣龙眼好吃。岂止是好吃。当我站在山坡，看见一树一树龙眼披挂着，累累枝头，意态飞动，让我满心喜欢。碧绿的树冠像巨伞撑开，正值炎夏，树荫间清风徐来，蝉鸣声声。一不留神，树林里闪现出半张笑靥，那是一个圆润的笑容。像在梦中见过。蓝黑色衣裳，长裙短衣，头包青色绣花帕，腰系绣花围裙。叶簇间，有碎光和麻雀跳舞。我对她痴望半天，已经忘记是来吃龙眼的。她一只柔荑之手握着一枝龙眼，另一只手轻轻摘下一颗，掰开壳，将细嫩雪白的果肉送进口中，未了，丹唇轻启，一枚墨玉般的核吐出。原来夏季竟是那么的清凉和安静。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000682": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000682",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000683": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000683",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>我不能自已。摘下一颗龙眼。果体饱满，圆润，壳面黄褐色。将那浑圆的果子用拇指和食指捏住，我感觉到了一种柔软，依稀记起了某种柔软的感觉与此相似。壳很快裂开，露出晶莹的果肉。我轻咬一口，顿时，眉舒目展，为这果味诱惑。肉质软润，味甜，脆爽，清香。这感觉与吃荔枝不同。荔枝肉略有一点点酸感。龙眼没有。龙眼是鲜甜。再看手上的半边龙眼，果肉白若凝脂，乌黑的核，像一只美丽的眼睛。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000684": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000684",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000685": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000685",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>我想到了故乡。可故乡没有圣山灵水，更没有龙眼。生长龙眼的地方，必然是山清水秀，需要山水之灵气滋养。我的故乡一马平川，故乡的女孩们无法享受新鲜的龙眼。她们吃桂圆，即烤干了的龙眼，长途跋涉从南方运过去的。桂圆在故乡人的心目中，是一味高级补品。李时珍说，久服强魂聪明，轻身不老。过年过节，给老人送礼，都是桂圆包。包装精致的桂圆盒，在故乡一直畅销。还有，女士吃得多。女孩子们身子不爽时，都将桂圆放在身边，零食一样，随时剥着吃。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000686": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000686",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000687": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000687",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>在故乡，乡里人办喜事，少不了桂圆。新人要吃红枣、花生，桂圆、莲子做成的&quot;早生贵子&quot;羹。方法是：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000688": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000688",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000689": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000689",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>花生仁去膜，莲子去心，用清水浸泡。捞出。红枣去核。将红枣、花生仁、莲子放入汤盆里，倒入适量的清水，上笼屉用火蒸，再加入桂圆肉、冰糖，再蒸至酥烂，取出即可。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000690": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000690",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000691": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000691",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>饱啖龙眼，心满意足从武鸣赶回邕城。路上，看到许多山村的吊脚楼。那是壮乡人栖息的地方，龙眼挂满了屋檐。一个壮乡女子，爬上长长的竹梯。我心里暗暗焦急，想着，她是否站稳了。那一刻，真想走过去扶她一把。她没有注意到远处的我在对她凝望。她把装着龙眼的簸箕顶在头上，一手扶着簸箕，一手扶竹梯，很灵巧地往上爬。把簸箕放在屋顶上，让烈日暴晒。几个日头，龙眼就晒成桂圆了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000692": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000692",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000693": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000693",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>从武鸣带回一大包新鲜的龙眼。我坐在窗前，一边剥着龙眼，一边读着明人小品。偶尔抬头瞄一瞄窗外闲闲淡淡的一剪疏影。忽然想起一个诡异的故事。这故事是柏杨的一篇小说，叫《龙眼粥》。据说还拍成了电影。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000694": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000694",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000695": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000695",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>说的是一个生死轮回的凄美爱情--</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000696": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000696",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000697": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000697",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>大学毕业后，我就被分到这个偏僻的小县城教书，这是一个非常落后的地方，盛产着竹子和风……</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000698": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000698",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000699": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000699",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>龙眼粥的做法很简单。用糯米，加水煮至半熟，加入龙眼肉，煮熟即可。我对柏杨那个奇异的故事记忆犹新，一直牵挂。想着哪天也能吃上一回龙眼粥。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000700": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000700",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000701": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000701",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000702": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000702",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><h2><span style=\"\">第26节：在倒影中萦回，在梦乡里开花--金花茶(1)</span></h2></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000703": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000703",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>\t</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000704": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000704",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>在倒影中萦回，在梦乡里开花--金花茶</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000705": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000705",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000706": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000706",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>写下这个题目，我的心情十分愉悦。虽然我经常把金花茶读成金茶花，可是有什么要紧呢。哪一种读法，都让我感到那些金黄的颜色像阳光一样无可遏止地从四面八方奔涌而来，把我裹成黄金甲。一种黄袍加身的醺醉感。那天，我们在邕城金花茶公园流连许久，直到后来，我们迷了路，在那些金花茶中间穿行，怎么也走不出去的时候，我才想起那个梦境。那个梦境与此竟是如此相似。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000707": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000707",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000708": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000708",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>我有一种预感，这个人迟早是要与我相遇的。这一切迟早都要发生。她是谁，我却无从记起。可她一直藏在我的记忆最深处，我怎么也找不到。我曾千百次试图唤醒那个梦中的记忆，很多日子过去，一无所获。曾经，在一个初夏的早晨，在扬州天宁寺门前，一个须发飘然的卦师拦住我的去路。我说，我是不信卦的。卦师扯住我的手臂，说送我一卦，分文不取。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000709": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000709",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000710": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000710",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>他在我的耳边说了一句话。我寻思良久，想想，还是给了他一笔卦费。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000711": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000711",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000712": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000712",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>那以后，我开始做梦。奇怪的是，梦中所见，皆是明媚的山谷，河边杂木林下，灌木丛中，竹林或茶林中，常有一条金黄色的巨蟒悠然游行。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000713": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000713",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000714": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000714",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>对于蟒，我是不怕的。小时候，在故乡，我常常到竹园里的树上采叶，那树临近河边，有时一抬头，便可见到一条巨蟒正警惕地望着我。见的次数多了，也没啥。你动作要轻，不要惹它，什么事也没有。但是，那条巨大的金黄色的蟒，怎么总是游在我的梦境里呢。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000715": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000715",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000716": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000716",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>奇怪的是，后来，那条巨大的金黄色的蟒，真的被我看到了。那是来邕城不久，大约九月份吧，在邕城动物园。我们的小区与动物园很近，中间只隔一条心圩江。每天早上，动物园各种各样的鸟鸣，就传到我的枕上来。那天我们就去了动物园。不可思议的是，我居然看见了那个梦中巨蟒。它有个富贵的名字，叫黄金蟒，稀贵，宝贝似的供着，观者啧啧称奇。这条黄金蟒身披金黄和白色相间的大鳞片，一身金黄色的彩装，非常鲜艳。极富高贵的气质。体长约有三米，被誉为蟒中极品。我用手去摸它，它很温顺，把头贴到我的手背。我能听见它发出吁吁的声音，犹如寒风的啸声。很多女孩将黄金蟒缠在身上，与它合影，也不见任何的惧怕。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000717": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000717",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000718": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000718",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>动物园驯养员介绍，黄金蟒性格温顺，不会主动攻击人，也没有毒性。在原产地印度，印度教徒视黄金蟒为神灵加以崇拜。我所遇见的事物总是反复出现。以前的旧梦，以后总会在某个地方重现。有时我无法理解这个现象。但这验证了我对时间的看法，时间就像一个圆，完美，并且虚实相间。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000719": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000719",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000720": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000720",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>节外生枝写下这段黄金蟒的文字，是因为曾经做过那个梦。梦中黄金蟒肆意游走的环境，竟然是金花茶公园。奇怪极了。我说怎么这么熟悉呢。好像很多年前我就来过此地。我们来的时候，金花茶正满园盛开。顺着一条蜿蜒曲折的湖边小路前行，渐渐地，我们走进了一片金黄色。金花茶是常绿灌木，两米多高。树皮灰白，光洁平滑。树上的枝条较为稀疏，嫩枝淡紫色，也很光洁。花朵单生，也有两朵的，稍微下垂。花开时呈杯状、壶状或碗状，色彩鲜艳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000721": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000721",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000722": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000722",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000723": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000723",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><h2><span style=\"\">第27节：在倒影中萦回，在梦乡里开花--金花茶(2)</span></h2></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000724": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000724",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>\t</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000725": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000725",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>山茶花，红似火，白如雪，没有不喜欢的。美中不足的是，千百年来，一直没有发现黄色的山茶。李时珍在《本草纲目》中似乎有过记载：山茶产南方，深冬开花，红瓣黄蕊。这个红瓣黄蕊是不是黄色的山茶呢。文字不多，语焉不详。到底有没有黄色的山茶花呢。只有极少数人相信，世上一定有黄色的山茶花存在。于是不断寻找。日本植物学家津山尚，为寻找黄色的山茶花穷尽毕生精力，足迹踏遍印支半岛，最终无功而返，失望之余写下《幻想的黄色茶花历险记》。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000726": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000726",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000727": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000727",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>丘陵低山及河岸村中，有位稀世美人养在山间溪谷中。她像一个夏天穿白裙子的少女，裹着金黄色的披肩，她从时光里走来，几千年了？日益丰满，被世间许多人暗恋。她缓慢地进入生活，林间溪头，花前月下，或者小桥流水，她微笑着。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000728": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000728",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000729": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000729",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>有一天，一位植物学家在广西南宁地区邕宁县坛落乡的溪沟两岸，发现一种极为稀有的山茶，花朵金黄艳丽，点缀于深绿光亮的叶片之中，十分雅致。经确认，此乃稀世名花---黄色山茶花。1965年，此种稀世山茶，被正式命名为金花茶。这是植物史上的一件大事。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000730": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000730",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000731": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000731",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>金花茶公园，遍植山茶。四周林木苍郁，往前行，地势渐高，隐闻溪水潺潺，路过一片山茶，忽有一条清澈见底的溪水在林间奔流，绿树茂荫低垂于溪面之上，溪中彩色小鱼忽隐忽现地穿梭在碧绿的水草之间。继续前行又渡过了几条小溪几处小桥，道路逐渐开朗，大片大片的金花茶出现在眼前。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000732": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000732",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000733": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000733",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>金花茶是国家一级保护植物，是国宝。被誉为茶花皇后，植物界的大熊猫。来看金花茶的人很多。金花茶正在开放。那些金花茶也是随意散植的。在溪边，周围有买麻藤、藤金合欢、刺果藤、楠木、鹅掌楸等植物。金花茶的叶深绿色，厚实，狭长圆形。金花茶的花朵，一片黄色，耀眼夺目，仿佛涂着一层蜡，鲜丽悄致，似有半透明之感。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000734": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000734",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000735": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000735",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>金花茶的花期为每年11月至次年3月，一棵树上，花朵几百。花开时，繁花满枝，烂若黄金。赏金花茶，宜有阳光。阳光照透金瓣玉蕊，晶莹光洁，蜡质透亮，仿若金杯。这里没有幽静，也不是幽美。这里只有阳光，只有矜持颦笑中散发出来的华贵气韵。后来，在珠江公园，我又看到了金花茶，那又是一种别样的风姿。那时，我感到有一种明亮的，金黄色的气息在我身边围绕。让我阴郁的内心有了片刻的明朗。我目不转睛地注视着金花茶，整整一个下午。我甚至忘记了满地阳光。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000736": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000736",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000737": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000737",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000738": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000738",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><h2><span style=\"\">第28节：我的纯净而绵长的喜悦--红豆树</span></h2></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000739": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000739",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>\t</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000740": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000740",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>我的纯净而绵长的喜悦--红豆树</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000741": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000741",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000742": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000742",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>还是古人浪漫。热恋情人，恩爱夫妻，因赶考远走他乡，或四处谋生，驿路遥遥，间关千里，相互牵挂着，便有了相思。日日思君不见君，共饮长江水。痛苦甜蜜；衣带渐宽终不悔，为伊消得人憔悴。甜蜜痛苦。说的都是刻骨铭心的相思。因为相思，望穿了多少倚窗秋水，泪湿了多少漂泊的衣衫。每每读这些诗句，总感到有一种共鸣的心动，有一种天籁般的气息穿透心湖，直抵最柔软的灵魂深处。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000743": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000743",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000744": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000744",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>神话传说，诗词歌赋，都离不开相思。相传，古时有男子出征，其妻朝夕于树下远眺，望夫归。音信全无。泣于树下。泪流干。再流，是粒粒鲜红的血。久之，血凝，化作红豆，生根发芽，长成大树，结满一树红豆，后人称之为红豆树。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000745": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000745",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000746": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000746",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>相思树古已有之。南朝任昉《述异记》记载，战国时，有人出征未归，其妻思苦而逝。墓上生树，枝叶皆倾向其夫出征方向，世人称之为相思木。梁武帝《欢闻歌》云：南有相思木，合影复同心。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000747": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000747",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000748": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000748",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>还有一种相思树。晋干宝《搜神记》记载，宋康王夺韩凭之妻。韩氏夫妇自尽，康王不许合葬。两冢相望。一宿之间，坟顶各生一株大树。久之，两树屈曲环抱，根系相交于下，枝叶杂错于上，并有鸳鸯一对宿于树间，日夜交颈悲鸣，挥之不去。宋人哀之，称此树为相思树。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000749": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000749",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000750": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000750",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>求之不得，寤寐思服，《诗经》以这样的相思开篇。相思是婉约派的主要内容。过尽千帆皆不是；才下眉头，却上心头。相思如此恼人，如此折磨人。帘卷西风，人比黄花瘦。一代女词家在《醉花阴》里，瘦得如此憔悴。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000751": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000751",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000752": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000752",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>有相思便有信物，作为寄托。不一定是金银。有时金银还不如一粒小豆子。王维的相思豆，一直挂在诗歌长廊上，到现在依然亮红亮红的，那么纯洁高贵，有几人买得起。有钱公子，赠给小姐的都是珠宝玉石。用红豆作信物，一定是贫穷书生灵感所至。离家赶考。临行前，想送样东西给热恋的情人，以慰相思。想来想去，忽然记起屋后那棵红豆树。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000753": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000753",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000754": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000754",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>红豆树生长于南国，是常绿乔木。其豆光洁，色泽殷红，不腐不蛀，久存不变色，恰似红宝石。多惹人喜爱。树上结豆荚，内含一粒两粒鲜红光亮的种子，这就是红豆。红豆树开花结果，全凭自然造化。有的树几十年开花一次，开花后还不一定结果。因此红豆成了稀有珍品。红豆略呈心形，中间饱满凸起，四周略扁，色泽鲜红，娇小而动人。书生采撷几颗红豆，赠给妩媚的恋人。大家竞相效仿，开始了一个古典的浪漫。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000755": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000755",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000756": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000756",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>曾去江阴访友。友人带我去顾山镇，看红豆树。此树被誉为海内孤木，1500多年历史。树大，约10米高，枝繁叶茂，三月舒叶，五月放花，十月结果。周围廊壁上，刻满了密密的相思。读着，生出感动，心中溢满思念。遂买了一颗圆而饱满的红豆，准备浪漫一回，把我在外多日的相思，带回家。掏出手机，想告诉她，我买了一颗相思豆。忽然间红豆落地，滚了滚，在草丛里消失不见。不由苦笑，相思丢了。古典浪漫对我们已是奢望。纵然远在天涯海角，可我们拥有特快专递，图文传真，笔记本，电话，手机，伊妹儿，QQ，用不着日夕惦念，几个按钮，就可把我们拴得紧紧的。哪里还有相思。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000757": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000757",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000758": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000758",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>红豆作为饰品，于玉颈皓腕，都是天作之合。女人最俗的装饰，便是佩金戴银。玉腕上，最宜翡翠镯。或者红豆。金银饰品皆人工打造，工序太多，从矿石到首饰，必要经过千锤百炼。工序太多的后果是，世间浮游的污浊之气一遍一遍融入其中，饰品上沾染了无数工匠的手污与汗渍，融入了世间太多的繁杂与太多的贪婪目光。金银饰品散发出来的光，带给人们的感觉是复杂，骚动和不安。这样复杂的饰品怎可与细润的肌肤相亲。翡翠镯也打磨，但工序很少，翡翠从玉矿采出，经切割，到加工成品，只有外表打磨，内里纯洁透明，外界浊气无法浸入。所以，翡翠镯怎么看，都清爽温润，悦人眼目。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000759": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000759",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000760": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000760",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>红豆乃是一种喜悦。纯自然的一种饰品，最原始，最纯真。红豆树高达七八十米，吸天地之灵气，精结而成红豆。在南国，有许多地方，红豆被唤作灯豆。很久以前用油灯。将红豆放进灯油里，利用红豆的光泽反射出新的光亮。多少女子在油灯下看着红豆，做着春梦，渐渐照亮出一张张晶莹透亮的脸。据说，在很多山区，装有红豆的油灯，是父母为女儿准备的不可或缺的嫁妆。那是给孩子们的祝福。那么一点亮光，感受到的，却是一缕缕温暖的气息。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000761": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000761",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000762": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000762",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>秋天到了。在南方，秋天的天空像玻璃一样晶亮，两朵，三朵，暖暖的云。我们在清晨去白龙湖。传说宋代名将狄青率军驻于此处，见湖边白羊一群，像白龙游动，遂起名白龙湖。去山顶的石阶，名望仙坡。两侧有许多红豆树。向上望，红豆树和天空一样高远。正是红豆成熟季节，遍地红豆。我们一直在捡红豆。高远天空下的南方煦风干净地晃动我的白衬衣。我抬头去看相思树下那个捡拾红豆的女人，一个和天空一样晶亮的女人，她也正抬头，温暖地看我一眼。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000763": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000763",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000764": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000764",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>红豆树作为一种风景而永恒。有些风景一晃而过，有些人事经久不去。每个人对于爱的理解不一样，并无正确与错误之分。不断向前，同时又落下很多东西。这过程常伴随着忧伤。爱的情感并不复杂，甚至很单纯，却又让人感觉难以捉摸。浸入内心的是繁密得无以言说的情绪。每一个人都是一个故事。不要轻易放弃生命中的任何一处风景。一颗小小的红豆，一片沉寂的荒芜，都可以让我们感到如坐春风，化作一股暖流涌上心头。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000765": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000765",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000766": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000766",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000767": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000767",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><h2><span style=\"\">第29节：老松与菟丝花的传说--茯苓(1)</span></h2></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000768": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000768",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>\t</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000769": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000769",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>老松与菟丝花的传说--茯苓</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000770": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000770",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000771": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000771",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>山中多古松。我像个采药师行走在崎岖的大明山。在此之前我没有见过茯苓。我按照古书上的记载寻找千年松树。书上说，望松树赤者，下有茯苓。野生之茯苓，其生长在地下十年或数百年不等，得松之精气，其皮黑皱，其肉坚实，不论何地产，皆为佳品。书上又说，千年之松，下有茯苓，上有菟丝。我谨遵古训寻找着松根下细白的菟丝。菟丝为采药者寻找野生茯苓之标志。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000772": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000772",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000773": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000773",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>很多人都没有见过茯苓。一天，我在万绿参天的大明山腹地行走。树林阴翳，松涛满耳轰鸣。我趴在一棵老松下。松如飞龙劈空，雄古奇伟。我像尝百草的神农，拨开泥土，对着树根上一团怪物审视良久，外皮黑而皱，形如鸟兽。掰开，露出纯白的肉质。我像个经验老到的行家，肯定地点点头，这就是茯苓了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000774": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000774",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000775": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000775",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>茯苓是一种很奇怪的植物。它是寄生者。多寄生于古松根部。藏而不露，面目怪异。在古代一直被视为神物。它的形状不雅，形态各异。如兔如马。很能激发人们的想像。古人因看到茯苓长于老松根上，便以为它是松树精华所化生的神灵之物，称它为茯灵，茯神或松腴。《广西中药志》中，称茯苓为松薯，松木薯，松苓，十分的形象。大松下，附根而生，无苗叶花实，作块如拳，在土底，大者至数斤。似人形、龟形者，为最佳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000776": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000776",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000777": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000777",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>诸家本草著作，对于茯苓的叙述，都很详尽。古人多认为茯苓乃千岁松脂。高山有大松，或百岁，或千岁，其精变为青牛，为伏龟，采食其实得长生。又说茯苓得松之精气，久服百病自去，长生不老。在很多典籍中，茯苓经无数次的传说，已变得荒谬怪诞。有记载说，茯苓千年以上者，变化为兔或为马，服之轻身，成就仙道。《西游记》第一回曾讲述：猴王率领众猴采仙桃，摘异果，刨仙药……，熟煨山药，烂煮黄精，捣碎茯苓并薏苡，石锅微火漫炊羹。人间纵有珍馐味，怎比山猴乐更宁？原来，孙悟空也是吃了黄精，茯苓，薏苡等如许滋补神药才变成猴精的。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000778": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000778",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000779": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000779",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>得道成仙的说法固然夸张，茯苓却是一味长寿保健用药，医家无不看重。《神农本草经》说，茯苓久服安魂养神，不饥延年。魏晋时期，食茯苓以求长生蔚然成风，据说南朝齐梁时期陶弘景辞官返乡时，梁武帝每月赐茯苓五斤，白蜜二斤，以供服用。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000780": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000780",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000781": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000781",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000782": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000782",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><h2><span style=\"\">第30节：老松与菟丝花的传说--茯苓(2)</span></h2></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000783": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000783",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>\t</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000784": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000784",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>茯苓很多人没见过，但名字不陌生。《红楼梦》第六十回，茉莉粉替去蔷薇硝，玫瑰露引来茯苓霜，其中写道：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000785": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000785",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000786": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000786",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>昨儿有粤东的官儿来拜，送了上头两小篓子茯苓霜。余外给了门上人一篓作门礼，你哥哥分了这些。这地方千年松柏最多，所以单取了这茯苓的精液和了药，不知怎么弄出这怪俊的白霜儿来。说第一用人乳和着，每日早起吃一钟，最补人的，第二用牛奶子，万不得，滚白水也好。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000787": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000787",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000788": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000788",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>这是古代的白粉，制法秘而不宣。茯苓霜是口服用的，是味补品，饮之可以养生长寿。古人对于养生术的研究，规模之宏大与成果之丰硕，令人惊叹。无数的养生术让人眼花缭乱无所适从。对于生之留恋与爱惜，古人做得全面而又细致。活着终究是美好的。而时常袭来的疾病却又看不见摸不着，如幽灵般在身边浮游着。除了祈求上苍，对于仙丹妙药的寻求，成了无数古人的梦想。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000789": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000789",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000790": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000790",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>于是，茯苓成了稀罕之物，大家服食茯苓已成时尚。但茯苓多在深山。山高谷深，不易得。有人开始造假。柳宗元上过一次大当。一次，柳宗元积劳成疾，遵医嘱服茯苓。久不见效。去询问医者。医生感到不解，审视药渣，原来不是茯苓，是用老芋头加工的假药。柳宗元大怒，写下《辨茯神文》，告诫人们要学会辨别，防止以假充真。由于此文好玩，文字不多，现全文录于此：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000791": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000791",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000792": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000792",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>茯神之神，在于舒肝愉心，解积化滞，调和阴阳，君之食之，其乐扬扬。野芋多生于低湿之地，于水中潜藏繁盛，常与蝗虫混杂滋生。单夫施计伎，刮野芋皮，削于茯神状，中空而外泽，以伪乱真，敝之误服之，险遭不测。乱真之世，无力挽救，药物既多伪，知之者甚少，故著词意，以悟来者。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000793": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000793",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000794": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000794",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>唐宋时服食茯苓已很普遍。再说苏氏兄弟食茯苓的逸事。苏辙在陈州期间，开始研究养生之术。葛洪认为，长生术要服金丹。但苏辙认为金丹不易得，于是服茯苓。通过服食茯苓来固形养气，延年益寿。为此他还专门写了一篇《服茯苓赋》。这篇赋在当时流传甚广，苏辙后来出使契丹，契丹臣僚对他说：闻常服茯苓，欲乞其方。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000795": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000795",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000796": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000796",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>东坡很会做茯苓饼。他曾披露了做茯苓饼的秘诀：以九蒸胡麻(即芝麻)，同去皮茯苓，少入白蜜为饼食之，日久气力不衰，百病自去，此乃长生要诀。东坡晚年仍能有惊人的记忆力和强健的身体，或许与他常食茯苓饼有关。后来，慈禧太后也喜欢吃茯苓饼。她常命御膳房做茯苓饼，并以此赏赐大臣。其制法是，取茯苓细粉，米粉，白糖各等份，加水适量，调成糊状，再以微火于平锅里摊烙即成。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000797": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000797",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000798": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000798",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>茯苓可以养颜。其神奇功效在古代典籍中屡被提及。《集仙录》曾载一个故事：四川眉山一女子避难，逃至深山，被山洪阻隔于孤寺，十余日不炊，幸得茯苓充饥，以后续以茯苓为食，容颜变成美貌的仙女模样。李时珍披露了一个养颜秘方：用酒渍茯苓，日食一块，至百日，肌体润泽，延年耐老，面若童颜。要年轻，食茯苓。想想现在的女士们，动辄几百上千元的化妆品，不管有没有副作用一股脑儿往脸上搽。怎么就没想到茯苓这样的天然美容品呢。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000799": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000799",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000800": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000800",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>我这样写茯苓，缘于我到过梧州。一个消耗茯苓最多的地方，做龟苓膏用。到梧州不能不吃龟苓膏。怎么说呢，龟苓膏之于梧州，如羊肉泡馍之于西安。都属于传统街头小吃。龟苓膏爽滑细嫩，羊肉泡馍肥腴柔韧。一碗羊肉泡馍馋倒无数人，一碗龟苓膏能让人丢了魂。让人丢魂的，多是美女。龟苓膏是个青衣美女，站在苍梧山头水袖飞扬，风情万种，诱惑着你。西安是大城市。梧州是个弹丸小城，但梧州历史并不比西安短。《史记》说，舜南巡狩，崩于苍梧之野。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000801": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000801",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000802": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000802",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>现在的梧州城，满街都是龟苓膏，双钱牌，钱王牌，钱钱钱，这么多的钱在你眼前晃，蛮撩人的。2007年初秋的一天午后，天空飘着细雨。我在苍梧山区的梧州城吃龟苓膏。吃了很多。口感极好。后来又吃。一天丢几次魂。觉着不写一则文字留着纪念，委实说不过去。于是就写下了茯苓。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000803": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000803",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000804": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000804",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000805": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000805",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><h2><span style=\"\">第31节：关于故乡，轻描淡写的记忆--南瓜(1)</span></h2></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000806": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000806",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>\t</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000807": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000807",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>关于故乡，轻描淡写的记忆--南瓜</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000808": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000808",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000809": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000809",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>原以为我对南瓜的熟知，如同我熟悉家长里短的村邻一样。十岁之前我还总是随母亲檐前屋后栽种南瓜。我跟在母亲身后，在篱笆的草丛中和屋檐下刨几个小坑，丢几粒瓜籽，掩土浇水。种南瓜就这么简单。南瓜很容易生长，不用施肥。几丝细雨，几泼日光，瓜籽就醒了，慢慢生长。先是嫩芽，再是青青的藤蔓。再后，就开始出现如麻绳一样粗大扭曲的瓜藤和长满毛刺的叶子，茎长达数十米，节处生根，粗壮，有棱沟，很多卷须。卷须又分很多叉。顺着草绳攀缘而上，爬满屋顶，或者就在荒草丛中沿着篱笆四处蔓延。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000810": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000810",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000811": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000811",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>一年复一年，花开花谢，瓜熟蒂落。吃南瓜长这么大。无数大小南瓜结结实实地长成我的肉。但是来南方之后才意外发现，我对憨态可掬的南瓜几乎一无所知。不知道它的由来。不知道是番瓜还是饭瓜。尤其不知道瓜花藤苗皆可入馔，这些瓜花藤苗甚至可以堂而皇之端上星级酒店的筵席。在此之前，我私下里认为南瓜是粗鄙的，一副憨态，又无长相，充其量不过是普通时蔬聊以充饥，就像邻家的胖妹，墩墩的，在野地里默默割草的样子，看到你，憨憨地笑笑。说不上多好，也没坏印象。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000812": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000812",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000813": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000813",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>七月，八月，南瓜熟了。长圆，扁圆，圆形或瓢形等。嫩时绿色，成熟时赤褐色。熟了的南瓜卧在屋顶上，或藏在密密草丛中。面盆那么大，摘一个可以吃好几天。屋顶上晒了那么多的南瓜，很是好看。青瓦，黄瓜，绿叶。我有时就躺在洒满阳光的屋顶上。四周很静谧，没有一丝风，白云在蓝天上，凝视着这个孤独的世界。母亲反复叮嘱我，不要碰到瓜藤。瓜藤受伤了，这一株南瓜就会枯萎。我这才明白南瓜藤上为什么总长着许多小刺，原是不让人轻易碰它。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000814": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000814",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000815": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000815",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>日子是这样的诗意，生活又是那样的艰难。我曾在饥寒交迫中度过了十多年的童年时光。那些荒芜的岁月，我天天沿着墙根荒园找瓜果野草果腹。南瓜，在我的家乡又叫饭瓜。是可以当饭吃的。所谓瓜菜半年粮。在那段日子里，我吃过太多的山芋，胡萝卜，玉米，麦子。米饭极少，只有过年过节才能吃上一顿。但是，有一个问题至今让我疑惑不解，在那样困难的情况下，遍地的南瓜花和南瓜的藤苗，在我的故乡为什么一直没人吃呢。我知道南瓜花和南瓜苗可以食用，却是在二十多年之后的今天。我来到南方。有一次逛菜市，惊奇地发现，菜摊上摆满了花花绿绿的南瓜花和南瓜苗。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000816": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000816",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000817": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000817",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>查了一些资料。说南瓜的生长已有一万年历史。葫芦科植物，原产亚洲南部，也就是以前所谓的南番，所以也叫南瓜，番瓜。外域传入的蔬果皆冠之以番，番瓜番茄番薯，番石榴番荔枝番木瓜。但我更愿意叫它饭瓜。家乡人都是这么叫的。在我故乡，南瓜花开了，然后又落了。掉在地上，无人问津。更没人注意南瓜苗，那样青青的苗，竟也是一道可口的野蔬。南瓜花，洗净，清炒可食。南瓜苗，要费些功夫，把瓜苗的清皮剥去，露出脆嫩的茎。也是清炒。一盘黄花，灿然开放。一盘青藤，酷似豌豆苗，却又比豌豆苗脆嫩。味之鲜美让人如闻山歌，一曲难忘。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000818": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000818",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000819": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000819",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000820": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000820",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><h2><span style=\"\">第32节：关于故乡，轻描淡写的记忆--南瓜(2)</span></h2></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000821": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000821",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>\t</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000822": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000822",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>后来，我深入壮乡山寨，尝到了一种南瓜糯米饭。壮乡人独特的风味小吃。我在恭城县的观音乡目睹了做南瓜糯米饭的全过程。南瓜黄熟，摘下，存放一段时间，使之糖化。做南瓜糯米饭的方法如下：取熟南瓜，去硬皮，去瓜瓤瓜子，切成大片，入锅煮熟。然后将糯米撒在它上面。再煮。米熟成饭。将瓜和糯米拌匀，即成。无需调料。其味香而清甜。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000823": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000823",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000824": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000824",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>前不久读《本草纲目拾遗》。书上说，南瓜色黄味甘，多补元气，不得以贱而忽之。可是我呢，从小就对南瓜贱而忽之。不过当我来到南方，见到南瓜，竟有他乡遇故知之感，于是就不停地吃，竟也吃出许多感觉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000825": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000825",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000826": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000826",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>每每看到菜市上的南瓜，我就自然想起胖妹。很多年前的那天中午，我扯了一只大南瓜扑到河里去洗。胖妹割野草回来，也在河边洗。她蹲在水边的木码头上。我记得胖妹胆子很小的。我就游过去，摇晃木码头的两根柱子。胖妹神色紧张，吓得直哆嗦。我越发兴奋，用力摇晃。终于，胖妹站立不稳，落下水。她刚割的一篮野草，飘得满河都是。我知道闯了祸。忙去拉她。可是，胖妹越是挣扎，越是往深水处去。慌乱之中，我看见大南瓜，忙抛过去，说你快抱住南瓜。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000827": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000827",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000828": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000828",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>胖妹抱着救命南瓜游到岸边。看到满河飘浮的野草，不停地抽泣。我不知道怎么安慰她。我说我把南瓜给你，你带回去。胖妹怎么也不肯要。末了，兀自提了空篮，缓缓离去。我心里忽然一阵的紧。因为我知道，胖妹的母亲凶得可怕。如果胖妹没有割到野草回来，猪就没得吃。可想而知，胖妹免不了一场皮肉之苦。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000829": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000829",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000830": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000830",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>很多年前的这件往事，因为我写南瓜又被记起。胖妹早就没有了消息。记得我后来回故乡，还是见过胖妹的。有一次在河边遇见她，我们还说了许多话。她是回娘家来的。我问她，以前河边的那件事还记得吗。胖妹想了一下，怎么也想不起来。她说，不会吧，怎么可能呢。她手上捧着个大南瓜，对我说，婆婆要我天天吃南瓜呢。我说为什么啊。胖妹下意识地抚了一下肚子。安详，丰满，羞涩，充满甜味。她也不说，一脸的幸福。我立即明白了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000831": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000831",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000832": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000832",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>秋日寂寥。我依然深入在南方的壮乡瑶寨。我走在心圩江畔。这里有个棚户区。年轻的男女都出去做工。家里的老人，坐在榕树下卖些野菜时蔬。我看到有个年迈的老太坐在小凳上，剥着南瓜苗。一朵黄灿灿的南瓜花插在她苍苍白发上，她的面容多么慈祥。翠绿清亮的南瓜苗在她手中鲜活地跳跃。一个俊俏的姑娘静静地从她身边走过，美丽的眼睛，开满金灿灿的南瓜花。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000833": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000833",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000834": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000834",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000835": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000835",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><h2><span style=\"\">第33节：阳光里摇晃的马车--香蕉(1)</span></h2></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000836": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000836",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>\t</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000837": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000837",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>阳光里摇晃的马车--香蕉</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000838": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000838",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000839": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000839",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>在南方，香蕉乃寻常之物。村头，塘边，屋前屋后或山脚闲散土地都有种植。还有一些丘陵地带，满眼都是成片的香蕉林。天天看见，再美的风光也会索然无味。香蕉熟了，一把把割下，剥了皮吃。没啥感觉。但北方就不一样。北方的香蕉都从南方运过去。北方人没见过香蕉林，不知道香蕉是长在树上还是结在藤上。香蕉没有籽，没有核，也就是说没有种子，那么香蕉又是如何种植的呢。邹韬奋写过一篇《硬吞香蕉皮》，说有个东北官僚在宴会上第一次看到香蕉，不假思索连皮吃下，看得众人目瞪口呆。等一会，看到同座的人是剥了皮再吃的。他又不肯认错，居然一本正经解释说，我向来吃香蕉都是连皮吃下去的。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000840": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000840",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000841": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000841",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>扬州并不属于北方。但二十年前，香蕉于我还是无比的神秘。我生活的扬州城很小，小到很少有香蕉卖。偶尔有也是稀贵，价格高得让人却步。后来有机会到南方。第一站到广州。一下火车就看见许多挑担卖香蕉的。价格极便宜，五毛钱一斤。不管三七二十一，买它五斤回招待所囫囵吞枣饱餐一顿。吃饱了，撑着，肚子滚圆。算是彻底过了一回香蕉瘾。过瘾的快感过去不久，麻烦来了。腹泻。原来，吃的那些香蕉熟烂了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000842": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000842",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000843": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000843",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>还有一个关于香蕉的事，北方人似乎至今也不知道。就连我也是来南方后才知道的。在北方，很多水果买回来就可以吃。认为香蕉也一样。把香蕉割下到市上来卖，当然表示此果已熟，可以吃了。不熟你拿出来做什么。香蕉买回来，很多人迫不及待地剥开皮就吃。那香蕉皮还是青青的。吃在嘴里很生涩，也不香，也不见甜。就纳闷，香蕉也不怎么好吃啊，还那么贵。哪里知道，香蕉不是割下来就可以吃的。需要存放几天，直致表皮黄了，有许多梅花斑点产生，那样的香蕉才算熟，剥开后香气四溢，吃起来绵甜可口。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000844": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000844",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000845": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000845",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>中国古代栽种和采食香蕉，历史久远。香蕉在古代称为甘蕉。《广志》书中称香蕉为芭蕉：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000846": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000846",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000847": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000847",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>或曰甘蕉，茎如荷芋，重皮相裹……剥其上皮，色黄白，味似葡萄，甜而脆，亦饱人。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000848": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000848",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000849": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000849",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>饱人是可想而知的。味似葡萄，实在想像不出是什么品种。还有，甜而脆，怎么会呢，香蕉会脆吗。古人的文字，有时像雾里看花，很玄乎，让你莫衷一是。你不能全信，又不能不信。说不定是灭绝了的一个品种呢。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000850": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000850",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000851": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000851",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>在岭南文化中，有一部非常重要的文献，《岭外代答》，作者宋代周去非。《岭外代答》是周去非惟一传世著作，是他仕于广西时所写的笔记资料。广西在历史上开发较迟，民族多，物产丰富，风俗殊异，中原人颇不熟悉，遂目之为奇异之乡。周去非的这部书，内容繁杂，具有多重史料价值，堪称不朽之作。其中，香蕉在宋代，是这样一种情形：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000852": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000852",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000853": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000853",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>芭蕉，极大者凌冬不凋，中抽一干，节节有花如菡萏。花谢有实，一穗数枚，如肥皂，长数寸。去皮取肉，软烂如绿柿，极甘冷。四季实。以梅汁渍，暴干按匾，所云&quot;芭蕉干&quot;是也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000854": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000854",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000855": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000855",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>鸡蕉（即牛乳蕉），则甚小，亦四季实。芽蕉（即羊角蕉），小如鸡蕉，尤香嫩甘美，南人珍之，非他蕉比。秋初方实。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000856": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000856",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000857": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000857",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>--宋·周去非《岭外代答·蕉子》</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000858": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000858",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000859": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000859",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>鸡蕉，现在的邕城街头，都可见到。比拇指大不了多少。我尝过一些，感觉很甜。但是，在古代，鸡蕉的最大作用，却是用来喂婴儿的。许多地方志中，均有鸡蕉喂婴的记载。《邕宁县志》云：鸡蕉，又名观音蕉，树高八九尺，实小而香甜，性平，可饲小儿。《龙津县志》云：鸡蕉者，味清香甜淡无毒，人多以为哺婴孩之用。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000860": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000860",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000861": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000861",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>清代医家赵学敏所撰《本草纲目拾遗》中，述及南方民间用香蕉喂婴的做法。若产妇乳汁少，婴儿吃不饱，可用香蕉喂之。书中还说，用香蕉浸酒，味甚美。不知是香蕉味美还是酒味美，反正是味美，很诱人。家中还有半坛老酒。香蕉切块，浸入。封严。几日开坛，酒味蕉香扑鼻，饮之，绵甜爽口，果然好。得此佳酿半盏，挑灯听雨，赏砚，读画，快何如哉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000862": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000862",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000863": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000863",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>南方多雨。窗外几棵芭蕉，一片清绿。雨打芭蕉自古就令人销魂。雨点落在蕉叶上，柔情万种。蕉叶极美。我藏有一方老坑端砚。给几个行家看，皆言蕉叶白。蕉叶白为端石中佼佼者。产于肇庆羚羊峡北岸坑。石质坚润、色青，纹理间有纯白如蕉叶者，故名。此蕉叶白，如蕉叶初展，一片娇嫩，白中略带青黄。古人对蕉叶白评价极高：浑成一片，净嫩如柔肌，如凝脂。这是我收藏的几方老坑砚之一，秘不示人。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000864": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000864",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000865": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000865",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000866": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000866",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><h2><span style=\"\">第34节：阳光里摇晃的马车--香蕉(2)</span></h2></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000867": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000867",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>\t</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000868": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000868",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>由小小的蕉叶白，忽然想到几片硕大的蕉叶。此为《芭蕉美人图》，明代画家姜隐之妙品。芭蕉苍翠浓郁，湖石雄古奇崛，地面芳草萋萋。一美貌女子亭亭玉立于葱茏的芭蕉旁，等同伴来弈棋。她的神情淡然而清纯，姿容娇媚。她是谁。此等闲雅气质几百年来令无数男子为之心仪，为之嗟叹。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000869": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000869",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000870": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000870",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>晋代嵇含所著《南方草木状》，开篇就是写香蕉。当时是叫甘蕉：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000871": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000871",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000872": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000872",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>甘蕉，望之如树，株大者一围余。叶长一丈，或七、八尺，广尺余、二尺许。花大如酒杯，形色如芙蓉，著茎末百余。子大，名为房，相连累，甜美，亦可密藏。根如芋魁，大者如车毂。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000873": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000873",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000874": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000874",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>香蕉开花，我是见过的。很大，如尖荷。但香蕉是没有籽和核的。如何种植呢，原来，是取根部的芽栽植。春季萌发的芽，形似竹笋，叶片细小如剑，此为剑芽；还有一种，褛衣芽。从地下的茎部萌发，由于冬后叶片干枯下垂，形似破衣衫，故名。把这些芽栽种，不久就长成一片翠绿的香蕉林。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000875": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000875",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000876": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000876",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>香蕉一大串，重几十斤，都以为它是长在树上的。其实不是。高达十数米的香蕉竟然不是树，而是草本植物。香蕉是结在草上的浆果。香蕉在采摘时是青色的，其形状有人说像象牙，其实不像。象牙是由粗到细。百色产芒果，有一种象牙芒，那才酷似象牙。街上卖的芭蕉也不错。只是身材短小。最近，芭蕉的价格一直超过香蕉。因为产量低，种的人少。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000877": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000877",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000878": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000878",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>我来南方之后，吃了不少的香蕉与芭蕉，都是她买的。很多时候，她拎着沉沉的香蕉回来，满头是汗。买回来的香蕉在茶几上放着，在我一天天的注目中，蕉皮上的梅花斑一点点多起来。蕉香也一阵阵透过。像她从我身边走过时飘来的体香。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000879": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000879",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000880": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000880",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>香蕉这样的植物，只适合于南方。她只适合于蛮烟瘴雨。白天，她并不张扬，尤其是她的叶片，即使是在风中，也是秀丽，娴静，婉转，像在山坡上遥望我的那个女子。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000881": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000881",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000882": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000882",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000883": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000883",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><h2><span style=\"\">第35节：盛满时间的陶罐--东源板栗</span></h2></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000884": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000884",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>\t</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000885": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000885",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>盛满时间的陶罐--东源板栗</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000886": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000886",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000887": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000887",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>板栗与桃、杏、李、枣并称五果。南北方都有。其香糯味美，一直是普通百姓的休闲佳品。非常奇怪的是，北方的板栗，个小，与北方的浑厚大气并不相称；而南方的板栗，与那些大块头的热带水果很相似，个大饱满，吃得很过瘾。来南方后，往来桂林无数次。桂林街头到处都是板栗，问之，皆阳朔产。阳朔板栗是广西名果，种植历史悠久，其中以果红板栗品质最好，其果皮呈赤褐色，油亮光泽，饱满粒大，肉色嫩黄，可生食，极脆甜，若熟食，则粉甜清香。熟食常用于包粽子、蒸年糕、做八宝饭、焖肉等。桂林的名菜板栗鸭，即用正宗阳朔板栗做原料，名震南国。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000888": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000888",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000889": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000889",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>但是南方又不仅仅是阳朔产板栗的。百越大地植物之繁多，水果之丰富远远超出我们的想像。很多时候我奔波在岭南腹地。我常常一个人，从邕城坐火车在百越大地上行走。黎塘，贵港，玉林，河唇，茂名，阳春，肇庆，佛山等地让我流连忘返。我喜欢这些地方的原因是，这里的植物像一个巨大的隐喻，冲破了时间的屏障。我穿梭在百越大地如同穿行在现实与时空之间，我甚至可以闻见遥远的蛮烟瘴雨的气息。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000890": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000890",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000891": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000891",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>板栗是大自然的馈赠。适应性强，我国南北都有种植。树高七八米，三五年结果，十年后进入盛产期。单株产量上百斤，寿命可达三百年以上。李时珍说：其壳生黄熟紫，壳内有膜裹仁，九月霜降乃熟，其苞自裂而子坠者，乃可久藏，苞未裂者易腐也。其花作条，大如箸头，长四五寸，可以点灯。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000892": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000892",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000893": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000893",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>我在很多年前到过河源。到过苏家围。那时我还不知道东源板栗。直到后来，出生在龙川县的黄美英老师送我几包东源板栗，我才知道这岭南佳果。黄老师是岭南散文作家，我是她的忠实读者。阅读她的作品让我感受到一种来自山野的质朴与安静。安静是一种力量。这种力量像坚实的栗果，它能让人听到来自大山深处的深沉与共鸣。有一次，我读到了她的这样一段文字：&quot;板栗成熟了，栗色的果实从球刺里爆裂开来，一阵风过，板栗就掉下来了。在树下寻找板栗，一颗一颗的惊喜。&quot;</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000894": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000894",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000895": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000895",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>很多时候，我被这样明润而清澈的文字感动。每次阅读总会有一种漫过心灵的温暖。她把自己诚实的感知交给了文字，她的散文有一种单纯而又驳杂开阔的美丽。一边品尝东源板栗，一边咀嚼黄老师的文字，我仿佛旧地重游，来到了河源。那简单、诚实、聪睿、美好的文字，是经得起时间长河淘洗的。就像我看到的那一种枝叶茂密的植物，树冠丰满，树阴浓郁。长在深山，沐浴山风。这就是岭南腹地鲜为人知的佳果，东源板栗。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000896": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000896",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000897": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000897",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>黄老师赠我的板栗，有个好听的名字，叫望郎回。板栗外形玲珑，色泽鲜艳，不粘内皮。果仁呈米黄色，糯性强，甘甜芳香，口感极佳。当年游览河源，便记得这个望郎回的地方。距河源城十多华里的白岭头，路左侧约二里许，有圆锥状石山一座，突兀而出，石山壁立，高千尺。有小径蜿蜒，可至山顶。远看此山酷似美人挽髻伫立，祈盼归人。山脚下有一对脚印向着东江。那石山有个流传很广的故事。一女子思夫心切，日复一日，年复一年，风雨无阻登此山顶望夫回来。天长日久，便踏出一对脚印，人们便把此山叫做&quot;望郎回&quot;。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000898": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000898",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000899": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000899",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>此妇何人？夫妇为何分离？和东源板栗又有何关联？后来，黄老师告诉了我这样一个故事：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000900": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000900",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000901": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000901",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>在美丽的东江河畔，住着一户普通人家。一家三口，在东江打鱼为生。女儿英英，正是豆蔻年华，生得桃唇柳眉，轻盈体态，举止落落，堪称小家碧玉，其父母爱若掌上明珠。朝出晚归，逢集卖鱼，一家人的生活，倒也过得去。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000902": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000902",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000903": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000903",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>不远处有座破庙，一个书生寄住在那里，早晚苦读。英英一家打鱼归来，天色已晚，远远就能看到江边破庙里的油灯。久而久之，这盏油灯，成了英英一家的灯塔，照着他们的小渔船晚归。经过庙旁，那书生的朗朗之声，如潮般涌来英英的心房。她爱上了他。有时，她在他门前放一条鱼，有时，她卖了鱼，再买些栗子带给他。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000904": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000904",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000905": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000905",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>英英的父母也是善良之人，见书生刻苦读书，心生喜欢。郎才女貌，虽是穷苦人家，倒也是幸福的一对。择日成亲，把书生接回家里。没过多久，一个黑色的日子降临了。山下有个大户人家，丁姓，财大气粗，横行乡里，无恶不作。又豢养一班家奴，为其打手。此人外号丁庄主。乡人痛恨，然敢怒不敢言。一日，丁庄主带领家丁进山打猎，遇见美丽的英英在溪边浣衣，惊叹良久，以为仙女下凡。顿起歪心，拦住英英。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000906": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000906",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000907": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000907",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>眼看丁庄主就要抱住英英。就在这时，一阵狂风吹过，只听得噼噼啪啪的声音，天空中忽然落下无数的卵石，把丁庄主一伙砸得抱头鼠窜，落荒而逃。英英仔细一看，不是卵石，而是坚硬的栗子。她感到奇怪，这里哪来的栗树呢。回家后就问书生。书生说，我种的。你每次买给我的栗子，我都舍不得吃。我去买了一些栗种在这里，开花结果了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000908": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000908",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000909": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000909",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>然而，丁庄主并不因此善罢甘休。他对英英的美貌早已垂涎三尺。买通县令，强征书生充军千里外。英英一家遭此大祸，悲痛欲绝。书生说，我会回来的。你等我！一定要等我！说罢，夫妻抱头痛哭，依依作别。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000910": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000910",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000911": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000911",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>此后，英英无时不思念丈夫早日归来，数十年如一日，攀登巨石之巅，遥望东江归帆，以泪洗面望郎回。冬去春来，雁来雁去，丈夫还是音信全无。盼望何时了？何时了？脚印一双深陷了。英英最终化作一尊石像，遥望着远方。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000912": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000912",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000913": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000913",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>黄老师说完了。我问，后来呢，那个丁庄主的阴谋得逞了吗？黄老师笑着说，朗朗乾坤，有阴谋，更有太阳。英英自书生走后，又种了许多的栗子树。丁庄主又来找英英，奇怪的是，每次来，都被爆裂的栗子砸得头破血流。吃了几次大亏，丁庄主隐隐明白什么，隐姓埋名，远走他乡。所以，在我的故乡河源一带，任何做坏事的人，都要被栗子砸头的。而那些心地善良之人，将会有幸品尝到英英种下的甜美香糯的望郎回板栗。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000914": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000914",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000915": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000915",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>卷三</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000916": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000916",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000917": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000917",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000918": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000918",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><h2><span style=\"\">第36节：十丈珊瑚--木棉花(1)</span></h2></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000919": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000919",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>\t</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000920": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000920",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>十丈珊瑚--木棉花</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000921": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000921",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000922": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000922",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>早知道无缘何必怨相逢，往日情永远留在我的心怀。说无缘也好，诉无分也罢。这段情已渐渐迷路……--电视连续剧《木棉花的春天》插曲</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000923": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000923",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000924": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000924",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>我花了一天一夜的时间看完了《木棉花的春天》。我不明白的是，一部漏洞百出的情感电视剧何以能如此吸引我，并且，居然数度让我眼眶湿润。故事俗而老套。爱恨情仇，富家小姐看上穷小子，百般磨难，有情人终成眷属。具体的情节已经沓远，俊男靓女也已模糊。可我心中还时时记挂着这部编造拙劣的电视剧。真是奇怪。为生计奔波途中或者夜阑人静，脑海中总是响起剧中荡气回肠的旋律。还有剧中美丽丰饶的南国风光：清朗明丽的瀑布，大片翠绿的茶园，还有一幕幕火红的画面。那是木棉花。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000925": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000925",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000926": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000926",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>来南国之前我对木棉花一无所知。惟一的印象，是读舒婷的《致橡树》：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000927": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000927",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000928": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000928",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>我必须是你近旁的一株木棉，作为树的形象和你站在一起。根，紧握在地下叶，相触在云里。每一阵风过我们都互相致意，但没有人听懂我们的言语。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000929": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000929",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000930": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000930",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>从那时起知道有一种木棉树，并且开花。并不知道木棉花是什么形状，是什么颜色，只隐约知道，木棉花是和爱情联系在一起的。《木棉花的春天》的导演很会运用木棉花作为道具并极尽渲染之能事，让主人公的命运随着木棉树的生长，花开花落，让屏幕前的观众为之牵肠挂肚欲罢不能。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000931": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000931",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000932": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000932",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>我来到南国正是木棉花盛开的季节。我行走在邕城的江南路与白沙大道。这里是邕城木棉树最集中的地方。我第一次看见如此高大如此热烈的木棉树，心灵被一种强烈的燃烧震撼。我看见木棉树高大的树干伸向蔚蓝的天空，满街高耸的木棉树上，清一色大朵大朵绚烂的木棉花占满枝头，没有青枝绿叶，满眼云蒸霞蔚，一路密密的燃烧远去，直至天边。这是何等气势，何等壮观。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000933": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000933",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000934": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000934",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>木棉最早见载于晋代葛洪著的《西京杂记》：积草池中有珊瑚树，高一丈二尺，一本三。……是南越王赵佗所献。号为烽火木。至夜光景常欲燃。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000935": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000935",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000936": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000936",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>烽火树即木棉树。现在南越王庙还在，在岭南龙川县。我的朋友黄美英老师就生活在龙川县。我说，我想去龙川看木棉树，南越王进贡的那一种。黄老师说，龙川的木棉树多在山谷里。有机会我带你去看南海神庙的木棉树吧。黄老师说南海神庙前曾有十余株木棉树，颇为古老，每年旧历二月，木棉花盛开，每天人如潮涌，观者达数千人，场面热闹。清屈大均以《南海神祠古木棉花歌》颂之：十丈珊瑚是木棉，花开红比朝霞鲜。现在南海神庙仍有两棵古木棉树，久经风霜，挺拔依然。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000937": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000937",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000938": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000938",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000939": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000939",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><h2><span style=\"\">第37节：十丈珊瑚--木棉花(2)</span></h2></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000940": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000940",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>\t</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000941": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000941",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>木棉树是一种乔木，高大魁梧，是一种很特别很有性格的树种。最奇怪的是，它先开花，后长叶。木棉树生长速度快，观赏性强。树冠总是极力地高出周围的树群，以争取阳光雨露滋润。春天开花时见不到一片绿叶，当朵朵木棉花全部掉落以后，光秃秃的树枝才开始抽出嫩绿的新芽。果实为蒴果，成熟后会自动裂开，吐出云一样花絮。木棉飞絮，是岭南一景。风一吹，花絮便随风飘舞，天地都鲜活起来。深深的月光，长长的水色，暖暖的艳阳，一片交融，正是这个季节里最美的诗章。岭南人以木棉为棉絮，所谓衣裁木上棉。做棉衣、棉被、枕垫，又织之为毯，洁白如雪，温暖无比。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000942": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000942",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000943": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000943",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>这是一种多么让人神往的植物。在春天，叶子还没有生长的情况下，木棉花说开就开了，不需要任何条件。一场雨水后绽放的木棉花，如同长久寂寞之后的喧闹。那花开得很张扬，每一朵花都是那么恣意盎然，屹立枝头。花开了，总有谢的时候。木棉花的凋谢也很奇特，不是飘落，而是毫不犹豫，坚定而执著，带着悲壮，毅然从枝头飞落，啪！掷地有声。理想。单纯。疯狂。热烈。高贵。一团令人窒息、令人炫目的烈焰，跌落在我面前。多么像爱情。这样坚定而悲壮的飞落惊心动魄，如同流星划过夜空。闪亮，然后熄灭。譬如绿珠。譬如杜十娘。譬如尤三姐。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000944": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000944",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000945": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000945",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>所有的花卉中，玫瑰花约定俗成，成了爱情的代名词。就花卉的品格与象征意义而言，木棉花则更接近于爱情的本质。事实上，《木棉花的春天》中的木棉花，就是爱情的象征。很多时候，我们并不明白爱情，或者说我们并不真正拥有爱情。所谓门当户对，所谓郎才女貌等等，都与爱情无关。于是，灰姑娘与王子，穷书生与富小姐，就成了爱情的传奇剧从古代上演到今天。其实，爱情并不神秘，甚至如同小女孩那样明白单纯。可是，大家不愿意得到爱情，很轻率地对爱情视而不见，或者践踏爱情。内心寻找却又不愿意得到。到头来，只能对着屏幕上拙劣的爱情故事唏嘘感叹。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000946": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000946",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000947": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000947",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>今年春天，一家人去看了德天跨国瀑布。《木棉花的春天》中频繁出现的瀑布景观就是在这里拍摄的。正是春水季节，宽阔的大瀑布飞流直下。河对岸是越南起伏的群山。崖草泛青，山花吐蕊，木棉花盛开，归春河两岸一片红霞。在红花万朵丛中，德天瀑布犹如一匹银色素洁的白练，轻盈欢快地飞舞。后来又去明仕田园。《木棉花的春天》很多场景，也是在这里取景。这是一处世外桃源，明仕河曲折盘旋，清澈宁静，两岸的凤尾竹修然亭立，竹梢下垂随风轻摆，岸上，蕉吐新绿，木棉花开了。红艳的木棉花，野火似的一路烧来，在我内心深处涌起一缕浓浓的暖意。四周的风景都在感动。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000948": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000948",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000949": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000949",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>这些日子我在岭南的山间行走。我在寻找木棉花。我已经感到了她的声响，色彩，和温暖的气息。我感到木棉花渐渐改变了我忧郁的面孔。我要给自己种一株木棉树让她幸福地生长，我要为那些燃烧的木棉花写一首温暖的诗歌。听见了吗。时间如溪水般淹没了我的青春。我们都在时间里生息，然后在时间里消亡。时间像沙漏里的沙粒那样不停地流淌。多少日子来了，又旧了。在这过程中我们想抓住些什么，譬如飞落的木棉花。可是生命却在指间瞬息流逝。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000950": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000950",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000951": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000951",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>蛮烟瘴雨，一个熟悉而陌生的声音在山谷里飘荡--榕树</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000952": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000952",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000953": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000953",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000954": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000954",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><h2><span style=\"\">第38节：蛮烟瘴雨，一个熟悉而陌生的声音在山谷里飘荡--榕树(1)</span></h2></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000955": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000955",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>\t</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000956": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000956",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>很多年前，我到过福建，曾在宁德山村和乡镇之间行走将近两个月。一座我至今都无法忘怀的南方城市。海边那些湿漉漉的山岩和满是热带风情的翠绿植物成为我对南国的最初记忆。榕树是第一次见。初来南方，很多植物扑面而来，目不暇接，对榕树并没有留下多么深的印象。惟一记住的是它的繁茂、宽宏和气势磅礴。从榕树的榕字，我想到另一个字，容，一个类似大肚能容的形象。我想继续无限深入，探究榕树里的秘密。许多年过去，却始终没有机会再和榕树相遇。我所见到的，更多是些落叶乔木与灌木丛。与榕树相比，寻常树木怎么看都像是鸡肠小肚。但我的潜意识之中，一直有棵榕树存在。一棵硕大的榕树总是在我梦中出现。那时候我在阳光下眺望山野，它在同一个地方出现了很多次。好像总有阳光。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000957": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000957",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000958": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000958",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>在邕城，我见到了满街榕树。朝阳广场上的榕树很奇特，枝干贴地生长，很多人，就躺在斜斜的树干上，像栖息在树上的鸟。他们居然可以酣然入睡而不会滚落下来。每次经过朝阳广场，我都会停下脚步看那些树上的人。我想，在很久以前，蛮烟瘴雨的洪荒年代，这些壮族的先民们是否就这样在树上生活过。那些蛛网似的气根在风中千丝万缕，多么像垂挂的珠帘。南方的阳光很猛烈，几棵榕树，就遮蔽了整个广场。静静地走在巨大的榕树下，心里变得单纯而孤寂。寄蜉蝣于天地，渺沧海之一粟。坦坦荡荡，心间广宽，一片空灵。空灵的心，方盛得下许多世事风雨吧。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000959": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000959",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000960": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000960",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>邕城的榕树最集中的地方，在南湖边。这里是榕树王国。那些榕树之庞大，奇特，怪异，皆闻所未闻。常见一种情景，林间小道上，烟雾缥缈，又有阳光的照射，透出热带雨林一样的神秘。此景多在午后。步入南湖边的榕树林，只见榕树的树干、树枝间源源不断涌出一缕缕乳白色的雾，然后散发在空中，弥漫在青碧的草地上。几百棵大榕树浸在雾中，烟雾缭绕。雾锁榕树园的场面十分壮观。真应了那句诗，蛮烟瘴雨溪州路，溪边桃李花如雾。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000961": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000961",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000962": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000962",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>很晚了，南湖边灯火还在不知疲倦地闪烁，我看见一些水鸟平整地一条线掠过水面往南而去。夜色终于掩盖了那些榕树。鸟们也收好翅膀归巢了。我在榕树林里轻轻地走，不想吵醒任何生命。我假装一切都没发生，睡在这些巨大沉默的榕树之下，做一个与它们无关的梦。偶尔有一些细密的风像低语从不知什么方向吹拂过来，整个榕树林像一个巨大的谜。还有一些喁喁私语和轻微的响声。我渐渐睡着了。梦从远方赶来。似乎有一双明媚的眼睛向我俯视并向我靠近。我不知道她是谁。黎明时也许我会发现她留下的馨香和轻盈的脚印。夜晚目睹了一切，却默然不语。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000963": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000963",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000964": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000964",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>心圩江桥西不远处，有棵巨大的古榕，它站在那儿已经多年了。是一棵粗壮的榕树，在人行道上孤零零地挺立，保持着一种倔强的姿态。我为生计奔波的时候，无数次从它身旁经过，注视它的皱纹，倾听风经过时它的叶子发出的悉悉之声。我不知道在我遇见它之前，它看见过什么。我不知道有多少人从它的身旁走过。它的躯体上有一些记号，是刻痕，或深或浅。没人知道那是什么。仿佛与生俱来一般。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000965": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000965",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000966": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000966",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>但是它只有一半。这棵榕树只有半个身躯。它仍然以一种挺立的姿势耸立在心圩江桥畔。我每次走过，都能听见它发出的无数轰鸣声。仿佛是山谷里湍急的流水，像两岸的松涛一样笼罩四野。那感觉让我惊悚。我看见无数身材矮小的百越人身着斑斓彩衣，戴着傩面具唱着山歌在榕树下起舞。他们马步而立，两手屈肘平举，祈求神灵保佑。他们长着夸张的耳朵，面部黝黑且文身。神灵真的来了。在一个闷热的中午，低垂的云脚，在看不见的远处与大地交接，雷声从那里滚来。风声雨声在榕树的叶子上呼啸而过。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000967": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000967",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000968": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000968",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000969": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000969",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><h2><span style=\"\">第39节：蛮烟瘴雨，一个熟悉而陌生的声音在山谷里飘荡--榕树(2)</span></h2></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000970": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000970",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>\t</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000971": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000971",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>一把白亮的剑，自空中斜刺而来。雨水朦胧，雷声轰然而至。榕树剧烈地颤抖，枝叶抽搐，扭动。咔嚓。伴随着声响，痛苦正流过它的身体。雷，击中了它。凌空劈开。另一半，发出沉沉的吼声，像受伤的巨人缓慢扑倒。它躯体斑驳，显示出它所经历的漫长岁月。像迟暮的英雄，它惟一可以炫耀的是仍能敞开胸怀接纳雷电与风雨。它的气根仍能像藤蔓一样肆意延伸。那天晚上，骤然清朗。夜空中一颗耀目的星斗在西北方向划过，陨落在山那边潮一样的瀑布中。到那里，要经过此榕树，并且要翻过一座山峰。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000972": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000972",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000973": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000973",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>我相信很久以前的榕字的原始意义，就含有容的意思。有容乃大。包容，一个博大而温暖的词。最近欣赏了李安导演的《色戒》。我以为王佳芝最后放走易先生，最终体现的是爱的包容。她包容了易先生所有的被认为的罪行。我相信她当时并没有想到任何的后果，无论是派她暗杀的一方，还是易先生。那时她眼里的易先生是已钻入她内心的男人，而不属于哪一派哪一方。同样，在斯·茨威格的小说《一个陌生女人的来信》（张玉书译）中，陌生女人的爱与包容同样做到了极致。很多人以为，这封信是陌生女人饱含满腔的痛苦和哀怨的诉说，是对她一生付出的讨还。其实不是。如果那样解读是很狭隘的，也是对爱的一种亵渎。陌生女人的爱，包容了他的一切，包括他的风流放荡。爱情的高贵就在于此，它是一个人的情感。我爱你，但于你无关。它不容许有任何的附着条件。当爱情在心灵上滋生的时候，它所产生的力量能给人以震撼，可以摧毁一切枷锁。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000974": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000974",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000975": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000975",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>短短的《色戒》花了张爱玲将近三十年的时间。这也是汉语文学史上的一件异事。我相信当她完成这部作品的时候，主人公易先生无论是影射丁默村还是胡兰成，对她来说都不重要。重要的是，爱战胜了一切。张爱玲说，她还是真爱他的，是他生平第一个红粉知己。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000976": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000976",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000977": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000977",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>邕城的榕树真是壮观。在桂林也曾见过一棵硕大美丽的榕树。那是永久地印记在脑海中了。南方的风，和煦而又热烈，在铺天盖地的榕树上落下一阵又一阵。浓密的榕树叶在风中舞动，像一团团墨绿色擦抹在蔚蓝的天际。那是怎样的一种温暖啊。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000978": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000978",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000979": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000979",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000980": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000980",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><h2><span style=\"\">第40节：苦涩的忧伤因你而回味生津--苦瓜</span></h2></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000981": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000981",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>\t</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000982": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000982",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>苦涩的忧伤因你而回味生津--苦瓜</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000983": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000983",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000984": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000984",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>苦瓜是寻常物，不稀贵，想吃就吃。有人不喜欢，因为苦，哪有自找苦吃的。我喜欢。清炒苦瓜。切块，清炒。一盘的青翠，看着就喜欢。若想更好看，加红菜椒点缀，红红绿绿，很让人开怀。除了出盘好看，更多的人是喜欢苦瓜的清苦味，这是别种蔬菜无法替代的。虽然味苦，吃苦瓜的人从未间断--大量的苦瓜在市面上卖。苦瓜以嫩果和成熟果实供食用。嫩果果肉柔嫩，清脆，味稍苦而清甘可口。成熟果实内的血红色瓜瓤味甜清香，也可食用。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000985": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000985",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000986": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000986",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>更多的时候，我喜欢吃青嫩的苦瓜。来南方尝过的苦味，有苦丁茶，苦而后甘。王老吉，那才是一种苦，苦得令人咋舌--多数人受不了，但我喝过几次--像喝烈酒一样，一口一口咽下--超市里卖的王老吉都是变了味的，加了糖，严格说来，那不是王老吉了。还有咖啡。来南方之后，喝咖啡的机会多，邕城的大小咖啡馆基本上都去品尝过。我常常喝炭烧。不加奶与糖，味虽苦，可苦中有香，回味良久。苦瓜呢，有清香气，还没有苦到王老吉那种程度，多数人能接受。以前在家，母亲知我嗜苦瓜，常常会专门炒一盘苦瓜，给我下酒。他们都不太喜欢吃苦瓜。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000987": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000987",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000988": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000988",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>苦甜酸辣诸般滋味品尝过，便有了选择。譬如，我不太喜欢青橄榄。橄榄是有很多人吃的，只是，苦得青涩，又甜得夸张。本来是开胃之物，最后弄得满嘴的味蕾失调，所有食物吃到嘴里都没有味道。苦瓜不一样。苦瓜被誉为菜中君子。苦瓜和别的菜搭配，不把自身苦味传给对方。照我吃苦瓜的经验，吃苦瓜宜一人独饮，不必烈酒，酒一辣，苦瓜的味就没了。宜饮啤酒。可以坐在窗前，一人独品。那时你的思绪很远。投视窗外，仍是那半山苍茫的月，无言地注视。偶有一缕深寒的风像苦味一般流过全身。那是熟悉得不能再熟悉的人生光景。只有这时才可看见，那一路走来的荆棘，正开着白莲花。所有的苦味，扩宽了人生的容量。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000989": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000989",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000990": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000990",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>苦瓜，因味苦得名。一年生草本，开黄花。果实纺锤形或长圆筒形，果面有瘤状突起，熟时黄赤色。未熟嫩果可作蔬菜。多数人吃苦瓜的目的，是除邪热，解劳乏，清心明目，益气壮阳。苦瓜的形状很奇特，就有了很多别名，雅俗都有。癞瓜、癞葡萄、癞蛤蟆、红姑娘、凉瓜、君子菜等。这些名字中，还有个苦瓜和尚。苦瓜总是让我想到石涛大师。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000991": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000991",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000992": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000992",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>很多人都知道苦瓜和尚。很少人知道大师为何要取这么一个别号。传说的版本很多。还是从他的另一个别号大涤子说起吧。当年，我住在寄啸山庄里的片石山房，那里有一座被誉为人间孤本的小山，即石涛堆叠。那小山上，灌木丛生，还长苦瓜。石涛别号很多，苦瓜和尚，清湘陈人，瞎尊者等都很有名。大涤子最为世人熟知。关于这一别号，众说纷纭，有各样解释。细读石涛代表作《余杭看山图》，大涤子别号之由来，一代宗师深邃而隐秘的内心世界，或可窥见一斑。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000993": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000993",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000994": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000994",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>翻开石涛全集，有一幅作品，其风格与石涛其他作品截然不同。画面构图雅洁高远，整体气势，给人以风起云涌的感觉。此卷就是《余杭看山图》。这是石涛晚年精品。图中款识，左右两处，右上款题诗：湖外青青大涤山，写来寄去浑茫间。不知果是余杭道，纸上重游老眼闲。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000995": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000995",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000996": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000996",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>由是观之，此卷描绘的是浙江余杭南部的大涤山。江南青山，明媚锦绣，写入画</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000997": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000997",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000998": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000998",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>卷理应赏心悦目，至少意境清新，春意盎然，方能显示江南山清水秀特征。此画则不然。石涛摒弃传统笔法，通篇山势，用画水法为之。水波为柔，山石为刚，以柔示刚，险笔也。非大手笔不能做到。观者欣赏这幅作品，无不在胸中顿生波涛汹涌之感。这感受让人陡生疑惑：石涛似乎在表现什么，或者，在向人们暗示什么。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000999": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000000999",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001000": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001000",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>大涤山为余杭胜迹，有道观大涤洞天，为道教三十六洞天之一。石涛游大涤山，从他生平行踪推测，大约在25岁左右。其时道教在大涤山已经没落，大涤山渐趋荒凉。但是让石涛在此流连忘返，在他年轻的心中掀起狂澜，并且决定用大涤子作为他常用别号的，却是大涤山的另一个悲壮激昂的故事。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001001": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001001",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001002": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001002",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>大涤山是抗清名将黄道周的故地。黄道周是南明朝廷礼部尚书。早年曾在铜山孤岛石室中读书，因号石斋。其书法独特，自成一家。南京失守后，黄道周与程邃等人啸聚山林，回到他从前开坛讲学的大涤山，谋求复明大业。然而壮志未酬，往江西征集军队，行至婺源时为清兵所俘，后在南京遇难。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001003": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001003",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001004": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001004",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>这里牵涉到一个由来已久的话题：石涛的气节。石涛在南京扬州两次接驾，并且做诗歌颂新朝。对此颇有微词的，首推黄宾虹和石涛研究专家郑拙庐两先生。他们认为石涛是明朝王孙，早已削发做了和尚，却两次接驾，对新朝歌功颂德，这是变节行为，是不能原谅的。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001005": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001005",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001006": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001006",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>这对石涛是多么苛求。石涛与朱耷、渐江的情形不同。朱耷和渐江的人生际遇如出一辙，清兵入侵，断送了他们的锦绣前程，他们对清王朝视若水火，是一种刻骨铭心的仇恨。石涛则不同，明亡时石涛仅三岁，国破家亡的痛苦，无法感触，但自己是明代遗民，这是无法改变的事实，潜意识中，他对满清的抵触情绪，也在内心滋长。他没有去清廷为官，岂止如此，他用了这样两个世人皆知又让人费思的古怪别号：苦瓜和尚，瞎尊者。苦瓜何解？石涛双目明亮，又何以称瞎尊者？传说版本很多。较流行的说法是：苦瓜者，皮青，瓤朱红，寓意身在满清，心记朱明；瞎尊者，失明也，寓意为失去明朝。失明之人，岂有不想复明之理。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001007": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001007",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001008": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001008",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>石涛路过大涤山，听到了黄石斋的事迹，凭吊了黄氏讲学的石公坛，心中骤然涌起了一股强烈的对故国的怀念，对失去的家园产生无比的依恋与渴望。这种故国情结深深地埋藏在石涛的心底，伴随他一生，越到晚年，这情结越浓烈。无法排遣之际，付诸笔墨，把早年拜谒过并且藏于心胸的大涤山描绘出来。从此，石涛便有了另一个具有非常意义的别号：大涤子。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001009": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001009",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001010": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001010",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>我藏有石涛的全集。我吃苦瓜喝啤酒的时候，自然而然地想起了这位令我敬佩的艺术大师。我时常翻开这部沉重的画集。我感受到了大涤山非同寻常的气势，感到画面上的苦瓜和尚与瞎尊者这两方钤印异常醒目。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001011": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001011",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001012": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001012",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001013": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001013",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><h2><span style=\"\">第41节：打翻夏天雨水的一枚青杏--荸荠(1)</span></h2></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001014": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001014",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>\t</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001015": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001015",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>打翻夏天雨水的一枚青杏--荸荠</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001016": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001016",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001017": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001017",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>写荸荠，是因为读归有光。早年对古文下过一番工夫。至今能背诵的作品，归有光有两篇，《项脊轩志》，《寒花葬志》。中国古代散文，对我写作风格影响最大的是《项脊轩志》。当然，唐宋八大家我也是喜欢。不知为什么，始终不及《项脊轩志》给我如此长久的回味。《寒花葬志》几百字，顺带背下来。归有光这两篇，在结尾处异曲同工。读归氏作品，那些平白文字并没有多少波澜，可给人内心带来的却是无比震撼。每每读着，如品香醪，称赏不已。想着人生种种，真是太多的虚幻，曾执意追求的富贵功名，到最后，也不过是云烟过眼，自贻伊戚而已。想想，不免心冷。尽管如此，还是有一缕温暖始终如煦风般缭绕心头，像阳光一样时时照在心灵最深处。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001018": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001018",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001019": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001019",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>小小荸荠和一个婢女名字联系在一起，虽只寥寥数笔，却载入中国文学史册。归有光是明代嘉靖进士，曾任太仆寺丞，其职位相当于今天社科院院士。&quot;一日，天寒，爇火煮荸荠熟。婢削之盈瓯。予入自外，取食之，婢持去，不与。魏孺人笑之。&quot;归有光为一个婢女写下这篇生动的文字。那天很冷。家中正在烧火煮荸荠，寒花将已煮熟的荸荠一个个削好盛在小瓦盆中，已盛满了。归有光从外面回来，伸手就要拿来吃。寒花一把挡住了他，把荸荠藏到身后，不给他。说，你好馋！这是给夫人吃的，就不给你吃！</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001020": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001020",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001021": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001021",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>这是一个招人喜欢、惹人爱怜的小丫头。寒花为婢女，年龄不大，却很懂事。叫她一起吃饭，却扭捏着不肯。削好的荸荠，太诱人了，那一种白，像什么呢，对了，就像寒花小小的玉腕。那又是一种什么白呢。归有光实在想不出。那就叫它荸荠白吧。有人说，那是一种玉白。不是。荸荠白不是玉白。玉白是柔和的，荸荠白像瓷色。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001022": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001022",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001023": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001023",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>当年在故乡也有荸荠吃。自家种。荸荠是一年生草本植物，水田边极容易生长。选个大、色泽好、芽充实、无破损的球茎做种。开春，就可育苗。在整好的苗田里，用苇席做圈，圈内铺湿稻草，将荸荠顶芽向上。上盖稻草，催芽。每天洒水，保持湿润。渐渐长出新芽，有三四个芽尖，即可播种育苗。苗田先上水，再将荸荠按入泥中，保持浅水，即可。常灌水。不久长出丛生细长的茎，管状，中空有节、无叶。花穗聚于茎端。花褐色。地下球茎即为荸荠。至寒露时停止灌水。立冬到立春时期为收获季节。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001024": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001024",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001025": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001025",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001026": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001026",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><h2><span style=\"\">第42节：打翻夏天雨水的一枚青杏--荸荠(2)</span></h2></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001027": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001027",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>\t</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001028": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001028",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>荸荠虽与莲藕一样出于污泥，可是当你洗净，就会发现那一种紫红或深红的光亮，十分诱人，把它们盛在白瓷碗里，紫的更紫，红的更红。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001029": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001029",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001030": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001030",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>很多人知道荸荠，读错这两个字的人却不少。荸荠最早叫凫茈。据说有一种水凫鸟喜欢啄它。李时珍也称它为凫茈。他说，凫芘生浅水田中，其苗三四月出土，一茎直上，无枝叶，状如龙须。其根白身，秋后结颗，大如山楂、栗子，而脐有聚毛，累累下生入泥底。也叫乌芋、地栗、通天草。都很形象。现在南方通称马蹄，也是一种形象的叫法。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001031": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001031",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001032": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001032",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>从故乡到邗城谋生，吃过不少的荸荠。价廉物美，水分又足，是初冬极好的果品。卖荸荠的多是村姑，被城管赶着，挑着荸荠担子走街串巷。遇此情景，我总是买很多。那村妇喜滋滋的拿一把小刨子，飞快地削着皮，只一会，就是雪白的一堆。云开月出。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001033": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001033",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001034": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001034",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>邗城也是汪曾祺的故乡。沟河纵横。汪曾祺在小说《受戒》中描写过荸荠：秋天过去了，地净场光，荸荠的叶子枯了。荸荠的笔直的小葱一样的圆叶子里是一格一格的，用手一捋，哔哔地响，小英子最爱捋着玩。荸荠藏在烂泥里。赤了脚，在凉津津滑滑溜的泥里踩着。哎，一个硬疙瘩！伸手下去，一个红紫红紫的荸荠。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001035": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001035",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001036": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001036",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>就这一段，读了多年，至今难忘。这是汪曾祺的名篇。如一支村野牧歌，和风细语，青青绿绿的。汪曾祺的小品文字，已自成一家，很清新。他写淡淡的人情，暖暖的人性。他的文字不深，就像浅浅的野河溪水。荸荠庵。天井。几盆花。石榴树。栀子花。都很可爱。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001037": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001037",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001038": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001038",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>到南方，吃荸荠在桂林。桂林真是个山水佳处。不说山水之美，就是寻常物产也有许多冠甲天下。荸荠是其一。到了这里，应该称为马蹄了。桂林的马蹄，样子也好看，个大，形扁蒂短，乌紫发亮。嚼之，鲜甜，脆嫩，无渣。仿若雪梨。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001039": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001039",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001040": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001040",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>桂林马蹄，种植历史很久远了。远到什么程度？在桂林市南郊一个石器时代的古文化遗址中，曾出土一枚陶质马蹄，比普通马蹄大。这么说，马蹄在桂林，有一万年了。最近读《广西农业经济史稿》，说桂林荸荠，以大墟区拓木乡为多，而以东附廓乡属一村所产为最佳，味清甜无渣滓。我去桂林多次，总想去那个叫大墟区的地方，尝一尝正宗的桂林马蹄。后来，我在桂林吃了马蹄炒漓江鱼片。盛出来一盘，雪白，点缀着黄的姜末、绿的葱花，鱼片的鲜香与荸荠的清脆相得益彰。很是清爽可口。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001041": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001041",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001042": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001042",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>1935年，当时在广西省立师范专科学校任教务长的陈此生先生，曾写信邀请鲁迅先生赴桂林任教。鲁迅因离开讲坛多年，体力日见衰退，便去信解释，并婉言加以推辞。鲁迅先生在信中，除了对陈先生的盛情邀请表示感谢外，还高度评价了桂林荸荠。他在复信中说：&quot;桂林荸荠，亦早闻雷名，惜无福身临其境，一尝佳味。&quot;一代大师，于小小的桂林荸荠不能忘怀，这样寻常的植物，便叫人更加的刮目相看了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001043": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001043",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001044": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001044",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>在四月，我去了桂林。看到了一亩亩翠绿的荸荠苗。南风起，那些水面上的茎草，一丛丛，在风中轻轻摇动。茎端绽开了淡绿色小花，犹如一支支碧玉簪儿。透着秀丽，娴静，婉转。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001045": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001045",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001046": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001046",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001047": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001047",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><h2><span style=\"\">第43节：爱我，趁我青春年少--紫苏(1)</span></h2></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001048": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001048",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>\t</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001049": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001049",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>爱我，趁我青春年少--紫苏</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001050": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001050",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001051": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001051",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>后来才知道紫苏南北都有种植。南方更多些。我就把紫苏列入南方植物来写。紫苏这样梦幻的名字，似乎更适宜于南方。第一次看见成片的紫苏，是在广东河源。大凡紫色，都如梦如幻。说来惭愧，我原先没吃过紫苏。来南方之后才知道紫苏是可以吃的。那是在一次晚宴上。朋友请客，吃鱼生，看见了紫苏。菜市上也有卖，很多都是野生。费些功夫，从山间采摘，新鲜，价也贱。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001052": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001052",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001053": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001053",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>平生第一次吃鱼生。桌上，一只龙形大船，装着满满的冰块。生鱼片，置在冰块上。鱼片切成薄片，肉色玲珑可观。我很奇怪为何鱼片那么白。朋友说，关键是要把鱼血放干净，最佳办法，是先割去鱼鳃，后放入水中，鱼不会马上死去，因痛苦而在水中游动，一边游一边流血。少顷，血尽，鱼肉就会白嫩无瑕，玉色逼人。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001054": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001054",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001055": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001055",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>自己也曾亲手剖过鱼，但像这样割腮放血的做法，还是不能接受。话虽如此，那玉色一样的鱼片，还是诱人之极。龙舟旁边，有数个玻璃碟，晶莹剔透，上面放着各样配料。紫苏，是吃鱼生的配料。吃鱼生，讲究配料。除了葱姜蒜辣油盐酱醋基本调料，还有一些特别的作料，如花生仁，芥末，柠檬，紫苏等。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001056": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001056",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001057": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001057",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>那么一大堆配料，我的目光一下子被紫苏吸引。晶莹的碟，紫苏叶放在里面，被切碎，变成菜丝，但仍可以看到叶子的紫色。紫苏极醒目，像一朵高贵之花，在盛开。我个人性格不是最喜欢紫色。我喜欢绿和蓝。但这样的夜晚，这样柔和的灯光，这样优雅的环境里，那一碟紫色脱颖而出，让我产生醉意与无边想像。红葡萄酒立在紫苏旁边，像绅士。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001058": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001058",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001059": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001059",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>无声细下飞碎雪。夹一大把生鲜猛料，包一片鱼生放入口中，那种鲜香的混合味直冲鼻腔。几种鲜香植物在味蕾的舞台上狂舞。那是阳光与月色在空间交错的感觉。鱼生在各种配料簇拥下渐入化境。一时间嗅觉受到极度震撼，味蕾大受刺激，口舌生津。这时我能很鲜明地感受到紫苏叶，如开在山间丛林里的幽兰，那是我的心情。心情的紫苏叶像夜空绚丽的焰火，在黑色的背景下迷幻而浪漫。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001060": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001060",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001061": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001061",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>鱼生一肴，不过是古代劳苦的打鱼者应付生活的无奈之举。船上没有了油盐酱醋，没有了柴火，有鱼，也只能生吞活剥。没想到这种饱含穷人眼泪的吃法，现在竟然成了一道名吃。来南方之后，鱼生吃过好几回。高低档的鱼生都有。一提到吃鱼生，我就想到紫苏。现在很难想像，吃鱼生没有紫苏会是什么感觉。其实，紫苏的香味极淡，不及芫荽那样浓重。我想，紫苏的主要功效不止是调拌味觉，更多的调和视觉。紫苏的颜色很醒目，在鱼生周围有这样一抹紫色，能让人在齿颊留芳的同时得到宁静与愉悦。就像在颠簸的尘世里我们还能看见山间的野花，情人的眼睛，使人感到生之美好。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001062": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001062",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001063": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001063",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>除了鱼生，再次看见紫苏，是在米粉店。南方的米粉，就像北方的面条，是一种大众化食物。南方街头到处都是米粉店。品牌也多。很多店就在调料上下工夫吸引顾客。北方人初到南方，第一次吃米粉，会茫然不知所措。因为不知道米粉的很多调料，要自己配放。我就出过这样的洋相。原以为，一碗米粉端给你，那就可以吃了，没想到还有很多调料没有放。看到其他人都在放调料，才明白自己的碗里可能缺少了什么。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001064": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001064",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001065": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001065",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>学着别人的样子，端碗过去。桌上放着许多调料品，有十来种。酸豆角，海带丝，酸笋，酸萝卜等。其中就有紫苏，任凭所取。我学着别人的样子，各样配料都放一些。再后来，我对南方米粉产生了浓厚兴趣，吃上了瘾。几日不吃，就特别想。我甚至知道哪家的米粉店质量好，哪家店偷工减配料。我吃粉有固定的三家。他们共同的特点是，都有紫苏叶。据我观察，这三家粉店生意特别好，最主要的原因，都是不惜配料。这是一种营销手段。不惜配料，有的顾客就会放很多，粉店可能暂时损失一些。但这样会吸引更多的回头客。譬如我，就是因为这三家粉店有紫苏，常常光顾。而且，我每次都要放很多紫苏。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001066": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001066",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001067": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001067",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001068": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001068",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><h2><span style=\"\">第44节：爱我，趁我青春年少--紫苏(2)</span></h2></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001069": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001069",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>\t</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001070": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001070",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>白的米粉，紫色的叶子。南方就这样很简单很直接地迷住了我。我开始注意这种叫紫苏的植物。想像它生长的样子。忽然记起，在很多年前，我就见过。2002年，我曾经在广东河源一带行走。去过苏家围。这个村子，是个山水画廊，风景极美。这里有个紫苏园，有蓬蓬的紫苏，一片紫色的雾霭。年年长，年年落。纯粹，又浪漫，成行成片，满眼都是。震撼心灵。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001071": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001071",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001072": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001072",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>这样写着，就特别想吃紫苏叶。决定亲自下厨，做一道清炒紫苏叶。五里亭菜市场，卖紫苏的山里人很多。紫苏叶刚从山间采摘下来，一把一把用草扎好，看着就很清爽。买了一捧回来。洗净。下锅。翻炒。就成了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001073": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001073",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001074": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001074",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>炒好的紫苏叶放在洁白的碟子里。仍然是清亮的紫色，显示出优雅，高傲与神秘，又让人感觉到一种内心里的炽热与大方。一边品尝着清炒紫苏叶，一边想着生活在南方，是件多么幸福的事。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001075": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001075",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001076": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001076",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>听说还有一种紫苏茶，在古代极盛行。《本草纲目》记载，大宋皇帝仁宗，昭示天下，评定汤饮，其结果是紫苏熟水第一。熟水即饮品。也就是说，在宋代，紫苏茶获得最高殊荣。宋代饮料品种之多，绝不亚于现代。孟元老在《东京梦华录》里记载了几十种饮品，其中就有紫苏茶：甘豆汤、豆儿水、鹿梨浆、卤梅水、姜蜜水、木瓜汁、沉香水、荔枝膏水、苦水、金橘团、雪泡缩皮饮、椰子酒、梅花酒、五苓大顺散、香薷饮、紫苏饮。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001077": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001077",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001078": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001078",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>紫苏叶吃过了。紫苏茶还没品尝过。不知道有没有加工好的。不过，总还是能想像出那种滋味---当你沏茶的时候，你会看到山间的小溪急速流淌，河边长满一片紫色的野花，那就是紫苏。清香四溢。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001079": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001079",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001080": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001080",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>已然醉倒千年百年，方才染就十里八里--乌桕</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001081": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001081",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001082": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001082",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>很多古诗脍炙人口。一个共同特点是，作者不自觉中赋予了词语多重解释。每个人因此都可以得到不同的阅读体验，这是古诗恒久魅力所在，也让作者始料未及。譬如，杜牧《寄扬州韩绰判官》中的二十四桥，玉人等。还有一首作品，充满梦幻一样的色彩，千古传颂。张继的《枫桥夜泊》。江枫渔火，还是江村渔火。枫桥还是封桥。枫桥、江枫中的枫，又作何解？至今争论不休。清代王端履著《重论文斋笔录》卷九论及此诗，注云：江南临水多种乌桕，秋叶饱霜，鲜红可爱，诗人类指为枫。不知枫生山中，性最恶湿，不能种之江畔也。此诗江枫二字，亦未免误认耳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001083": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001083",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001084": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001084",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>诗人兴象所至，不可执著。有时是幻觉。有时是想像。有时是记忆。有时是错觉。我个人的看法是，不必追究真相。只要能产生独特美感，无论是枫，还是乌桕，各取所需。可以并存。东坡赤壁，已经很明确不是周郎赤壁，但并不妨碍《赤壁赋》的魅力。如果真要钻牛角尖，王端履的说法，也站不住脚。&quot;枫生于山中，性最恶湿，不能种之江畔，&quot;这句话就有问题。即使不是植物学家，读过《琵琶行》的人都知道：浔阳江头夜送  客，枫叶荻花秋瑟瑟。这枫不是在江边吗。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001085": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001085",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001086": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001086",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>乌桕，一种落叶乔木。李时珍说，乌喜食其子。其木老则根下黑烂如臼，因以名之。江南临水多种乌桕，固然不错，可是，我所读到的，所见到的乌桕，都是出现在山间。我案头有本薄薄的《乌桕》（金代钧著，广西人民出版社1981年版）。这是一本关于乌桕的科普读物。书中列举几种代表性的乌桕树，其中就特别提到，宜丘陵山区发展。并且写到了可以在山地造林，平原和丘陵造林，甚至可以在土地比较干旱的石山地区种植。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001087": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001087",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001088": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001088",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001089": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001089",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><h2><span style=\"\">第45节：爱我，趁我青春年少--紫苏(3)</span></h2></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001090": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001090",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>\t</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001091": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001091",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>如：铜锤桕：主要优点是树体小，宜适当密植，单株结实性能好，群体产量高。适应性强，较耐旱耐脊，宜丘陵山地发展。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001092": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001092",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001093": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001093",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>鸡爪桕：树体较高大，发枝能力强，枝条密度大，幼枝光滑，结果枝比率高。它的优点是适应性强，宜丘陵山区发展。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001094": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001094",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001095": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001095",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>周氏兄弟都写过乌桕。鲁迅在乌篷船上看到的情景是：我仿佛记得曾坐小船经过山阴道，两岸边的乌桕，新禾，野花，鸡，狗，丛树和枯树，茅屋，塔，伽蓝，农夫和村妇，村女，晒着的衣裳，和尚，蓑笠，天，云，竹，……都倒影在澄碧的小河中，随着每一打桨，各个夹带了闪烁的日光，并水里的萍藻游鱼，一同荡漾；周作人写过《两株树》，一株写白杨，另一株写乌桕，他说乌桕似乎只生长于东南，北方很少见。周作人沿用了王端履的说法，认为张继寒山寺诗所云江枫渔火对愁眠，也是在说乌桕的红叶。其实，在整个南方，都有乌桕生长。更多的，是山间丘陵的野生乌桕。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001096": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001096",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001097": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001097",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>人们喜爱乌桕。这是一种温暖的植物。千百年来，乌桕对于人类无言的关怀，使得历代文人墨客为乌桕树写下许多不朽诗篇。乌桕长成后，主要是采收种子，用以榨油。乌桕树收子取油，甚为民利。他果实纵佳，论济人实用，无胜此者。桕油是制漆的好原料。现代人讲究绿色与环保，桕油就异常珍贵。还可以点灯。在古代，桕油是照明的主要原料。诗云：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001098": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001098",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001099": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001099",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>山村富乌桕，枝丫蔽田野。榨油燃灯光，灿若火珠泻。上烛公卿座，下照耕织者。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001100": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001100",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001101": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001101",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>乌桕花，可酿蜜。乌桕木，木质细密，纹理美观，不翘不裂，宜家具，宜雕刻。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001102": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001102",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001103": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001103",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>很多年前，去福建漳州。住一私人旅舍。主人养很多水仙花。我在清雅的水仙花香中洗了脚，意外地穿上了木屐。奇怪的是，脚下的木质软软的，不太硬。问之。说是乌桕木。走几步，又脆脆的响。后来上街，看到许多卖木屐的小摊，牌子上写着，乌桕木屐。还有苦楝、枫木制成的，上用皮革、棕辫作带，女用木屐还上漆描花。木屐价格低廉，穿着干净、凉快。我记得那几天，一到傍晚，就听到一片木屐声，至今不忘。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001104": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001104",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001105": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001105",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>真正领略乌桕红叶之美，是在前不久，与自治区总工会熊玉碧主任去肇庆鼎湖山。在此之前，很少有人知道，我们所看到的大部分红叶，竟是乌桕。而红叶的美名，一直让于枫树。在很长时间里，红叶成了枫叶的代名词。但也有人已经意识到，乌桕的红叶，要甚于枫叶。陆游说，乌桕赤于枫，园林二月中。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001106": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001106",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001107": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001107",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>在鼎湖山的天溪，潺潺山泉流过，游鱼粒粒可数。泉之两侧，路崎岖，遍布野蔓，奇花，异草。越上行，山泉越急。有水帘洞。洞上瀑布飞泻。至老龙潭，水碧绿，清可见底。溪旁悬崖峭壁。老潭周围，多参天古木，野趣盎然。蓦地，几株乌桕，在夕阳下火红欲燃。抬头看，天地间一片的素净。一抹夕阳，自高空斜射过来，那一片乌桕叶，红得妖娆，虽只是群山中零星点缀，却惊心动魄，让人感觉可以燎原漫山遍野。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001108": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001108",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001109": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001109",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>我们走在林荫道上，那火一样红的叶子，绯红点点，如血如胭。有几枚飘飘洒洒，落在我们的肩。我们站在乌桕树下，默不作声。呆呆地看着那几棵乌桕。也许，被那火红的颜色扰乱一点心思。一些想像也许真的会发生。一杯茶的工夫，黄昏就来了。暮色又细又长。我听见岭南名刹庆云寺的钟声，正四面涌来。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001110": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001110",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001111": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001111",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001112": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001112",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><h2><span style=\"\">第46节：蛙声一片，稻香十里--稻花香(1)</span></h2></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001113": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001113",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>\t</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001114": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001114",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>蛙声一片，稻香十里--稻花香</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001115": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001115",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001116": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001116",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>北方麦子。南方水稻。麦子是北方辽阔的大地。比起其他谷物，麦子让人心里踏实和温暖。稻子呢，阳光如雨，稻穗沉甸甸的，是喜悦与光芒。很多年，我的体内依然保持着这种感觉。我的故乡盛产麦子。大麦，元麦，小麦，都有。水稻也种。种水稻是一种非常麻烦的农活。很繁琐。犁地，然后放水，耙田。再种秧，起秧苗，栽秧，蓐草……总之，每种过程都是累死人的活。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001117": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001117",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001118": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001118",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>祖父是种田的好把式。每每稻子熟，我就看到他眉目舒展，捋起袖子敞开怀在田埂上不停地走。我印象最深的一个细节是，他把稻穗托在掌心看几下，数数颗粒，然后摘下稻穗。他的手掌粗糙如磨盘，双手互相捻磨几下，金黄色稻壳就脱下来。吹去壳，剩下白白的米粒。祖父眯着眼睛把掌心放在鼻下，嗅嗅那些稻米的香，疲惫又虔诚的脸上露出少有的笑容，再拿几粒米放进嘴里，轻轻嚼碎。米很脆弱，轻轻一咬就碎了。那时，祖父脸上是稻壳一样的辉煌色。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001119": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001119",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001120": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001120",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>水稻扬花，不特别显眼，花小，细碎的小花粒挂在穗头上，白色，无特别清香味。所谓稻花香，不过是田野上一种宁静和愉悦，一种极好的心境。大片稻田扬花时，会产生条件反射，觉得有阵阵稻花香。辛弃疾夜走黄沙岭，写下稻花香里说丰年；郭兰英唱的风吹稻花香两岸，都是平和喜悦的情境。那时稻子青青。妹妹在田埂上奔跑，催开了古溪河边的一路槐花。祖父在牛屁股后扶着犁。我跟在祖父后面，脚趾间踩着黄牛粪。我常常在祖父满是汗味的腋下进入梦乡。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001121": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001121",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001122": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001122",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>水稻喜温暖，湿润，强光。稻子扬花，在六月，天气正热。那时，稻花是否有香味，谁也不会注意。太阳升起前，祖父已在稻田里拔完稗草，拖着酸痛的腰身走在田埂上。侧目望去，原野上绿油油一片。那是祖父的希望。稻子长势很好，只需勤戽水，又是丰年景象。祖父心里比任何时候都要满足，满脸皱纹也展开了。走在田埂上很轻松，像散步。祖父总是问我，春儿你闻见稻花香了吗。我说什么也没有啊。真的什么也没有。稻花香，在很长的年月之后，我才真正闻到。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001123": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001123",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001124": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001124",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>六月。太阳散发出炫目的光。热辣辣地照着。稻田里的水，在不知不觉中蒸发，娇嫩的秧苗，在渐渐干涸的地里焦渴难耐。田岸边有条弯曲的小渠，水是有的，却很少。祖父就去戽水。戽水要两个人。祖父和邻家大伯顶着草帽，拎一只戽斗，赤足走在田埂上，他俩要给秧田戽水。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001125": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001125",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001126": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001126",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>戽斗实为木桶，一种人力提水灌溉农具。戽斗有两只耳，扣麻绳用。水渠岸上，两农夫面对面站立，戽斗置中间，手里各握一绳。戽水时，动作需协调一致。先将戽斗撂到水渠里舀满水，顺势收绳，戽斗就拉上岸，水倒入秧田。如此反复，连续不断。灼人的日头下，祖父浑身被汗水湿透，腰酸臂痛的那种苦楚，除了世代种田的乡里人，又有谁知道。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001127": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001127",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001128": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001128",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>晚上呢，月白风清，凉爽的风送来缕缕稻花香。祖父拿大蒲扇，在田埂边纳凉，周身弥漫着稻花香的气息，再听听可爱的蛙声，祖父也有逍遥的时候。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001129": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001129",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001130": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001130",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>故乡稻田无边无际。镰刀和脚步在稻田里忙碌。麻雀们做好俯冲的准备。大地和天空即将对话。天地之间，只有阳光。一切豁然开朗。镰刀与稻秸接触瞬间，发出刷刷的声音。成片的稻子倒下，像金色的阳光铺满大地。再一把一把捆扎。祖父抽完一台水烟，就挑担子，把割下的稻，运到打谷场。最后的一抹夕阳慢慢淡去。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001131": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001131",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001132": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001132",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001133": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001133",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><h2><span style=\"\">第47节：蛙声一片，稻香十里--稻花香(2)</span></h2></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001134": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001134",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>\t</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001135": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001135",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>后来在某个日出或某个月夜，记不清了，我看到祖父蹲在稻谷堆旁边，喃喃自语，与稻子喋喋不休说些什么。我很惊异木讷的祖父有如此滔滔不绝的话。他脸上盛满沧桑的沟壑也生动异常。似与稻子话别。第二天，祖父就走了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001136": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001136",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001137": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001137",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>金秋的稻田，是凡·高的一幅画。稻谷打下来，稻草被捆成一把一把，堆得山高。我把草垛里的稻草抽出几捆，草堆就有了一个温暖的草洞。月亮刚好就挂在草垛尖子上。有一次，我硬拖着秋姐钻进草洞。我们也不说话，能够听到四野秋虫的鸣叫。稻谷的清香满鼻子都是。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001138": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001138",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001139": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001139",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>荷枯了。又一个夏天走了。阳光随稻浪一波一波涌向远方。沉甸甸的稻穗，像秋姐的辫子摇晃我的眼睛。稻子要搬家，姑娘要出嫁。稻花就是这样飞到秋姐的秀发上，开出含苞待放的大红喜事。稻子熟了。那年，秋姐出嫁，蒙着红头巾。风儿吹过田野，吹绿了一个少年的心田。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001140": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001140",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001141": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001141",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>我在水稻成熟的季节来到了热烈的南方。住在城里很久了，秋天也改变了模样。我常常走进壮族瑶族侗族山寨。忽然有一天，鼻腔里突然有了亲切的味儿，淡淡的，幽幽而来，绵绵不尽，让人忍不住深深呼吸几下。原来是清清的稻花香。一个美妙的下午，我开始了在南方的一次旅行，因为稻香，我在岭南的一个小山村走过一片稻田。我闻见了久违的稻花香。一般人是不容易闻见的。但是我能。我就痴痴看一回稻子。晚上就做梦。头枕着一片稻谷，居然梦到一个女子，在古溪河边奔跑，她一个侧身的微笑，就已让我醉得不轻。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001142": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001142",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001143": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001143",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>稻花香的日子用阳光浆洗，宽敞而辽远。一些事物，总会在记忆的长廊里走来走去。譬如稻花盛开的声音。我甚至在以后的岁月中常常能感受到原野上清清的稻花。那些波浪起伏的稻子，一片片在风中摇晃，把天空和稻田反复刺入我的眼睛，让我心中生出一次次长长的舒展。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001144": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001144",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001145": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001145",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>南方的岁月如太阳火热。我从南方的一座城市辗转到另一座城市。岭南山间那些零落的稻田总能让我感受到稻花纷扬的气息。南方的风将稻花香轻轻糅进阳光里。我已经记不清黄昏是怎样到来的，太阳又是怎样离我而去。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001146": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001146",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001147": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001147",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>我总在想，什么时候，稻子再扬花呢？稻子一扬花，心上的花都开了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001148": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001148",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001149": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001149",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001150": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001150",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><h2><span style=\"\">第48节：让我醉吧，我好疯给你看--美人蕉</span></h2></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001151": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001151",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>\t</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001152": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001152",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>让我醉吧，我好疯给你看--美人蕉</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001153": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001153",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001154": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001154",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>来南方，我认识了许多美丽植物。其中就有美人蕉。我常常想，我生命里注定与这些植物有缘。跋山涉水，千辛万苦，原来只是为了在这里与她相会。有很多种蕉类植物，天天看见，却叫不出名字。我常常把旅人蕉与美人蕉弄混淆。像旅人蕉那样亭亭玉立，容姿俊秀者，无论如何都可以放在美人之列。可它不是美人蕉。真正的美人蕉，却又让我想起美人娇。娇巧，娇笑。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001155": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001155",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001156": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001156",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>万物皆有情，一点不假。有时我就想，那些不能言语的植物，对于人类怀着多少的情义。她们贡献自己，贡献各类果实谷物，释放馨香，捧出鲜花。偌大的植物王国，奇花异草，争奇斗艳，无不用尽花香形色，令人感叹。想想也是，在纷繁世上，一棵植物长久站在那里，日晒雨露，望穿秋水。身边行者步履匆忙，千帆过尽也等不来匆匆的一瞥，这是何等的伤感与幽怨。但是植物也有非常手段，或放出幽香，或展出千娇百媚的容姿。终于，有一天在不经意间看见了她的脉脉注视，看见了她娇艳的繁花，闻见了妩媚的馨香，在对视的那一瞬间便闪出了热烈的火花，想着一生中能有这样片刻的喜悦，也不枉来此一世了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001157": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001157",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001158": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001158",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>美人蕉是植物里极聪明的女子。她的个头并不很高。想着自己天生的花容月貌，若是无人欣赏，也真愧对上苍对于生命的恩赐了。很多植物，万年孤寂，无人过问默默离去。不若放出妖冶的手段，尽情展示自己一回，或可有人驻足观望。遂把真名隐去，叫美人蕉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001159": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001159",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001160": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001160",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>于是她放下矜持，像喝了点酒，有些把持不住自己。她秋波流转，抛向一阵轻薄的风。阔大叶子如坠地的一袭绿衣，翩舞于风中，袅袅婷婷。一次次艳舞，妖艳的身段被热辣辣的南风狂追猛拍。从她微醉的眼眸里散射出全部的女人味，可她没有做妻子的欲望。含苞欲放，犹如美人的兰花指，一旦清风舒展，便唤醒她那似圣火一样闪耀的花瓣。开出艳红的鲜花，却没有果实，她甚至也没想过要去当一个母亲。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001161": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001161",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001162": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001162",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>风轻轻吹。掀起她的绿裙，她抖动裙裾像拉丁舞一样摇摆。伴随着疯狂的旋律，腰肢在扭动。骄阳当空，奔放的节奏涌出炽烈的情欲。那是些血一样鲜红的花，让人心旌止不住摇荡，使人疯狂。她撩开绿裙向路旁的过往行者展示她的青春骚动。她的花只在夏天开得妖艳。她在夏天的阳光下奔跑，展示着青春的肉体，她的整个身子都充满激情和诱惑。夏天过去了，她仍然会如痴如醉尽情舒展，留给我们无数关于情欲的想像。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001163": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001163",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001164": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001164",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>很多年前我去防城港，第一次来到邕城。在一个明媚的下午，我在邕城火车站看见一个卖花女。就是那么无意间扭头看见的。她梳了一个越南髻，清秀俊美。我问她手里捧的是什么花，她不明白我说什么。原来，她是越南女。那些花很醒目，翠绿的叶片间裹着一束束艳丽的花朵，红艳艳，金灿灿，如一朵朵炽热欲燃的火焰。火红的花朵点燃了我的眼睛，也点燃了那个热烈的下午。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001165": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001165",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001166": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001166",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>有人告诉我，那个花，叫美人蕉。这时，邕城的天空一片晴和。我感到这个陌生城市的一种亲切，有一缕清风从心头拂过。想来想去，应该是那一束束火红的美人蕉。第一次看见，那鲜丽的色彩便给我的心灵以最热烈的炙烤，留给我永久的印记。我即将去海滨城市防城港。我上车，坐下，看到熙攘人群中那个越南女人的背影。她的身影在一片火红的光影里闪动。她一回头，也看见了我的凝望。我急切地想对她说点什么，譬如，我要买她的花。正要开口，车却开了。背影渐去渐远，美丽的双眸却留在我的心中。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001167": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001167",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001168": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001168",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>小区那片疏疏离离的美人蕉一直是我留恋的地方。我看到那些美人蕉正在肆意生长。从早春到仲秋，我每天都会去看她几眼。秋后的美人蕉，也能从冷冷的寂寞中透出绿色的诗意。我盼望着美人蕉能再次绽放花朵。那将是下一个盛夏了。一丛丛美人蕉花繁叶茂，花朵硕大，火红欲燃。花朵叶边，绚丽的花蝶飞舞，一派盎然生机。花的芬芳，蕉叶的绿荫，蝶的倩影，使得过往行者心中无不为之亢奋。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001169": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001169",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001170": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001170",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>那些美人蕉有半人高了，开出艳丽的花，多数是鲜红色，还有黄的。观赏美人蕉最好有阳光。仲夏屋檐下，美人蕉投给你寻常的一顾，顷刻间你会感觉到阳光万里，浑身透亮。雨后的美人蕉含羞欲露，愈加灼灼动人。在雨过天晴的晨光中，抖落露珠，新妆初成，露出最美的一瞬：带露红妆湿，迎风翠袖翻。那朵美人蕉的花，多么像一个笑声，躲在绿色的怀里。当你靠近时会发现，她的花瓣中有少许白色条纹，好似在花瓣上涂抹了一层白粉，薄施粉黛，风情万种，真令人遐想联翩。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001171": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001171",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001172": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001172",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>那天晚上我在小区散步。月朗风清。馨香弥漫。洒水车刚刚经过，美人蕉的绿叶上滚动闪亮的水珠。我的脚步很轻。我隐隐听到了梦中的情话，还有一种临水的惆怅。有声声的呼唤在我耳边响起。我在恍惚之中回到了那个美人蕉盛开的时节，那个火热的夏天。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001173": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001173",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001174": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001174",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001175": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001175",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><h2><span style=\"\">第49节：阳光下，我是一尾漫游的鱼--鱼尾葵(1)</span></h2></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001176": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001176",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>\t</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001177": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001177",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>阳光下，我是一尾漫游的鱼--鱼尾葵</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001178": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001178",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001179": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001179",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>南方与北方贺岁习俗终是有很大的区别。北方，大年三十烧好的大青鱼不能马上吃，白瓷盘里盛着，感觉它在不停地游，游啊游，一直游到初五，留给财神。所谓年年有余。家乡年初五，是迎财神的日子，午夜十二点一过，鞭炮齐鸣，家家户户迎财神。南方就不同。邕城的初五，子时一片寂静。不见一丝的爆竹声。似乎不是禁放，大年三十晚上，也是大鸣大放的。很会做生意的南方人，难道不知道迎财神么。今年春节，多阴天，有时还有小雨。初五上午，洗了澡，就和孩子去动物园。一进门，就看到了大棵大棵的鱼尾葵。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001180": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001180",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001181": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001181",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>鱼尾葵长在一角，静静地游着。看到鱼尾葵，想到一个笑话。北方人初来南方，见到鱼尾葵，一定很惊讶，什么人把好端端的叶子剪成了鱼尾。鱼尾葵叶形奇特，叶色浓绿并富有光泽，给人以清秀之美。鱼尾葵的最大特征，就是它的叶子，酷似鱼尾，造化真是奇妙。远看鱼尾葵，像棵硕大的草，但它是乔木，因其小叶先端呈不规则的锯齿状，似鱼尾得名。鱼尾葵有丛生，也有单棵的，二十多米高，树干有节，如不仔细看，很容易认为是青竹。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001182": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001182",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001183": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001183",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>鱼尾葵除了叶子特别，它的果序也很可观。记得第一次看到鱼尾葵的果序，我是惊呆了，以为不是真的，那样排列有序、整整齐齐的果序让人感到一种梦幻般的精致。鱼尾葵的果序非常奇特，果序长达几米，多分枝，悬垂。果实小球形，成熟后淡红色。我曾亲手摘下几个果子，去皮，有坚硬的核。每序有果数百粒，青绿色，像翠绿的珠帘，又如将军勋绶，极为可观。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001184": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001184",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001185": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001185",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>小区里有许多低矮的鱼尾葵，羽叶较窄，枝多叶茂，高十来米。叶片丛中挂着一穗穗绿色或红色的小果球。鱼尾叶不时随风飘曳，像一尾尾游来游去的鱼。我常常行走在鱼尾葵丛中，真像是游在清碧的水里。迎面吹来清新凉爽的风，感觉心胸一片开阔，只见近处碧波荡漾，远处天水相接，翠绿的鱼尾叶和珠帘垂于水面，随风摆动，如一幅恬静秀逸的山水。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001186": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001186",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001187": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001187",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>动物园就在心圩江畔，平常，我在小区里都能听到园里的鸟鸣。却没想到有这么多的鱼尾葵。鱼尾葵下面是一碧清池，两尺长的红鲤成群结队。一把鱼食撒下去，水里就是一片翻腾。那些鲤鱼成了精，嘴张得很大，嗷嗷待哺的样子。甚至你可以用手去抚摸它们，只是它们滑溜得像泥鳅，怎么也抓不到。那么多鲤鱼，黑压压一片。心想，哪来的那么多的鱼呢。仔细一看，原来是岸上鱼尾葵的倒影。红的鲤鱼，绿的鱼尾葵叶，水里岸上，而我们，生活在鱼群中间了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001188": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001188",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001189": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001189",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>在那个风和日丽的下午，我和孩子在鱼尾葵里穿来穿去。没有柳絮拂鬓，没有暗香浮动。看不见蜂飞蝶舞，看不见秋波脉脉。在我们身边，只有一簇簇的鱼尾葵。那些鱼尾叶快活地在我们身边绕啊绕啊，绕个不停。不是年年有余么，我们身边这么多的鱼。远处还有丛丛娇柔的九里香。这样的感觉是多么奇妙，我想起以前的一段往事。我清楚记得，那个傍晚，在水榭，我们吃了晚饭，一起赏月，就在那时，我惊奇地发现，有无数的鱼儿，追簇着行走的月亮。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001190": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001190",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001191": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001191",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001192": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001192",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><h2><span style=\"\">第50节：阳光下，我是一尾漫游的鱼--鱼尾葵(2)</span></h2></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001193": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001193",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>\t</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001194": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001194",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>很多时候，你无法相信闹市中会有这样一个幽静所在。居闹市却不见游人。那里面是一个植物王国，鱼尾葵长得很高，有三四十米吧，正挂着几米长的翠玉珠帘。掀开翠绿的珠帘，漫步荫生园，醉绿，绿海，抱珠楼，浑身清凉。微风吹来，花香阵阵。在水榭观水处吃了晚饭，看见小小的湖面，居然有初月云出，那轮明月，一直在鱼尾葵里穿行，风一吹，仿佛千万只游鱼簇拥着月亮在水里游动。在那样清幽的月光下，你像一尾游鱼，若有所思。水波飘荡。这情境很容易让人想起传说中的美人鱼。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001195": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001195",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001196": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001196",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>走到湖边，临水远眺，风从湖面吹来，像一首轻柔的歌声拂过耳际，余音不散。珠帘般的果序整齐地挂在天空，叶子随风轻摇，仿佛山林中深潭里欢唱的鱼儿。空山鸟语，寂静悠然的天地。往回走，不觉已是万家灯火，满天繁星。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001197": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001197",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001198": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001198",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>你一直怀疑这是个梦境。可是想想那些鱼尾葵，它们就要开出一条条的花序，结出珠帘一样的果实，那些鱼儿就绕着果实不停地游啊游啊，不知道它们有多幸福。有时你就站在鱼尾葵下仰面观望。鱼儿在天空中游来游去，感觉天空就如此的大了。星光满天。真想抓几尾快活的鱼儿回家。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001199": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001199",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001200": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001200",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>你在鱼尾葵丛里经历过短暂的爱恋。这没有结果的爱并未让你迷惘。只是淡淡的忧郁浮现在你丰满的脸上。你在鱼尾葵丛中若隐若现，仿佛你与这鱼尾葵与这水下的一切本来就是一体。鱼尾葵那长长的树叶伸过来，柔柔地缠住了你，你想轻轻地挣脱，又没有一丝的气力。岸上没有一个人，你分不清那是灰色的阳光还是银白的月光。你有一丝慌乱。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001201": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001201",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001202": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001202",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>你在你的世界里像鱼儿一样悠闲生活。有时你并不快乐。所以你经常走过鱼尾葵，让你的忧郁心情追随鱼尾叶随风飘散。你活在一个遗世独立的世界，透着古典的性灵与光芒。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001203": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001203",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001204": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001204",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>在荒野的阳光里，一个同样古典的书生正抬头遥望，遥望那座竹楼，祈祷竹楼上的你，祈祷你手中的绣球从楼上轻轻飘落，他一个鱼跃，穿过许多鱼尾叶准确接住。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001205": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001205",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001206": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001206",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>在不知不觉之中，鱼尾葵越长越高，我的天空突然间飞满了小鱼儿，密密麻麻的，这似曾相识的情境，使我本已平静的心海如潮涌动。我惊叹哪儿来的这么多鱼儿。我心里生出一些水灵的感觉。我知道，潮湿的回南天即将来临。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001207": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001207",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001208": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001208",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001209": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001209",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><h2><span style=\"\">第51节：金线吊芙蓉--沙田柚</span></h2></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001210": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001210",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>\t</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001211": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001211",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>金线吊芙蓉--沙田柚</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001212": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001212",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001213": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001213",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>去过恭城瑶族县观音乡。很偏远的一个地方，远得像遗落在天边的一轮弦月。地虽偏，风景却好，满目青山，产柚子，黄黄的，漫山遍野垂挂着。柚子缀满枝，像一个个硕大的黄梨，真让人喜欢。它的结果非常奇特，长在纤细的枝条上，往往一根细长的枝条挂着两三个硕大的柚子，感觉随时都能掉下来，给人以命悬一线的担忧。这样的景致，当地人还有个诗意的说法，叫金线吊芙蓉。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001214": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001214",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001215": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001215",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>看到那些柚子悬挂枝头，有时会想，多么像是柚子树渗出的雨滴，很快就要滴落下来。想想，那该是多么大的雨滴啊，滴滴答答落下来，空山寂静，那是深谷的清音，是山野的琴声。有琴无琴没关系，这千古的山水，已是千古之事，凝聚成一个个的柚子在风中悬挂。这些前尘旧事终于没有滴下来，它在静静地想。静静想想，已然是高山流水。桂乡多处地方产柚子，佳品者，为沙田柚，产恭城、容县两地。以前在北方，也吃过柚子。但是，柚子的口味，终是不对，不是苦，就是酸涩。来南方吃到沙田柚，才知道，柚子中还有这样的纯情。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001216": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001216",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001217": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001217",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>柚子在古代，有几个很奇特的名：文旦，栾，抛。实在想不出是什么寓意。古时候的柚子，很不好吃，品种极差，皮厚瓤小，不堪食用，书上称为臭柚。在很长的一段时间里，柚子像个粗糙平常的山野村夫，无人搭理，默默无闻。柚子的声名，一直到清朝才得以改观。八桂大地开始出现一种名扬天下的柚子，沙田柚。沙田柚成熟后果形较整齐、端庄，色泽艳丽，果皮细薄，呈鲜黄色，底部有金钱状的印环，称之为金钱督，这是沙田柚的主要特征。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001218": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001218",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001219": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001219",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>正宗的沙田柚，产于容县沙田乡。民间的传说是，乾隆年间，容县沙田村廪生夏纪纲，从浙江辞官还乡，带良种柚苗回沙田栽种。次年适值当地发牛瘟，家人把牛骸作肥料埋于树根旁，以后更得容县土质，气候长期驯化，才有今天名扬天下的佳果。柚树高十余米，枝叶繁茂，春季绽开小白花，霜降便是它的成熟时节。容县沙田柚除了好吃，还有个好处，极耐贮藏，常温贮藏一段时间后食用，香蜜味浓，口感更佳，像个天然的水果罐头。《容县志》上说：柚，今容地所产，叶类橙，春花秋熟，实大如瓠，皮黄，上尖，下有圆脐，肉白味甜如蜜，曰蜜柚。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001220": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001220",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001221": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001221",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>2007年仲秋。我和区总工会的熊玉碧主任到基层考察，回来时路过玉林，当地工会的领导，送我们每人两箱正宗的沙田柚。这是我第一次吃沙田柚。果然名不虚传。两三斤一个。剖开，一般有十二片瓤瓣，片片形似娥眉月，大小厚薄均匀，瓤肉柔软晶莹，肉质细嫩、无渣。口味极佳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001222": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001222",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001223": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001223",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>很多人吃柚子，只吃内芯的瓤肉，厚厚的柚皮扔了，很是可惜。在桂乡，有一道名菜，柚皮扣，就是用柚皮做的。我吃过这道菜，也亲手做过。用柚子皮，切成小块，稍煮，拧去涩水，再配以五花肉，加调料烹制，最好有豆豉。柚皮扣做成了，其味妙不可言，绵软，甘腴而不腻，色泽黄红，清鲜不淡，真让人执筷难舍，饱尝为快。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001224": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001224",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001225": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001225",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>我寓居在心圩江畔，一边吃沙田柚，一边读废名。很久以前，我就读废名的。废名是现代文学史上的异数。很多人知道沈从文，不知道或者不喜欢废名，多么遗憾。就我个人的艺术趣味而言，这两位现代作家，我更喜欢废名。就像扬州八怪，郑板桥的声名远远超过了金农。世上多数人知道郑燮，却对金农不甚了了。金农到最后落魄潦倒，无处栖身。我一直认定他是八怪中的扛鼎者。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001226": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001226",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001227": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001227",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>人不可貌相。废名长相很特别，照周作人的说法，废名之貌奇古，其额如螳螂，声音苍哑，初见者每不知所云何。但是，废名独特的风格却令人惊奇。很多人不知道废名，可能与他的文字有关。他的文字简洁幽深，平淡朴讷，又生辣奇僻。他用文字走进记忆中的童年世界，建构他心中的世外桃源。他的语言像诗，像山水画。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001228": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001228",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001229": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001229",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>小说《柚子》，是废名的代表作。主要内容写的是：我与表妹柚子青梅竹马，却因祖母为我另缔婚约，弄得有情人不能成眷属。故事并不曲折，人物的不满与怨恨也是淡淡的，给人的总体感觉是忧愁。但是，这样氛围里的柚子，在家境败落的情形下，仍是那样刚强与自尊。柚子和《桥》里的细竹是同一个人，柚子是废名朦胧的初恋情人，一直关注着她。在废名笔下许多人物当中，她是最深情着墨最丰满的一个女性。这是一幅意境深远的画面：已长成大姑娘的柚子家道艰难，与我相互心存爱意：见了我，依然带着笑容叫我一声焱哥。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001230": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001230",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001231": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001231",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>读废名的小说，可以让人心里明净。乡村，是他的一个重要的题材。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001232": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001232",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001233": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001233",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>他写了很多小人物，很多是天真烂漫、纯洁无瑕的儿童：程小林、史琴子、细竹、柚子、焱哥等等，生活的苦难和不幸并不妨碍这些小人物心中闪现出来人性的光辉。他们身上没有惊心动魄的故事。有的只是最平凡的乡村生活。那是无比恬静的乡野风光，是中国最真实的农村：小河环抱，山坡起伏不定，明媚的村庄，还有小溪边浣衣的美丽女子。一个明朗、悠远宁静的世界。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001234": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001234",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001235": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001235",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>柚子春天开花。雪白。还有清香。苍翠的柚子树叶，雪白的柚子花，会让人一下子想起废名的《桥》，想起《柚子》。一个像柚子一样挺拔美丽的女子，正提篮走过石拱桥。她去河边洗发。桂乡女子多乌发，与柚子花有关。她们一直用柚子花洗发。她们说，这是祖上传下来的秘方，用柚子花洗发，可以满头青丝，轻柔顺滑。远处的柚子林，花开了，又飘出几个女子，皆美姿，叽叽喳喳走上石桥，喧笑而过。渐行渐远，影如淡墨。</p></div>"
        },
