            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>\t</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001270": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001270",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>灼灼夭桃--朱槿</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001271": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001271",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001272": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001272",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>人在日月山川里行走，不只是磨难与曲折。栉风沐雨之后也会遇到艳阳高照，山花烂漫。那一刻无数山野气息与朵朵繁花向你扑来。人与花两两面对，脉脉相望，彼此间心扉豁然敞开。无限情语不着一字。天地风光便永驻心间。初来南国，有次行走邕城心圩江畔。忽听后面有人喊我名字。声音很陌生。回头看，不见人影。再看，灌木丛中有两个女生，看着几朵红花笑。花没见过，却红得耀目。叶子像桑叶，花色玫瑰红。真是天生丽质，天光都暗淡了。我走过去问这是什么花。说朱槿花。明白了，谐音的误会。这花名与我的名字谐音，听起来真是那么的像。很奇妙。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001273": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001273",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001274": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001274",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>朱槿在邕城遍地生长。不只在西乡塘，邕城大街小巷都有朱槿花。后来才知道，朱槿花是邕城市花。难怪满城都是。岂止是邕城，普天之下，喜朱槿者多矣。云南玉溪市花，台湾高雄县的县花，马来西亚国花，美国夏威夷州花，也都是朱槿。千古名花，如此普及，并不多见。朱槿花以其美艳的花容顽强的适应能力，融入普通百姓的生活。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001275": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001275",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001276": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001276",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>南方的花多艳美耀眼。朱槿花开放的时候，阳光从敞开的花朵间飞流而过。一蓬蓬，一丛丛，满城都是笑声。一路走一路风光，榕树婆娑，朱槿绽放，乱花渐欲迷人眼，一路恍惚而过，微醺的感觉，春光被打开。朱槿花层层绽放，一片又一片，那种蓬勃气势在这大好春光里张扬。天天花丛漫步，满目姹紫嫣红，仔细想想，这日子真是奢侈。抬头遥望南国天空，风清日朗，走着走着，脚底下都是灿烂阳光。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001277": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001277",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001278": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001278",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>朱槿原名扶桑，古书上说，东海日出处有扶桑树，其叶如桑，故名扶桑。因其花如木槿，颜色深红，又名朱槿。还说，其花光艳照日，又称日及。虽有些夸张，无非是说此花明艳比阳光。唐代李绅《朱槿花》诗云：瘴烟长暖无霜雪，槿艳繁花满树红。繁叹芳菲四时厌，不知开落有春风。说的是，在古代南方山林中布满湿热蒸郁、能致命的蛮烟瘴雨。鲜艳的朱槿花却繁花满树，红霞一片。恶劣的自然环境有时会生出异树奇葩。朱槿是其中之一，红艳无比，且能四时开花，一波又一波，不因春风之来而开，也不因春风离去而凋落。社会环境也是如此。譬如罂粟。再怎样铲除，它总是见缝插针，顽强生存，其花之眩目之艳美，非寻常花等所能及。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001279": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001279",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001280": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001280",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>扶桑生长在一个叫汤谷的地方。汤谷是传说中东方大海中的古国名，位于茫茫大海深处。扶桑乃神木，高数千丈。扶桑树上栖息着十只太阳鸟。强烈的阳光烤焦了大地，庄稼枯死，甚至连石头都快要熔化，海水如开水一样沸腾。人们在灼热的阳光下无法安身。凶狠的毒蛇猛兽乘机出击，伺机害人。英雄后羿挺身而出，决心冒险为民除害。这位英雄连射九日。留下一日，至今还在天上照耀着我们。这就是著名的后羿射日的故事。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001281": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001281",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001282": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001282",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>汤谷在何方，已不可考。说到扶桑，古书上有个扶桑国。《梁书·扶桑国传》记载，扶桑在大汉国东二万余里，地在中国之东，其土多扶桑木，故以为名。按书中方位，大约相当于今之日本，故日本至今有扶桑之代称。鲁迅名诗：扶桑正是秋光好，枫叶如丹照嫩寒。其中的扶桑，即指日本。扶桑树曾栖息过十个太阳鸟，受十个烈日炙烤而无损伤，此树定然是神木了。其花之艳丽耀目，可想而知。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001283": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001283",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001284": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001284",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>朱槿之美，爱者无数。最著名的人物，乃是宋代大书法家蔡襄。蔡襄花痴一个，书法了得，此外他还是个植物学家。他写过世界上第一部荔枝专著《荔枝谱》，并对朱槿情有独钟。他曾在福建漳州任判官。州西有耕园驿，驿庭有扶桑树十株，开花繁盛。前后十几年，蔡襄迁徙他乡，却念念不忘耕园驿的扶桑。数次探访耕园驿，为之作诗作序，甚是殷勤。诗云：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001285": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001285",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001286": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001286",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>溪馆初寒似早春，寒花相倚媚行人。可怜万木凋零尽，独见繁枝烂漫新。清艳衣沾云表露，幽香时过辙中尘。名园不肯争颜色，灼灼夭桃野水滨。--宋·蔡襄《耕园驿佛桑花》</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001287": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001287",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001288": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001288",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>《南越笔记》等书则谓佛桑为扶桑复瓣者，以其中心高出一层花瓣，故一名花上花。朱槿花之艳丽可与牡丹媲美，所谓朱槿牡丹。花冠微微下垂，南方人又习惯称之为大红花。骄阳七月，扶桑敞开热烈胸怀，捧出红彤彤花朵。早晨太阳喷薄而出，日出扶桑，多么绚丽的一个词，鲜花之光艳，之瑰丽，仿若日光照射下的一丛丛火焰。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001289": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001289",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001290": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001290",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>在岭南山间，我看到许多山村女子鬓际插花。这是自古遗传的习俗。女子爱美乃人之天性。一枝鲜艳野花，水灵灵的插入发际，摇荡着山野之风，自然之情。古代南方女子，对于朱槿也是由衷喜爱。她们以朱槿簪于发间，天人合一，朱槿更加美艳，女子更加妩媚。这是屈大均笔下的形象：佛桑亦是扶桑花，朵朵烧云如海霞。日向蛮娘髻边出，人人插得一枝斜。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001291": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001291",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001292": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001292",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>扶桑树其叶如桑，常有同根偶生相依相扶。这形象实在感人。令人想到比翼鸟连理枝。花既如此，人何以堪。旅美作家严歌苓写过一部小说《扶桑》。一百多年前，一个名叫扶桑的中国女子被卖到花旗国。在那个年代，她不可避免地成了妓女。扶桑在蛮荒之地简直美艳无比，不单吸引苦难的男性同胞，也以她的异国风韵吸引白种男人。这部小说着力描绘了中国妓女扶桑与白人少年克里斯刻骨铭心的恋情。是一部大胆、令人激动的爱情小说。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001293": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001293",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001294": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001294",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>暾将出兮东方，照吾槛兮扶桑。这是屈原《九歌·东君》中的开篇。扶桑生长在太阳升起地方。这一定是个偏远神秘的仙山峡谷。我站在南国的山巅向东遥望，扶桑花漫山遍野向我涌来。我转过身，张开双臂，向着身边的扶桑作出一个热烈的拥抱。我看见朱槿花火焰一样缀满了纤细的枝头。灼目的颜色一朵接着一朵。整个夏天都在燃烧。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001295": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001295",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001296": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001296",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001297": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001297",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><h2><span style=\"\">第55节：夏日金色的静谧，已经飘远--芒果(1)</span></h2></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001298": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001298",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>\t</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001299": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001299",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>夏日金色的静谧，已经飘远--芒果</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001300": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001300",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001301": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001301",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>很多人对于芒果是陌生的。那样一种奇形怪状的水果，以为是舶来品。其实不是。纯粹国产。南国百色市产芒果。百色是老区，左江右江根据地。百色起义纪念馆，位于百色市东北郊迎龙山。很少有人知道，百色产芒果，而且是全国最大的芒果产地。邕城去百色，234公里，坐火车，两个小时到达。因为交通便利，往返过数次。每次去，都带回一箱芒果。各种芒果都有。不到百色，不知道芒果品种之繁多，不知道什么叫芒果之乡。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001302": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001302",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001303": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001303",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>我往返百色的原因，是去田阳县。一开始，我并不知道田阳是芒果之乡。这是一个偏僻的小县城，却有着鲜为人知的历史遗存。我要考察的地方有两处，一是去拜谒抗倭女英雄瓦氏夫人。瓦氏夫人墓位于田阳县田州镇那豆屯；另一处是敢壮山。敢壮山位于田阳县白育镇六联村那贯屯，是布洛陀文化圣山，是我重点关注的地方。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001304": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001304",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001305": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001305",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>瓦氏夫人抗倭的故事，轰轰烈烈，发生在明嘉靖年间。瓦氏夫人精击技，会武术，通兵法。她率众七千五百多人，长途跋涉数千里，来到东南沿海与倭寇作战。她身先士卒，在中国古代史上留下了一段千秋佳话。她是我国少数民族出身的不可多得的巾帼英雄。令人肃然起敬。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001306": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001306",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001307": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001307",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>我没有买香。我买了许多芒果，献在瓦氏夫人墓前，向她三鞠躬。瓦氏夫人不会料到，五百年后的今天，她曾经生活的地方，繁花妖娆，遍地果香。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001308": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001308",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001309": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001309",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>百色，地处桂西山区腹地。在百色、田阳、田东三市县的右江河谷地带，有成片的芒果园。这里是著名的芒果之乡。栽培的品种，目前主要有：香芒、青皮芒、象牙芒、紫花芒、桂香芒、串芒、金穗芒等。果实椭圆，皮光洁，果肉甜，蜜味芳香。每到夏秋季节，芒果的表皮由青变为淡绿，继而橙黄，金灿灿，像一个个黄金果。成熟的芒果肉是淡黄色，柔软多汁，蜜甜，气味芳香，令人垂涎。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001310": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001310",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001311": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001311",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>百色芒果，不只是田阳才有。那坡、田东等县也种芒果。有一次，我去那坡县寻找八角林。那坡是香料八角的重要产地。却意外的在那坡县平孟镇看见了一株芒果王。平孟镇是边境小镇，与越南接壤。在北斗村，有一棵古老的芒果树，高约30米，树冠占地面积一亩有余，树干之粗，须有三人方可合抱。这棵芒果树树龄已近百岁，盛果时节，一年可摘芒果1300多斤，最少的年份也收获800斤。这样年代久远的芒果树，十份罕见。村人以为神树。树前有人点烛，焚香。树枝上系有红绸带，那是村里人的祈祷和祝福。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001312": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001312",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001313": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001313",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001314": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001314",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><h2><span style=\"\">第56节：夏日金色的静谧，已经飘远--芒果(2)</span></h2></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001315": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001315",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>\t</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001316": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001316",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>百色产芒果最多的地方，在田阳县。右江河流经田阳，境内还有古美河、福禄河、活旺河、扁村河、玉凤河等一些小河。但是，田阳县地处低纬度，靠近北回归线，夏热冬暖，气候十分炎热。雨水的蒸发量大于降雨量，就形成了干旱地带。这样的气候，却是适宜于芒果的生长。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001317": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001317",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001318": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001318",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>芒果产地，较有名地方，在县城东郊田州镇的东江村。我是专门去东江村吃芒果的。在这里，我第一次看到了像小西瓜那么大的芒果，每个重量可达到2～2．5公斤。色紫红，皮光洁。真是大得吓人。一个人吃一个芒果，还吃不完。此品种当地人称之为香芒。把皮撕开，纤维少、皮薄，核薄，汁多，十分香甜。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001319": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001319",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001320": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001320",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>六月的东江遍地芒果飘香，树上挂的是芒果，地上放的是芒果，车上装的是芒果，手上拿的还是芒果。我去一家芒果园参观。但见硕果累累，满园芒香。许多村人正在园里欢声笑语摘芒果。看这样子，就知道今年的芒果，又是丰收了。问园主今年产量有多少。说，看这样子不下于20万斤。问有多少收入呢。说可以卖到50万元。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001321": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001321",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001322": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001322",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>芒果又名杧果、檬果，果实椭圆形为主。在北方，芒果是稀罕之物。很难吃到。超市里偶尔也有。有些芒果形状奇特，外形有鸡蛋形，圆形、肾形、心形、等等，虽不规则，但都是流线型。皮色有多种：浅绿、黄、深红、紫红。果肉为黄色，有纤维，味道酸甜不一，有芒果香，汁水多，果核大。一般人看见芒果，都有一种怪怪的感觉。即使买几只回来，也是茫然无措，无从下手。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001323": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001323",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001324": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001324",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>来邕城的时间长了，很喜欢吃芒果。也就有了些经验。方法很简单，首先要让芒果熟透，这样皮软，容易剥。熟了的芒果，香味极浓郁。放几个熟芒果在室内，整个房间里都有芒果香。挑选黄熟皮软的芒果，用小刀在芒果尖端，划个十字，然后像剥香蕉一样，四下拉开即可。青芒果，也可以吃。青芒果鲜嫩，酸涩清脆，很多人蘸着盐或五香粉吃，也别有风味。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001325": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001325",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001326": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001326",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>我在南方腹地的邕城享受着芒果美味，也静静地读完了《芒果街上的小屋》。这是一部令我惊异的书。如此优美纯净。一个人。一件事。一个梦。几朵云。几棵树。几种热望和梦想。语言清澈如流水。读这样的文字，在回味的片刻，你会有繁花堕树、清风吹涧之感。一种遥远的关于蛮烟瘴雨的记忆在脑海中有了触动，然后又归于沉寂。你会情不自禁地仰望</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001327": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001327",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001328": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001328",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>天空。你还能很清楚地念出书里的句子：&quot;你永远不能拥有太多的天空。你可以在天空下睡去，醒来又沉醉。&quot;</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001329": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001329",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001330": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001330",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>作者写道：&quot;我写的不单是美国的事情，也是你们的。我肯定，在中国，也有这样一条芒果街。&quot;岂止一条。在邕城，有好多条芒果街。芒果树是这座城市的街景之一。阳光从厚实浓密的枝叶间艰难地挤进来，筛出斑斑驳驳的光影。每到春天，芒果树开出淡淡的黄色花序。芒果开花很多，结果却艰难。但它仍不厌其烦地开下去。细雨霏霏，春风摇荡。芒果花一朵一朵地绽开，又一朵一朵地凋谢，一簇一簇地张扬，再一簇一簇地憔悴。那些芒果花，铺天盖地，向我微笑。直至青涩的果子缀满枝头。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001331": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001331",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001332": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001332",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001333": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001333",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><h2><span style=\"\">第57节：十万八千里的鸟语花香--桂花(1)</span></h2></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001334": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001334",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>\t</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001335": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001335",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>十万八千里的鸟语花香--桂花</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001336": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001336",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001337": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001337",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>三月韶华似锦。我写南国桂花，是在这个明媚的春天。南国桂花在春天开放。中华路，满满一条街，都是桂花树。一路都是桂花香，一路都是婆娑树影。很多人选择走路。走在桂花丛中。衣香鬓影。走走停停，嗅嗅花香。如此情境，即便身处芸芸俗世，什么功名，什么利禄皆可抛忘，情愿这样闲闲淡淡过每一天。浓浓的桂花，香透了这个春天的早晨，又醺醉了树下的多少行人。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001338": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001338",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001339": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001339",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>南国的桂花开得早，那就让她开着。我们先去翁家山赏迟桂花吧。现代作家当中，我是达夫的铁杆粉丝。达夫其貌不扬，却是个天才作家，是现代作家里最具才情的一位。我多次说过，如果把沈从文与郁达夫的作品放在一起，我会毫不犹豫选择达夫。我曾花了好长时间去追踪他的生平与创作。甚至，我终于得到了一封王映霞的手札。我没有恋物癖。但这封手札却让我和现代文学多少有了一丝最直接的联系。我把王女士的这封手札精心保存着。这样，我仿佛感觉到先生离我很近。追随达夫多年，这封信也算给我心中一点慰藉吧。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001340": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001340",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001341": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001341",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>《迟桂花》是现代文学史上不可多得的名篇。我读了二十多年，至今余香袅袅，回味不尽。这篇小说在艺术上最精致、成熟、完美，让人爱不释手。达夫自己也很喜欢这篇小说，他在给王映霞的信中说：&quot;这一篇《迟桂花》也是杰作，你看了便晓得。&quot;&quot;《迟桂花》我自认为做得很好&quot;。作品的女主人公是翁莲。二十多岁吧。不幸守寡。然而人生的不幸并不能掩饰她纯朴自然的天性之美。她纯真，活泼。很容易让人想到蒲氏笔下的娇娜与婴宁。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001342": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001342",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001343": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001343",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>翁家山的迟桂花让人飘然欲醉。翁莲就是那山野里的迟桂花。先是桂花茶。翁莲说，这茶叶里的还是第一次开的早桂，现在开的迟桂花，才有味哩！因为开得迟，所以日子也经得久。接着一男一女游山。花香正浓。翁莲在前。我跟后。她浑圆的臀，紧密的腰，高突的胸脯，一双水涔涔的大眼睛。从背后又吹来了一阵微风，里面竟含满着一种说不出的撩人的桂花香气。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001344": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001344",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001345": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001345",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>一边是空灵苍翠的青山，一边是妩媚动人的翁莲。那种情欲的气息绵绵不断袭来眼前。撩得人心烦意乱。我对翁莲产生了某种邪念。去五云山的路上，一味清凉触鼻的绿色草气，和入桂花香味之中，闻了仿佛是宿梦也能摇醒。一路上源源不断的桂花香，毕竟是山野的气息。就像阳光之于树叶的光合作用，山野的桂花香渐渐地净化了一个人的灵魂。当我觉得两颊潮热、眼睛里也有点热起来的时候，翁莲率真自然的神态、举止，纯洁无邪的心灵，终于使我的心地开朗了，情欲得到净化。看山下景物又是一番赏心悦目的景象：山下面尽是些绿玻璃似的翠竹，西斜的太阳晒到了这条坞里，一种又清新又寂寞的淡绿色的光同清水一样，满浸在这附近的空气里流动。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001346": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001346",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001347": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001347",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>最后，翁莲和郁成了兄妹。世间所说的红颜知己，也许就是这样的吧。就像娇娜。心心相印，但也只是异姓兄妹，是好朋友，是知己。却不做夫妻，也不做情人。如果拿娇娜和翁莲相比较，蒲氏所追求的，是男女之情的一种至境。而达夫所描写的，则是保持这种至境的艰难。这毕竟是文学作品中的形象。现实生活中，异性之间这种纯洁的情感，存在吗。我相信是有的。尽管渺茫得如同寒夜中的几缕星光。而这几缕星光，却是人性中最闪亮的光芒，它给我们越来越贫寒的心灵以抚慰与温暖。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001348": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001348",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001349": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001349",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>迟桂花开完了。南国的春天又飘扬着早桂的花香。桂花三月开放，以前是闻所未闻的。桂花仍是那么细碎微小，然而那是满树满树的气势，一起开放，一起浓烈。叶密千层绿，花开万点黄，落在地上，也还是香尘一片。八桂大地真是名不虚传。处处是桂花。处处花香。尤其在桂林，到处都是桂树。和友人访靖江王府，被两棵巨桂吸引。金桂与银桂。枝荫交加，摇扬葳蕤。是日晚，再去王府赏桂，但见天高露清，山空月明。两棵巨桂如龙凤缠绵，荡漾不定。满树桂花堕地，飘香流金。既还家，桂香袅袅，数日不尽。耳畔桂树风声花香，犹恍然梦中遇也。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001350": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001350",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001351": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001351",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001352": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001352",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><h2><span style=\"\">第58节：十万八千里的鸟语花香--桂花(2)</span></h2></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001353": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001353",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>\t</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001354": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001354",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>桂花入馔，一直是民间专利。桂者，贵也。百姓喜欢，名堂就多了。做桂花糕，桂花糖，桂花莲子羹，窨制桂花茶，酿桂花酒等。似乎任何食品皆可加入桂花。小时吃桂花糕，桂花糖。现在，桂林的朋友送我桂花茶，桂花酒。这两种在我故乡并不多。故乡也有桂花树，却很少，开得也是吝啬，一年中只中秋开放，风一吹，花雨落地。风再吹，花香花影都没了。我故乡的原野太辽阔了，几棵桂花树实在微不足道。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001355": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001355",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001356": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001356",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>桂花茶是花茶中名品。我嗜茶。喜铁观音和绿茶。拒绝红茶。花茶中，只喝魁龙珠，还有就是桂花茶。魁龙珠由富春茶社独家秘制，只能在扬州买到。别处没有。来南方，我带来了几盒魁龙珠，这少量魁龙珠又分诸好友。我基本上是喝不到了。但有桂花茶。桂乡桂花多，桂花茶也多。桂花茶纯正清香，滋味鲜爽，叶底绿黄，明亮细嫩柔软。满杯满杯的阳光中，藏着素雅的绿叶。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001357": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001357",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001358": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001358",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>桂花酒是三花酒厂送我的。我曾去三花酒厂参观，有幸目睹了三花酒的全部制作工艺。并且钻入象鼻山的肚子里，细细地寻访了三花酒窖。这种地道的手工酿酒工艺现在不多见了。我几乎每天要饮一杯桂花酒。一个人独自坐着，摸出酒杯。玻璃杯。喝酒我总喜欢透明的玻璃杯。那样可以很清楚地看到美酒清澈透亮。很多人喝酒，只讲究味醇，却忘了酒色，就像看美人，只看容貌，却看不到身姿的曼妙，真是可惜。斟上二两桂花酒，轻轻抿一口，盈盈的柔和与绵香钻入胸怀。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001359": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001359",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001360": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001360",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>喝桂花酒，就想到故乡的桂花鸭。桂花鸭是金陵有名的特产。此鸭香鲜味美，乃佐酒佳品。所谓桂花鸭，很多人有误会。以为是桂花香味醺制的鸭，或以为肉内有桂花香。其实不是。金陵八月时节，桂花盛开，此时的水鸭正是脱毛季节，肉味极鲜美。故称桂花鸭。桂花鸭与扬州的盐水鹅制法约略相同。街头有固定的小摊。若有客来，去剁上一碟桂花鸭，已经成了普通人家必要的礼数。吃桂花鸭，饮桂花酒，那和惠的风情，人间的温暖，都会在金黄色的桂花里开出来。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001361": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001361",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001362": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001362",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001363": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001363",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><h2><span style=\"\">第59节：为何我每次来到世上你都不在--菩提树</span></h2></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001364": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001364",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>\t</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001365": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001365",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>为何我每次来到世上你都不在--菩提树</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001366": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001366",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001367": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001367",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>菩提本非树。菩提本是树。读《五灯会元》，这样的偈语比比皆是。大凡偈语，通常不是能马上让你明白，要想，要悟。不管你能否悟出什么名堂，但总能让你悬想半天。我没有任何宗教信仰，但这并不妨碍我对于宗教的兴趣。我精读过《大唐西域记》。甚至，我曾沿着玄奘西行路线，走完了国内往返行程。至于佛国的菩提迦耶、那烂陀诸圣地，在梦中也去过好几次。《大唐西域记》（中华书局2000年版）实在是部奇书。吸引我的地方，主要是它描写异域人情世俗，让我闻所未闻，爱不释手。菩提树，就是读此书知道的。却没见识过。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001368": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001368",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001369": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001369",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>多年来，我一直四处寻找菩提树。奇怪的是，我行遍北方大地，怎么也找不到。抑或树是有的，擦肩而过。照佛教说法，是没缘分。想想也是。菩提乃佛家圣树，谁让你不信佛的。尽管如此我仍然没有放弃寻找。我相信一定能找到。后来才知道，菩提树只适宜热带和亚热带生长。只有在南方，才有菩提树。两年多来，我穿越蛮烟瘴雨行走在南方，进入岭南腹地。终于有一天，在邕城良凤江畔，我看到了向往已久的菩提树。满树满树的红丝带在风中舞飞，刹那间，有一丝白莲花般的亮光闪过我的心际，一种奇怪的感觉在我心里触动。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001370": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001370",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001371": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001371",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>玄奘在书中详细介绍了那棵佛陀菩提树。此树颇为灵异，从古至今，戏剧性地充满传奇色彩，经历了人世间的种种悲欢离合。此菩提树原也是极平常的。生长在印度一个偏僻村野。2500多年前，乔达摩·悉达多毅然舍弃王位出家修行。寻求解脱人世困苦的灵丹妙药。风餐露宿，坚持不懈达六年之久。后来，到了一个野村，悉达多独自走到一棵枝叶繁茂的毕钵罗树下盘腿静坐。凝神静思。经过七天七夜的朝思暮想，获得大彻大悟。终于成为一代伟大的教主。毕钵罗树亦从此称作菩提树。菩提就是觉悟的意思。而这个小野村，从此名扬四方，叫做菩提迦耶。后来佛教一直视菩提树为圣树，印度则定之为国树。菩提迦耶的这棵菩提树，玄奘去拜见过。他在西域记中有详细记录：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001372": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001372",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001373": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001373",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>菩提树者，即毕钵罗之树也。昔佛在世，高数百尺，屡经残伐，犹高四五丈。佛坐其下，成等正觉。因而谓之菩提树焉。茎干黄白，枝叶青翠。冬夏不凋，光鲜无变。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001374": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001374",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001375": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001375",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>接着，玄奘详细地叙述了这棵菩提树的种种奇异遭遇。目前在菩提迦耶小镇上的这棵菩提树，虽非佛陀当年原物，却是从当年原树枝叶辗转传承下来的。据说，这棵菩提树自然落下的一片叶子，在黑市上可以卖到十美元。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001376": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001376",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001377": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001377",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>丁亥正月初五。我们驱车去良凤江。来此之前，我曾听好多人说过，良凤江有棵非常奇异的菩提树。至于如何的奇异，多数语焉不详。我决定亲自寻访。良凤江在邕城西南，约七公里。车往郊外去，沿良凤江畔行驶。过了一座石桥，满目翠绿迎面扑来，我们钻进一个山冈。喧哗的市声瞬间不见了。如同进入一个新的轮回。良凤江的草木山色淹没了我们。沿一条泥泞小路，攀上小山坡，坐在草丛里，凭眺远望。一棵大树。满树满树的红丝带。那里好像是个村庄，远远看去，仿佛一幅村居图。小村背后，是长满青翠的山冈。树在村中兀自挺拔，周围是绿色的灌木丛。远远望去，那棵树像座孤岛，在碧波涌动的大海中拔起。云烟缭绕，一派空濛。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001378": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001378",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001379": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001379",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>我没想到，和菩提树就这样猝不及防地相遇。树干十分粗大，约要五个成年人张开双臂才能合围。树的模样，给人感觉总有些特别，对它凝视半天，才明白，这是一棵合抱树。原是两棵，时间长了，一棵树把另一棵树搂紧，不再放开，形成了一棵树。我被这种奇特的造型震撼。从来没有见到过如此紧密的拥抱，密不透风，以身相许。我们只有在树叶上才可以区分这是两棵树。树枝分叉，有两部分，一边枝节直挺粗大，是大树叶，另一边，枝节小巧，柔媚多姿，是小树叶。一棵树上，两种不同的树叶。也是奇观。风一吹，大小树叶互相摩挲，耳鬓厮磨，窃窃私语。情之蜜蜜，意之绵绵，说不尽的恩爱衷肠。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001380": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001380",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001381": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001381",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>有人告诉我，这是国内惟一的阴阳菩提。此树具体来历已无查考。但长势依然旺盛，枝繁叶茂。正是正月头上。菩提树下，香烟缭绕，观音像，香炉，果品，点心，层层堆叠。据我观察，由于南方人口音差异，阴阳树，会听成姻缘树。这样岂不更好。难怪树下聚集了许多青年男女。他们焚香祈祷，神态虔诚。把写着愿望的红丝带，一条条抛在菩提树上。千丝万缕地挂着，不知有多少人来过。满树通红。若不是偶尔看到青枝绿叶，真让人会误以为这是一棵火红的枫树。旁边就是静静的良凤江。那里有个古渡口，很多人从渡口走上岸来，又有一些人走下去。上上下下，人生就这样沉浮。世上多数人并不快乐，就要来找寻，要梦想成真。那些快乐的人呢，又想佛祖保佑。就这样，菩提树上年复一年地系满了红丝带。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001382": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001382",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001383": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001383",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>出于好奇，我想看看那些红丝带上，都写着什么。风一吹，就有红丝带从树上掉下来。心头一紧。我捡起一条看，上面写着：死生契阔，与子成说。执子之手，与子偕老。时间比较长了，人名已经模糊。可现在，这条红丝带从树上掉下来。我心里掠过一丝不安。能写这几句话，应该是位书生吧。有一天，他与她来到良凤江的菩提树下，两人的海誓山盟，系在菩提树上。可是天有不测风云。红丝带掉下来了。他们现在还好吗。我的心中，忽然觉得难过。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001384": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001384",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001385": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001385",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>其实，我们不必固执地去寻找菩提树，也不必相信那些姻缘寄托。如果佛祖当年坐在榕树下，那么，榕树又会成为佛树。只要你心中有菩提，则山川草木皆是佛。事实也是这样，我在南方，看到很多古老的榕树上，同样系了许多红丝带。那些榕树盘根错节，苍老得让人产生敬畏。若只迷信那些所谓的姻缘树，任你把红丝带系满了树枝，也无济于事。正想着，一片碧绿的菩提树叶轻飘飘落下来，落在我的身上。多么美丽的叶子。叶片心形，状如水滴。我把这片菩提树叶带回家。夹在书中。不几日，叶片干枯。吹去叶皮，得到了一片清晰透明、薄如蝉翼叶脉。我叫它菩提纱。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001386": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001386",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001387": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001387",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001388": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001388",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><h2><span style=\"\">第60节：野菜花，风穿的舞鞋--南方野菜录(1)</span></h2></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001389": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001389",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>\t</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001390": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001390",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>野菜花，风穿的舞鞋--南方野菜录</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001391": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001391",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001392": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001392",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>【题记】</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001393": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001393",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001394": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001394",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>漂泊南方，旅居邕城心圩江畔。圩，在我故乡，一直读wei（围），六圩，十二圩等，都在江边。在南方，读xu（虚），是壮族青年男女对歌的地方。我站在心圩江的旷野，像一株植物，孤独地感受着天色的风清日朗。四周一片空旷，满地是茂盛的植物，密密麻麻的。我忽然感到胸怀广阔，像一个帝王。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001395": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001395",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001396": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001396",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>心圩江，原本月色溶溶，情歌欢唱。现在却是一片荒芜。断流久矣。整个心圩江长满野草。很大的一片荒原啊。如果再荒芜下去，又是一片蛮烟瘴雨了。我经常走进半人高的蓬蒿之中，见到了一些奇异的花草。本想采菊心圩江。奈何没有菊。要有，也是野菊。没有找到菊，却意外地遇见各样野菜，品种真是繁多。一时间春风满面，喜不自禁。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001397": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001397",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001398": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001398",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>那段时间，我频繁出入心圩江腹地寻找野菜。野菜吃得多，心也放马似的野，野到我居然做梦，纵舟心圩江。春江水暖，月色清明。绝不亚于酣睡十里荷花之中。也有香气逼人，只不过那是野菜香。向阳的山坡，绽放着许多野花，风穿过它们，向远方去了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001399": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001399",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001400": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001400",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>【一点红】</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001401": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001401",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001402": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001402",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>初来南方，听到这名字，我有一种莫名的惊诧，那感觉是惊艳。无法想像这样雅致的名字会与普通的野菜有关。初次相见，在超市蔬菜区。很平常。和许多野菜在一起，没什么特别，我找了半天，没见到一点红色，满目碧绿的叶子。可她的名字就叫一点红。让人一下子就能记住。万绿丛中一点红。红是暖色，虽只一点，却足以聚集所有的目光。大片大片的绿色看不到，只看到那一点红。如果换成万红丛中一点绿，效果就淡。红铺满眼睛，那一点绿早就被融化。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001403": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001403",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001404": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001404",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>记住了她。就去寻找。心圩江断流已久。长满野草。野草丛中有许多一点红。不只一点。是星星点点紫红的花。很奇怪，你的感觉，就是万绿丛中一点红。叶子的正面是绿色，叶背却是浅紫。风一吹，叶片就摇动。花花绿绿，像十里洋场的舞会。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001405": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001405",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001406": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001406",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>采几把水灵灵的一点红带回家。感觉带回来几个水灵灵的女孩。青枝绿叶，满室都是春天。一点红宜清炒，夫妻、恋人享用。双方对坐，并不说话。要说的话，就在盘子里。盘子洁白。洁白上面是碧绿。你吃下碧绿就是吃下一点红。不是印度女人的眉心红。眉心红虽然也是一点，但周围有红唇，有粉颊，所以黯然无光。哪有万绿丛中一点红那么金贵。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001407": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001407",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001408": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001408",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001409": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001409",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><h2><span style=\"\">第61节：野菜花，风穿的舞鞋--南方野菜录(2)</span></h2></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001410": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001410",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>\t</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001411": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001411",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>一点红吃起来清香嫩滑。一点红。一颗红心。这是一种让我难忘的野菜。她喜爱阳光，多生于荒地，路旁，小沟，山坡，林边的草丛中。不管是万绿丛中，还是万草丛中，她都是耀眼的一点红。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001412": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001412",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001413": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001413",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>【枸杞叶】</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001414": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001414",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001415": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001415",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>来南方之前，我并不知道，在我们身边有那么多的野菜可以吃。即使在最困难时期，吃粗糙的榆树叶，也不知道番瓜花、番瓜苗、山芋叶等可以吃。就那样白白地让它们落在地上，烂掉。还有枸杞叶。没想到那翠翠的叶子，竟是很清香的美味。现在想想，就懊恼不已。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001416": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001416",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001417": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001417",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>故乡的枸杞都是野生的，从没种过，这也是不被注目的原因。田埂上，小河边，灌木丛中，是它们生长的地方。印象中，枸杞果是鲜红的，像小小的红辣椒。那些野枸杞，我们吃过很多。就那样摘下来吃。不是很甜，有籽，味早就忘了，但枸杞果的鲜红，一直挂在记忆中。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001418": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001418",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001419": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001419",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>来南方之后，才知道枸杞叶是可以吃的。菜市里卖的，是枸杞的茎。上面有小刺。买回家来，要小心地把叶子摘下。枸杞叶，碧绿青翠。枸杞叶做蛋汤，极鲜美。是一种炒青的味道。一碗汤里，白，绿，黄，清心明目。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001420": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001420",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001421": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001421",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>心圩江畔，正是枸杞生长的天堂。蔓草灌木，都是野生的。半人高。尝到了枸杞叶的妙处，我就时不时地去采些叶子回来。我只采叶。那种鲜嫩的枸杞头，我是舍不得采的。主要是想让它继续生长，让它开花结果。让我记忆中小小的鲜亮的红果子重新挂上枝头。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001422": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001422",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001423": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001423",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>后来有人告诉我，说可以把枸杞叶切碎，放在通风处，自然阴干，可制成枸杞茶。不过，我没有去做。因为采回来的枸杞叶，不经吃。满满的一捧，只能做汤。要是想清炒，叶子的用量就多。那得要半天功夫去采叶。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001424": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001424",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001425": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001425",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>【蕨菜】</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001426": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001426",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001427": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001427",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>这是一种古老的野菜。生命力异常顽强，在恐龙时代，就有了蕨。也就是说，它是野菜中的族长。被称为山菜之王。可我还是来南方之后第一次见它，也是第一次品尝它的滋味。心圩江畔长着许多野蕨菜，半人高。它新生长的叶茎非常奇特，让你看一眼就能记住。嫩茎卷曲，像新生儿的手臂。也像龙头。更像玉如意。所以，它的别名就叫如意菜。像极了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001428": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001428",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001429": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001429",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>蕨菜很容易找到。它多生长于灌木丛生的阴坡和潮湿谷地。采蕨菜，就是摘下它新生长的嫩茎。此时蕨叶还未长出，上面有一层白色的绒毛。那一柄柄小小的绿如意摘下来就行了。也有紫色的。我采回来，多是炒食。那是一种什么味道呢。坦白地说，有苦味。但这是山野的苦味，透出清香与滑嫩。佐酒极佳。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001430": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001430",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001431": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001431",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>蕨菜鲜嫩多汁，邕城百姓多用来做蕨菜汤。谚云：猪肉解馋羊肉香，不如一碗蕨菜汤。可见蕨菜汤味之鲜美。想想，口水都流出来了。只是，蕨菜汤这名字不好听。蕨者，绝也。多难听。就改名叫如意汤吧。这名字是我取的，多吉祥。许多如意之事，就在汤里，喝下去，一切顺当，诸事如意。比如爱情。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001432": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001432",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001433": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001433",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>陟彼南山，言采其蕨；未见君子，忧心惙惙。亦既见止，亦既觏止，我心则说。……</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001434": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001434",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001435": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001435",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>采蕨是假，约会是真。他们采蕨做什么？就是想做如意汤。喝了朱氏如意汤，我心则说。但这如意汤虽由我命名，我却没有亲自做过。总想找个机会试试。只是来心圩江畔采蕨之人，日益增多，男男女女，其中不乏假采蕨真约会者。心圩江远离闹市，周围又有数所高等学府。是个约会的好去处。一边采蕨，一边等待。其中多数人满面春光，多数人我心则说。可见蕨之暧昧，如意汤之神奇。蕨不再是野菜，成了奇货可居的姻缘梦。现在，要在心圩江畔采到一把蕨菜，已很不容易了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001436": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001436",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001437": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001437",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001438": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001438",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><h2><span style=\"\">第62节：野菜花，风穿的舞鞋--南方野菜录(3)</span></h2></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001439": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001439",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>\t</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001440": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001440",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>【荠菜】</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001441": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001441",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001442": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001442",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>蕨菜是山菜之王，荠菜就是野菜中的王后。这王后是我封的。把王后这顶桂冠赐予荠菜，一直是我心愿。千百年来，荠菜是野菜中的花魁。色香味俱佳。没有哪种野菜可以与她媲美。名气太大，吃的人太多。只是村野与宫廷，反差太大。把王后二字用在荠菜身上，总是不太自然，就好像一个美丽的村姑，给她涂脂抹粉穿上浓艳的旗袍。荠菜就是荠菜。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001443": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001443",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001444": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001444",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>她的美丽就是山野清香。没有山野气息，没有清香，那就不是荠菜。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001445": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001445",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001446": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001446",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>山野清香，是荠菜的灵魂。是村姑身上的蓝印花布。荠菜也开花，田埂地头，花白色，星星点点，开在嫩绿的叶片之间，那么小，好看得让你止不住心疼。现在很多地方，把荠菜作为蔬菜来种植，架大棚，施化肥，加生长素。这样的大棚荠菜，个大叶大，也像模像样的好看，可它就是赝品，把荠菜最本质的清香丢了，少了村野气息。假得很。吃起来如嚼枯叶，扫兴，败味。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001447": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001447",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001448": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001448",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>吃荠菜，最要紧的，是要亲自到野外的田埂上去挑，才能切身感受到乡野之趣。挑，是我家乡的方言。含有挖、铲的意思。心圩江畔的荠菜很多。我没带小铁锹。实际上我也没有小铁锹。看见荠菜，就用手轻轻拔起。手上沾满泥土。我很久没有这样与泥土接触过了。我的沾满泥土的双手，在那样一个明媚的早上，清香四溢。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001449": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001449",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001450": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001450",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>在南方，野菜无数。荠菜只是其中极平常的一味。在我故乡，野菜就是指荠菜。通常，故乡的荠菜，都用来炸春卷。荠菜春卷包裹了整个春天，吃下去，满身心的春风荡漾。心圩江畔，春日和煦，荠菜盈野。我采了荠菜，只能凉拌。用开水焯一下，即可食。本来，我也想炸春卷吃。可在南方，居然没有地方卖春卷皮。想起来，主要是加工春卷皮有难度。用水和面，加鸡蛋清。置平锅上，摊成巴掌大。这就是春卷皮。平锅下是木炭炉。烙好的春卷皮，薄如蝉翼，轻如细纱，需要很轻巧的功夫。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001451": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001451",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001452": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001452",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>【野茼蒿】</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001453": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001453",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001454": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001454",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>野茼蒿真的很野。野性。顽强。遍布四野。它开一种特别的花。整个花束是圆锥形的。野茼蒿全年开花，花虽小，数量却多。风一吹，种子随绒毛飘荡，飘啊飘，天女散花，落下种子。四处风骚，处处留情。只要有空地，它就生长，无孔不入。所以，它又叫满天飞。它的最大好处，可以在很短的时间内把荒地、不毛之地变成一片绿色的蒿草地。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001455": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001455",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001456": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001456",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>野茼蒿的生命力极强。任何地方都想插一脚。这一点，颇让人讨嫌。最不能让人接受的是，它还想染指庄稼地菜地。不只是想占一席之地，而是大规模的入侵。其结果不言而喻，被采摘，被清理，成了盘中菜。其味与茼蒿略同。嫩茎炒食下酒。叶做清汤，鲜极。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001457": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001457",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001458": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001458",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>野茼蒿很容易采撷。邕城百姓喜食野茼蒿，他们叫此草为安南草。街边所卖，是刚从蔬菜地里采下来的。蔬菜地里并没有种茼蒿，这些都是天女散花的结果。如不及时清除，则危害其他蔬菜的正常生长，四处蔓延，最后登堂入室，占据整个菜地。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001459": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001459",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001460": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001460",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>心圩江现在荒芜着。是满天飞的乐园。毕竟是野菜，味道带苦是正常的。还有茼蒿味，茼蒿味是什么？很少有人说得出。打个比方，如果你看到一个漂亮的女人，可她是风尘女子。那时你心里的感觉，就是茼蒿味。所以，并不是所有人都能接受。野茼蒿再多，不过是荒地上极常见的野草。尝尝鲜，也就罢了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001461": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001461",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001462": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001462",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001463": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001463",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><h2><span style=\"\">第63节：野菜花，风穿的舞鞋--南方野菜录(4)</span></h2></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001464": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001464",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>\t</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001465": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001465",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>【辣椒苗】</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001466": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001466",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001467": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001467",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>辣椒苗与枸杞头很相似。鲜嫩可食。在春天开花之前采撷。我原来也不知道辣椒苗可以炒了吃。也是在菜市场看见的。一把把的辣椒苗，一碧的青绿。就想买回来尝尝。我按照传统方法，用开水焯一下。清炒。基本上，这些叶啊苗的，我都是清炒，除了盐油，调料放得极少，我想得到真味。数量少的，才用来做汤。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001468": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001468",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001469": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001469",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>一个人的口味，是可以改变的。比如吃辣椒。我上学时，不吃辣。后来四处漂泊，接触了各地的饮食，渐渐开始吃辣。比如湘菜、川菜，都能吃。来岭南后，发现这里的人对辣椒并不感兴趣。可我嘴里又淡，极想吃辣味。有一天，朋友送我一罐辣椒，当地产的。也没细看。在我心目中，只有四川、湖南两地的辣椒，是不可以掉以轻心的。有的会辣得掉眼泪。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001470": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001470",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001471": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001471",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>我把朋友送我的辣椒当成普通的辣椒酱，不知深浅地吃下去。只吃一口，顿时昏天黑地，涕泪滂沱。一股辛辣，从脑门直窜脚心。我想，我当时的模样一定是两眼通红，龇牙咧嘴，并且愤怒。浑身火烧火燎。很想找个人狠狠地掐一把才能解脱。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001472": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001472",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001473": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001473",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>从来没吃过这么辣的辣椒。彻底折服了。看产地，天等县。听说过。靠近越南。我经常看到去天等县的班车从北大客运中心开出来。后来才知道，天等辣椒，一般人是碰不得的。特殊的土壤气候，造就这样的奇辣。很少有人能扛得住的。大部分天等辣椒，去了四川、湖南。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001474": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001474",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001475": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001475",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>吃不了天等辣椒，就吃辣椒苗吧。天等不光产辣椒，也有辣椒苗卖。我就炒辣椒苗吃。不过，我吃辣椒苗的时候，仍心有余悸，吃得极小心。生怕辣椒苗有诈。毕竟，那辣死人的天等椒，就是这辣椒苗生出来的。还好。相安无事。只隐隐有一丝的辣味。不知道是不是心理作用。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001476": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001476",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001477": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001477",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>【马齿苋】</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001478": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001478",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001479": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001479",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>恕我的不敬，早年在乡下，马齿苋就是猪草。那年月，人无粮吃，猪倒养得壮实。岂止壮实，那猪肉绝对绿色，没有任何添加剂。就说我家的猪吧，一般吃这几样：大麦粉，小山芋，胡萝卜，各类野菜。我把这些剁碎，煮熟，喂猪。世道真是在轮回。这类猪食，现在端上了大酒店的餐桌。其中就有马齿苋。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001480": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001480",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001481": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001481",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>马齿苋的叶，像马齿，故名。马齿苋的叶与茎，给人感觉，就像邻家胖妹，肉嘟嘟的可爱。胖妹一直是我的跟屁虫，天天随我去挑猪草。但是，我贪玩。常到河里摘菱角吃，或者在槐树下美美睡一觉。哪有心思去挑猪草。太阳落山，我的篮空空如也。没有猪草回去，母亲不会饶我。胖妹挑了满满一篮子马齿苋。我对胖妹说，我们过家家吧。胖妹说好。于是我们拜天地。我问，你有嫁妆吗。胖妹说没有。我说，你就用马齿苋做嫁妆吧。胖妹犹豫一下，还是分一半马齿苋给我。于是，夫妻双双把家还。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001482": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001482",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001483": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001483",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>我对马齿苋的记忆，就剩下这一幕。现在来到南方，各类野菜见得不少。就是没有见到马齿苋。有一回，在心圩江畔，我意外地看到了马齿苋。我心头蓦然一惊，仿佛见到了胖妹。仍是胖嘟嘟的样子。开着小黄花，向我笑。心圩江畔的马齿菜并不多见。采摘的人太多。但只要细心，也能找到不少。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001484": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001484",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001485": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001485",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>【雷公根】</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001486": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001486",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001487": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001487",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>有一种野草，蛰伏在湿润的河岸，山间，草地中沉睡。忽然有一天，雷声隆隆，这野草一下子就苏醒了。它们淋着春雨，就像南方泼水节中的那些女子，个个鲜活，水灵。它们在春雷之后生根拔节，一棵棵长起来，出落得有模有样。这就是雷公根。它的叶片，像马蹄，叫马蹄草，就更加形象了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001488": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001488",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001489": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001489",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001490": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001490",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><h2><span style=\"\">第64节：野菜花，风穿的舞鞋--南方野菜录(5)</span></h2></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001491": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001491",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>\t</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001492": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001492",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>我原来不知道雷公根。在邕城的一些老街头，看到有卖雷公根茶。走过好几次，我很疑惑，不知道这是什么茶。雷公茶装在透明的大玻璃瓶里。褐色。瓶上写着：雷公根茶，每碗一元。桌子下面，放着一些野草，那就是雷公根吧。一个老婆婆，坐在桌边。偶尔有个行人停下，买一碗喝。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001493": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001493",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001494": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001494",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>南方的凉茶，我是深深地领教了。所谓凉茶，就是去热降火。南方天气炎热，人体一旦受到自然界火热之邪的侵袭，则很容易上火。于是，南方人发明了各种去火的凉茶，王老吉，是其中最著名的一种。真正的王老吉是很苦的，简直可以怀疑是不是用黄连做的。很少有人能吃得那苦。但我能喝。而且经常喝上一杯。雷公根茶是第一次见，也想尝尝。特地去买了一碗。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001495": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001495",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001496": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001496",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>我站在街头，端着一碗雷公根茶喝。味很苦。但我知道，大凡去火者，都是苦味。雷公根似乎没有王老吉那样苦。我很快就喝完了一碗。我拿起雷公根看，青青的，刚摘下不久。它的叶子，真像马蹄的样子。我问老婆婆在哪里可以采到雷公根。说在心圩江桥附近。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001497": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001497",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001498": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001498",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>我就住在心圩江桥附近，却不识雷公根。现在认识，也就好找了。果然，在心圩江桥下，有许多雷公根。它们的叶子，像马蹄，更像古代的铜钱。一文钱两文钱三文钱。桥下面铺满了铜钱。我把这些铜钱串起来带回家。真是大赚了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001499": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001499",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001500": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001500",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>【蕺菜】</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001501": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001501",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001502": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001502",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>蕺菜，不一定有人知道。如果写成鱼腥草，就很熟悉了。但是我不喜欢写成鱼腥草。这三个字本身就带有鱼腥味，无论是读或写，总能闻到。不信你感觉试试。鱼腥草是实名制。心圩江畔也长着许多鱼腥草。个头很矮，伏地而生，俯首帖耳的样子。它听命于大地。就像婴儿把身体贴在母亲胸前。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001503": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001503",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001504": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001504",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>我像个痴人走在干涸的心圩江底。遍地丛生野草灌木，让我目不暇接。我关注它们的形色香味。实际上，大部分植物对我来说很陌生。这里像个小小的植物园。我一直在想，为什么这里的植物如此丰富。后来我知道，心圩江不远处，有一个八桂田园，是植物研究中心，规模很大。里面长满各类花草树木。很多植物种子随风飘散。鱼腥草就是这样从空中游来了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001505": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001505",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001506": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001506",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>鱼腥草名字不雅，却长得俊美。花开淡色，中间有穗状花序。叶茂花繁。心形叶，嫩嫩的绿，叶脉带些紫色。茎上有节。野生于田埂、沟边及背阳山地草丛中。我一直想知道，鱼腥草是不是真的有鱼腥味。我决定亲自试一下。我摘下几片鱼腥草的叶子，放在鼻下闻。似乎没有传说中的那么夸张。或者说，有一点鱼腥味，要仔细才能感受到。揉之。叶烂，绿汁满手。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001507": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001507",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001508": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001508",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>这时，才真正有了鱼腥味。而这味，来自它的汁液。看来，名副其实。因为有鱼腥味，多数人不愿采摘。心圩江桥下，是鱼腥草的天堂。遍地都是，没人要。那些绿叶子在风中摇来摇去，真令我欣喜。我感觉到有无数的鱼在心圩江里游来游去。我捉了这些鱼带回家。有腥味要什么紧，茼蒿还有蒿味，芹菜有药味，臭豆腐不还是美美地吃了。去腥味简单。开水焯一下就行。不能彻底要什么紧，就留那点鱼腥味吧。没有一点个性，怎么能让人记得住。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001509": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001509",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001510": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001510",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>能吃到凉拌鱼腥草是一种口福，但不是每个人都能消受得起的。我吃鱼腥草，有独家的秘诀。想来想去，决定把秘方公开，毕竟，一人独享美味，有些寂寞。草木天下有之，让更多的人明白草木对人的情义，我觉得有公开朱氏秘制鱼生的必要。这是一种另类吃法。鱼腥草的茎叶太娇嫩，经不得炒、炖，不能单独做菜，只能凉拌，添一味清香。具体的吃法，兹介绍如下：</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001511": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001511",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001512": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001512",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001513": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001513",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><h2><span style=\"\">第65节：野菜花，风穿的舞鞋--南方野菜录(6)</span></h2></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001514": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001514",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>\t</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001515": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001515",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>青绿的春叶，白生生的须根。洗净。切碎入盘。调料是关键。辣椒酱，葱白，姜丝，芥末。这是鱼腥草的上佳的吃法，生吃。写到这里，你该知道怎么吃鱼腥草了。对，当鱼生吃。鱼腥草蘸着调料入口，大嚼，嘴里脆生生的响。这一种感觉，庶几可以和深海鱼生媲美，一种冷香，一种暖意，在嘴里缠绵。缭绕不去。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001516": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001516",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001517": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001517",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>【苦马菜】</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001518": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001518",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001519": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001519",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>有苦瓜就有苦菜。在邕城街头，我见过两种苦马菜。一种是种植的，一碧的青绿色，菜叶向上长，叶面平，叶边像锯齿；另一种是野生的，菜叶自根部向周围摊开，叶柄处是紫红色，最大的特征是，叶边残缺不全，皱褶，粗糙，像麻布。平叶菜味淡，批量生产的，苦味已改良，多数人都能接受。皱叶菜却是正宗的野菜，苦味重，多数人并不喜欢。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001520": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001520",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001521": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001521",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>苦茶的味是一种清苦。苦马菜的味，是一种幽幽之苦。心圩江畔的苦马菜，是纯正的野菜，自生自灭。味极苦，苦得让人吹胡子瞪眼睛，对它失去信心。那么多的蔬菜野菜，新鲜又清爽，干吗还来自找苦吃呢。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001522": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001522",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001523": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001523",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>我原来生活的城市，有家百年老菜馆，叫菜根香。很有名的。有个厨子望名生义，真的做了一道叫菜根香的菜。全部是菜根，竟然大受欢迎。最常见的菜根，有青菜根，白菜根。吃野菜，吃菜根。真不明白现代人的口味，到底是高了还是低了。我忽然想到苦马菜的菜根。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001524": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001524",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001525": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001525",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>苦马菜开花之后，菜叶就老了。不能吃。就那样长着很可惜。于是，我想尝尝它的根。咬得菜根，百事可成。那就更要咬咬菜根了。拔出苦马菜根，不大，细细的一条，没有根须。洗净，白嫩的样子。切碎，加料，生吃，竟然没有苦味，清香，清脆，是一种冷僻的韵味。可与扬花萝卜媲美。这道秘制菜根香，没人知道。我也秘而不宣。不然，大家蜂拥而至，都拔去了菜根，我到哪里去享受这样的野味呢。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001526": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001526",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001527": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001527",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>夜色深沉。温暖的灯的光影下，一边吃着秘制的菜根香，一边喝着啤酒。苦味没了。苦马菜一样的往事却不时涌来。我的南漂是孤独的，但毕竟是到了一个阳光温暖的地方。有吊脚楼。有山歌。有浅笑着拉我跳竹竿舞的女子。我的胡须好久没有剃了。头发的样子一定像那些蓬乱的苦马菜。我轻轻地把酒杯握在手心，轻轻地，如同抚摸一个女人。她爱我，为我吃尽了苦头。亲爱的，这是何苦呢。我感到一种钻心的痛楚。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001528": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001528",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001529": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001529",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>在江南水乡，寻觅李清照的蚱蜢舟--蕹菜</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001530": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001530",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001531": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001531",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>来南方之后，我频繁地听到一个词，客家人。事实上我遇到了许多客家朋友。他们热情好客，待人友善。博白县，在岭南腹地。客家人为避战乱一路迁徙，来到这个蛮烟瘴雨之地。当时，这一带山高林密，毗连千数百里，常常数十里渺无人烟。对一路风尘的客家人来说，这里是休养生息的好地方。于是就住下。所谓客家人，是岭南土著对他们的称谓。博白成了客家人最多的一个县。我到博白县很近，到玉林后，再转车，半小时就到了。博白的朋友请我吃客家菜。我是第一次吃。菜端上桌，都是大盘，分量很足。像东北菜。传统的客家招牌菜是：盐焗鸡、酿豆腐和红烧肉。到博白，还有一样菜是少不了的，蕹菜。朋友说，到了博白不吃蕹菜，会后悔一辈子。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001532": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001532",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001533": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001533",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>有那么神奇吗。蕹菜就是空心菜。说白了是大众菜。哪里都有。哪里都吃得。何以博白的空心菜那么神乎。又一想，人不可貌相，植物何尝不是如此。天下之大，平凡之中总有独特。博白的蕹菜风靡岭南，人们一提博白，脑子里条件反射似的，就出现了蕹菜。不起眼的蕹菜，成了一个县的招牌，自然有它的不寻常。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001534": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001534",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001535": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001535",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>  </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001536": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001536",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><h2><span style=\"\">第66节：野菜花，风穿的舞鞋--南方野菜录(7)</span></h2></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001537": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001537",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>\t</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001538": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001538",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>更奇怪的是，蕹菜端上桌来，报名：有凤来仪。当时我就有些晕。普</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001539": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001539",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001540": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001540",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>通的蕹菜，再怎么联系，与凤也扯不上边啊。细看，蕹菜清炒。盘子很大。上面栖息一只凤凰。蕹菜是整条的，没有切碎。凤尾是叶子，上面洒些红白相间的蒜片与辣子丁，很漂亮。洁白的蒜瓣，红红的辣子，绿油油的蕹菜。翠绿的蕹菜变成了美丽的凤凰。化腐朽为神奇，就这么简单。清爽，生动。像极了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001541": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001541",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001542": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001542",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>蕹菜不是腐朽。它是大好春光。它青翠的绿色早已让人置身蕹菜地。蕹菜地是什么样子？我见过。故乡太多。阡陌葱茏，整整齐齐的一片绿。那就是春光。春光给人的感觉不只是欣欣向荣。春光就是怀春。怀春是什么感觉？怀春就是焦急不安，心里空旷一片，需要急切地放进什么才舒坦。满满的一盘春光来了，正好能满足你。大好春光里有凤来仪，心情大好，胃口大增。蕹菜入锅前青绿色，出锅后的菜叶竟变成了翠绿。这时最好下箸。动作须快，冷了会变成墨绿，发黑。色淡了，味就淡了。大好春光稍纵即逝。快乐总是短暂的。只一会，凤飞走了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001543": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001543",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001544": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001544",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>在南方，有叶的蔬菜都称为青菜，这是一个大概念。青菜里包括蕹菜。青菜通常不切碎，整个下锅。除了炒，还有一种南方吃法，把青菜放进开水里焯一下，捞上来后，再放些调料。有凤来仪就是这一种吃法。我到现在还在回想博白蕹菜的滋味。怎么说呢，我想到两个字比较贴切，糯香。蕹菜没有青涩味，也不苦，与我以前吃过的空心菜大有区别。故乡的空心菜有一丝的清苦，而且清脆。博白蕹菜不是，不是很脆。脆不都是好事。蕹菜就不宜。如果满嘴里都是脆生生的嚼着，就少了温柔。博白蕹菜的糯香就是温柔，先是凤落梧桐翩然惊鸿的一瞥，紧接着浓郁的糯香迷住你的舌头和牙齿，那是恋人之间香吻的缠绵。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001545": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001545",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001546": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001546",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>凤飞走了。齿颊留香。博白蕹菜果然名不虚传。回味，意犹未尽。还想吃，怎么办。主人似乎早已摸透了客人的心里。最后一道蕹菜端上来。却是清汤。有个大气的名，叫青龙过海。白瓷盆里盛着清汤，几条青龙卧于其中，清爽，简洁，又极传神。其构思之精巧，想像之丰富，令人拍案叫绝。有凤来仪。青龙过海。一桌简单的宴席，变成了龙凤呈祥。这是多么令人开心的事。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001547": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001547",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001548": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001548",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>我故乡的蕹菜都叫空心菜，是在旱地里生长的。我记忆中似乎没见开过花。不知什么原因。我怀疑是不是一茬一茬的苗割去之后，就很难开花。当时自留地里种空心菜，是因为能反复采摘。一段时间之后，又长出新叶。南方的蕹菜较多是在水田生长。在博白，我看到许多的蕹菜田，却不知道里面是不是有水，或者是不是没有水而变成旱蕹了。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001549": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001549",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001550": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001550",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>但是我在城郊的南门塘，看见几亩真正的水蕹。这是一种延续了两千年的种植方法。水蕹，就是在水里生长。像水葫芦吗，不是。用筏种。就是说，把蕹菜种在水筏上。水筏的材料是竹子。南方竹子多，砍伐，编成竹筏。竹筏上布满小孔，蕹菜的种子就放在里面。及长，茎叶皆自竹筏孔中生发。时间长了，就是满满一筏碧绿的蕹菜。竹筏置水中，随河水上下，任意放流。或系于河岸，或泊于池边，走走停停。袅袅婷婷。像个山野的女孩。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001551": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001551",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001552": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001552",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>蕹菜一旦长成，则茎叶茂盛。采摘之后，不几日又长出新叶。离离水上草。采采复采采。哪里能采得尽呢。一年里，大部分时间都可以采摘。蔬菜当中，能如此持久采摘的，除了韭菜，就是蕹菜。采蕹菜，简直就是壮乡人在水边的一场对歌。对歌者是青年男女。歌是情歌。小伙撑了竹排，去河里采蕹菜。水流甚急。小伙紧追不舍。总想牵着她。姑娘左右躲闪。最后，山歌唱完了，小伙追到了姑娘。牵着她的手。水流走，她也走。欲走还羞。蓝天。碧波。绿菜。清风阵阵。山野花香。花是蕹菜花，像百合。</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001553": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001553",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p> </p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001554": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/51a210526ab7fa86/text/000001554",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-595ed6 twpub-51a210526ab7fa86-9882b5\"><p>我从玉林到博白，是专程去寻访王力的。王力在当地声名之大，可以淹没整个博白县。我用的《汉语史稿》（三册，中华书局1980年版）早就翻烂了。王力故居在县城西郊的新仲村。王力就出生在这里。童年也是在这里度过的。皇皇巨著，一代大师。大师之所以能成为大师，是他拥有一颗温暖之心。哪怕是一棵小草，他都可以产生悲悯与关怀。王力曾考证过博白的蕹菜。他认为，博白蕹菜可以与越南河内蕹菜相媲美，是天下奇蔬。</p></div>"
        },
